301161.desc: Wa ha ha! My "universal-as-long-as-there-is-a-ceiling" swing set is finally complete! Commander, are you jealous? Want to give it a try? Too~ bad~! This seat is reserved only for the noble and elegant Yukikaze!

301162.name: Winter's Snowy Wind
301162.desc: Wa ha ha~! Did your heart skip a beat from seeing the charming Yukikaze? Hmph... Well, looks like the Dragon Empery girls are setting off firecrackers... let's go join them! Here, make sure to hold on to my hand!

301168.name: The Warmth of Spring
301168.desc: This outfit is sooo cute~ ehehe... Ack!! *cough* *cough*! Ahem! From now on, you are the faithful companion of Yukikaze the Great! As such, you will not be permitted to leave my side, understood?

301171.name: Pumpkins and Festivities!
301171.desc: Commander, trick or treat! I expect you to give some candy to my sisters as well! These will-o'-wisps? Hahaha~ I tried imitating that gloomy sister of mine!

301179.name: Kagerou (Retrofit)
301179.desc: The newly-retrofitted Kagerou has arrived~ I won't let that sister of mine pass me up anymore! Commander, lead us forward towards distant shores!

301181.name: Mooncake Merchant
301181.desc: I see a chance... to capitalize on the Dragon Empery's famous mooncakes... Commander, would you like to have a taste of the Moon Palace's delicacies? If you buy them in bulk, I'll give you a special discount.

301189.name: Shiranui (Retrofit)
301189.desc: If you have this much money remaining... then you may visit me and spend it with confidence... A discount, you say...? Of course... Someday, I shall give you one...

301211.name: Snow Day Hatsuharu
301211.desc: Everyone's playing together...? I-I think I'll pass... Y-you want me to join them? Ugh, well, if you say so, then I-I-I'll try to socialize with them...!

301212.name: Hatsuharu in the Limelight
301212.desc: C-Commander, I will be your partner for the party tonight. Let's see, umm... I believe this is proper Royal Navy etiquette... D-did I do it correctly?

301213.name: Hatsuharu's Cat Café Caper
301213.desc: U-umm... In order to conquer shyness, umm, I've come to serve you... I just hope I don't get in everyone's way... Y-yeah! Thank you for your encouraging words! I'll do my best...!

301219.name: Hatsuharu (Retrofit)
301219.desc: Hatsuharu, retrofit complete... H-hopefully I'm a little bit stronger now...

301231.name: Holiday Special Wakaba!
301231.desc: Yaho~ Good morning, Commander! For a limited time only, Wakaba Claus will be delivering Christmas presents! Huh? My bag? Aaahhh! C-Commander, help me pick everything up!

301232.name: A Healthy Dose of Sunshine!
301232.desc: Hmmgh! Oh yeah... Ah, there you are, Commander! Care to join me? Come bask in the afternoon sunshine, it feels great!

301242.name: Perennial Joy
301242.desc: Cheers, Commander~ C'mere, you've got to enjoy the party too! If you're thinking of doing something tactless like running off to go back to work, people are going to get upset with you~

301249.name: Hatsushimo (Retrofit)
301249.desc: Hatsushimo's retrofitting is complete. You don't think I look all that different? Oh, Commander, you're still as simple as ever~ I've changed in tons of ways beyond what's just on the surface. Heheheh~

301251.name: Unending Friendship
301251.desc: Hope everyone enjoys the oodles of balloons I made for this party! Yeah, I'm sure the little girls will love 'em!

301259.name: Ariake (Retrofit)
301259.desc: Ah... So this is what it feels like to be retrofitted. I'll work harder for your sake, and for everyone in the 27th Destroyer Division~

301260.name: Yuugure
301260.desc: Sixth ship of Hatsuharu class Destroyer— Yuugure

301261.name: Maid-In-Training!
301261.desc: "I, Yuugure the maid, shall dedicate myself to Ariake, my sister, and you, Commander!"... Eek?! M-my skirt...!

301262.name: Twilight Blossom
301262.desc: The Dragon Empery's New Year celebrations and new outfits are sure to lift everyone's spirits~ My sister will probably love this new dress as well. Commander, what do you think?

301263.name: Evening Flower
301263.desc: I finished changing, Commander. This dress is very pretty, but... isn't it missing something up top?

301264.name: Summer Festival Shopping
301264.desc: Woah... These stalls have all sorts of amazing things~ Commander, will you help me pick a gift out for Ariake? Hm, let's see... How about this Daruma doll?

301265.name: Fun in the Sun
301265.desc: I was really looking forward to playing with you at the beach, Commander, so I changed into this swimsuit. Umm... Ariake told me that I had to choose something that was easy to move around in, and cute enough to make you lose your mind... Was she pulling my leg?

301269.name: Yuugure (Retrofit)
301269.desc: Ariake-class destroyer, Yuugure, has completed retrofitting. Ehehe, from now on... Ariake and I will be in your care once more, Commander.

302019.name: Yuubari (Retrofit)
302019.desc: I've finally finished developing my new equipment! Since we still have time, let's go and try it out in live combat right now, Master!

302040.name: Nagara
302040.desc: First ship of the Nagara-class light cruisers, Nagara.

302041.name: Spring Breeze Leisure
302041.desc: Good evening, Commander. This room...? Ah, it's a special Dragon Empery-themed set I bought from Akashi's. It looks pretty snazzy and was on sale, so I picked it up. Ehehe~

302050.name: Isuzu
302050.desc: Second ship of the Nagara-class light cruisers, Isuzu.

302051.name: Night of Fairy Tale
302051.desc: There will be lots and lots of ghosts and spirits during Halloween... I, I’m not afraid!... say, can, can you hold my hand?

302052.name: Cozy Christmas Eve
302052.desc: Commander? I only came here to help wrap up all the presents for tomorrow, n-not because the fireplace is too cozy and I don't want to get up...

302053.name: Accidental Overheat?
302053.desc: Wooah! ...I fell down again... But at least it's cooler now... Huh? A photoshoot? Noo, don't take a picture of me~

302054.name: Charge, My Trusty Steeds!
302054.desc: W-w-woah! W-wait up! You guys are going too fast! I'm gonna fall! I'm gonna faaaaall! You're supposed to carry me in a way that doesn't give me a heart attack!! Commander, something crazy seems to have happened with my cavalry~!!

302059.name: Isuzu (Retrofit)
302059.desc: Retrofit complete! ...Umm, Commander? ...Wh-what's the matter? Do I really look that different...?!

302061.name: Beach Paradise
302061.desc: Mmfhuhu~♡ What's the matter, Commander? Enraptured by my charms? Heehee, you're frozen in place! You can't begin to think of how to compliment me, can you? "Enough staring, out with the compliments!"

302062.name: Boisterous Night on the Cruise
302062.desc: Heheh♪ The brightest star in the venue, she with the power to shake the earth – none other than Natori, of course! Go on, Commander, and kneel before me~ "Nuo ho ho, even the whippersnapper is amazed!"

302070.name: Yura
302070.desc: Nagara-class light cruiser number four – Yura.

302071.name: We are Succubi?
302071.desc: Uh... I think these clothes are a bit too much... Commander, I... don't look out of place in these, do I...?

302080.name: Kinu
302080.desc: I'm Kinu. If you want this demon to do your bidding, then you'd better show me what you're capable of!

302081.name: New Year's Blade Demon
302081.desc: Grr! What are you here for? Speak up. ...Oh, you just wanted to take a tour of the club activities? Sorry 'bout that, I don't like getting disturbed in the middle of this kind of training.

302082.name: Token and Ghost
302082.desc: Well? I've still got one card in my hand. If you want to win, then show me everything you've got! I will not have you disrespect me just for wearing a silly costume!

302089.name: Kinu (Retrofit)
302089.desc: Retrofit complete... Look forward to commanding the might of the demon ascended. I shall not disappoint you!

302090.name: Abukuma
302090.desc: Sixth ship of the Nagara-class light cruisers, Abukuma.

302099.name: Abukuma (Retrofit)
302099.desc: Combat retrofit complete! First Torpedo Squadron flagship, Abukuma, ready to sortie any time!

302109.name: Mogami (Retrofit)
302109.desc: Are you sure this is a retrofit and not some weird hazing ritual? I look... Well, I suppose I do feel stronger. Guess I'll try to work a bit harder. Wouldn't hurt for you to look forward to it a little.

302110.name: Mikuma
302110.desc: Mogami-class heavy cruiser number two – Mikuma.

302111.name: Offerings of Floral Grace
302111.desc: Commander, may you and all our friends enjoy peace and good health... Alright, what did you think? That was a ceremonial dance I'd like to offer to everyone at the main event.

303010.name: Furutaka
303010.desc: First ship of the Furutaka-class heavy cruisers, Furutaka.

303019.name: Furutaka (Retrofit)
303019.desc: What's wrong, Commander? Why are you staring at me like that? My body? Yes, some things seem to have gotten bigger... Want to take a look?

303020.name: Kako
303020.desc: Second ship of Furutaka-class heavy cruisers, Kako.

303029.name: Kako (Retrofit)
303029.desc: Performance upgraded, improvements complete. This way I can finally... *cough* Oh, it's nothing, Commander. I must simply be more strict with you in the future. Are you ready for your psychological examination?

303030.name: Aoba
303030.desc: First ship of the Aoba-class heavy cruisers, Aoba.

303040.name: Kinugasa
303040.desc: Second ship of the Aoba-class heavy cruisers, Kinugasa.

303060.name: Chikuma
303060.desc: Tone-class heavy cruiser number two – Chikuma.

303061.name: Premium Prize on the Table
303061.desc: Commander, would you like to share a drink... or play a game together? If you win, I'll share some secret intel that you're sure to love.

303070.name: Myoukou
303070.desc: First ship of the Myoukou-class heavy cruisers, Myoukou.

303080.name: Nachi
303080.desc: Second ship of the Myoukou-class heavy cruisers, Nachi.

303089.name: Nachi (Retrofit)
303089.desc: Howzit? Now that my retrofit's all done, don't I look even more perfect than before? Maybe now, our ever-so-reserved Commander here will be super impressed by my new abilities~ Wh-what do you mean I've been staying up too late training with my rigging? W-we're not gonna talk about that!

303090.name: Ashigara
303090.desc: Myoukou-class heavy cruiser number three - Ashigara

303091.name: Brief Intermission
303091.desc: Phew... I finally managed to fix my dress... but I just can't seem to get used to it. Commander, how does my dress look? It's not strange, is it?

303092.name: Kaleidoscopic Summer
303092.desc: This whole "fashion coordination" concept is still a bit hard for me to wrap my head around, so I'm glad Nachi helped me pick out a swimsuit. Now, I just need to... Hey, Commander! Open your mouth! H-huh?! But this is what Nachi told me to do... is there some sort of problem?!

303100.name: Haguro
303100.desc: Myoukou-class heavy cruiser number four – Haguro.

303101.name: A Blessing in Disguise?
303101.desc: Ow! That freakin' stings... Can't believe I actually slipped on the stairs and hit my foot. Just how clumsy am I? ...Oh, Commander? Uh, welcome?

303102.name: Caught By Nightfall
303102.desc: H-hey, help me out! ...No, I didn't come in here for fun. When I finished my security duty last night, I got to thinking about how I was going to give you chocolate for Valentine's and fell asleep. When I woke up, I was stuffed in this thing...

303110.name: Takao
303110.desc: First ship of the Takao-class heavy cruisers, Takao.

303112.name: Beach Rhapsody
303112.desc: Commander, even I’ll get embarrassed if you keep staring at me like that... Eh? Why did I bring a volleyball? Did you not order me to bring it?

303113.name: The Lessons of Spring
303113.desc: Practicing writing is a type of training, isn't it? Commander... do you want to sit down and write with me?

303114.name: School Romanza
303114.desc: Hmm... school life, huh? It's a fairly fresh experience for me. Would it be fine to pin my hair up like this? What do you think, Commander?

303115.name: Full Throttle Charmer
303115.desc: Ugh... S-such shameless attire... If not for Atago saying that it would benefit me to experience different things...! It looks good on me?! I, I see...

303116.name: Divine Exorcist's Blade
303116.desc: My five senses are sharper than ever, perhaps even TOO sharp. No matter what trap awaits, my only way forward is to pierce through and focus on overcoming this trial... Haaah!

303118.name: Sakura Hanami
303118.desc: Commander, I've been undertaking countless bride training sessions in order to prepare for this day. As your bride, I won't let you down.

303120.name: Atago
303120.desc: Second ship of the Takao-class heavy cruisers, Atago.

303121.name: Summer March
303121.desc: The warm breeze that gently wraps around your skin, and delicate footsteps across the white sand... isn’t this the essence of summer? Commander, what does summer mean to you?

303122.name: Hallmarks of Winter
303122.desc: Oh my, it's begun to snow. Commander, should we find a nice, quiet place to enjoy the view?

303123.name: School Traumerei
303123.desc: Student handbook, textbooks... twin guns, torpedoes... and what else... Huh? Commander, I'm just packing my bags for school... is there anything I'm missing?

303124.name: Stunning Speedster
303124.desc: So, you want big sister to be your "fleet queen"? You got it. But you'd better give it your all out there, or else I'll be upset with you!

303125.name: Full Moon's Feral Wolf
303125.desc: Awooo! Tonight is a full moon, so you'll want to be extra careful so I won't eat you up! ...Just kidding. Even if I were a werewolf, I'd still protect and keep you safe.

303128.name: Lily-White Vow
303128.desc: Commander... Ahh, from now on, shouldn't I call you "darling?" Come and hold my hand... Ah, at times like these, I just can't help but to want to eat you up, dar~ling~

303130.name: Maya
303130.desc: Third ship of the Takao-class heavy cruisers, Maya.

303140.name: Choukai
303140.desc: Takao-class heavy cruiser number four – Choukai.

303141.name: Tidy Store, Tidy Mind
303141.desc: There, that's it for the entrance... Oh welcome, Commander! I've been cleaning, so give me a moment... I'll be right with you!

304010.name: Kongou
304010.desc: Kongou-class fast battleship number one – Kongou.

304011.name: The Beauties of Nature
304011.desc: We must fully live in the present, whether during work or during leisure - this is my mantra. Commander, shall we go for an outing together?

304012.name: Hospital Talent
304012.desc: "Celebrity Endorsement of the Port Medical Facilities"... Hehehe, you've made a wise decision picking me. Commander, I can leave the ad shoot to you, right?

304013.name: Breezy Commute
304013.desc: It would be a shame to pass on this lovely weather, Commander. Why have a dull commute by train when you can enjoy a leisurely bicycle ride in the sunlight, hm? Heehee♪

304014.name: Troubled Seas
304014.desc: That was a big wave... I need to balance better on my board, or else... Commander, can I take your hand – Hm? What's slippery? I have no idea what you're... Hyah?! My swimsuit?!

304020.name: Hiei
304020.desc: Kongou-class fast battleship number two – Hiei.

304021.name: Moonlit Cruise
304021.desc: Look how late it is... Commander, shall we embark on a dreamy voyage together?

304022.name: Fragrant Red Plum
304022.desc: I have to admit, these qipaos from the Dragon Empery are quite elegant... I might sound arrogant saying this, but I feel like this outfit really brings out my charm. Hehe, wouldn't you agree, Commander?

304023.name: Beauty of the White Sands
304023.desc: We're headed for the white sands of the beach today. We all could use a breather every now and then, so let's just enjoy the sea breeze today. Hehe~

304030.name: Haruna
304030.desc: Kongou-class fast battleship number four – Haruna.

304031.name: Free Time Before Class
304031.desc: I think it's fine to enjoy school life once in a while... Hm? You wanna know what I'm listening to? Sure, if you're okay with just one earbud.

304032.name: Scarlet Innocence
304032.desc: I guess that looks right... Since Kongou chose this for me, I must trust her judgment... Um, C-Commander, would you mind helping me out? ...It's a bit hard to walk in this outfit...

304033.name: The Elegant Lotus
304033.desc: "My dear Commander, is this dress that my sisters tailored for me to your liking?" ...Okay, no, I can't do polite Hiei-speak like she can... So, anyway, h-how do I look?

304040.name: Kirishima
304040.desc: Kongou-class fast battleship number four – Kirishima.

304041.name: After-School Cannon Time
304041.desc: Commander, enjoying school life is all fine and well, but we must not forget our duty... That said, what missions are waiting for us today?

304042.name: Summery Audacity
304042.desc: Being in front of my sisters in this outfit is one thing, but it really is embarrassing to be wearing it in front of you, Commander. Um... ahem! What do you think? Since you're here, want to walk down to the beach together?

304043.name: Casual Dazzle
304043.desc: "Commander, bad luck for you, but you're just going to become another notch on my blade." Haha, just kidding, it's a joke! So, what do you think? My New Year's attire is pretty snazzy, isn't it?

304044.name: Graceful Ink Incense
304044.desc: The Lunar New Year is known for its hustle and bustle, but it's nice to just sit down with a brush and take in the smell of ink. Hey Commander, got any words you want to see rendered in calligraphy?

305010.name: Fusou
305010.desc: First ship of the Fusou-class battleships, Fusou.

305011.name: The Celebration of Spring
305011.desc: Yamashiro said always dressing like a witch can be a bit old-fashioned, so she gave me a new outfit. That kid... Do you think it looks good on me, Commander?

305012.name: Perfect Partner?
305012.desc: Changing into leisure clothes, and waiting for the return of my beloved... Milord, I too have changed since meeting you.

305018.name: United in Heart and Soul
305018.desc: For richer, for poorer, in sickness and in health, to love and to cherish... May we be together forever, Milord.

305019.name: Fusou (Retrofit)
305019.desc: Milord! Thank you~ Not just for the retrofit, but for many many things. Hehe, it was the greatest of fortune for me and Yamashiro to meet you.

305020.name: Yamashiro
305020.desc: Second ship of the Fusou-class battleships, Yamashiro.

305021.name: Summer Offensive?
305021.desc: It’s just not summer without beach volleyball! Ah... Milord, you’re not playing? But I went through all this effort to pick out a swimsuit...

305022.name: Holiday Offensive
305022.desc: Merry Christmas! Milord, milord, how do I look? Is my Christmas outfit pretty? Ehehe~ Big sis also praised me today!

305023.name: Dressy Black Cat
305023.desc: Fusou told me that I have to wear a Western-style dress to the banquet, so she got one for me! Milord, Milord, isn't this dress pretty?

305024.name: Sales Clerk Offensive?!
305024.desc: Milord, Milord, welcome to the store! Yamashiro is a sales clerk today! Mhm, I'll do my best!

305025.name: Vacation Offensive!
305025.desc: Woah, even the air tastes totally different at this vacation spot! Milord, Milord, um, Akashi asked me to bottle up some of the air here for her! Want to give me a hand?

305026.name: Street Corner Offensive!
305026.desc: Uwaah! M-Milord?! I'm so, so sorry... You didn't get hurt, did you? Um... This is my school uniform. Fusou tailored it for me, hehe~ ... Awawa! I should head off to class now! See you later!

305028.name: Bridal Attack!
305028.desc: Milord, Milord, I've finished changing! What do you think, what do you think? Milord, do you like Yamashiro's dress~?

305029.name: Yamashiro (Retrofit)
305029.desc: Milord! I can do anything now~ bombardment or aerial strikes! So, the thing is, you can totally count on me, much much more, Milord! Milord~!

305030.name: Ise
305030.desc: First ship of the Ise-class battleships, Ise.

305039.name: Ise (Retrofit)
305039.desc: Planes: check! Main guns: check! Nobody can stop me now! Let's sortie right now, Commander! I'm fired up and wanna wreak some havoc on the battlefield!

305040.name: Hyuuga
305040.desc: Second ship of the Ise-class battleships, Hyuuga.

305049.name: Hyuuga (Retrofit)
305049.desc: Aviation battleship Hyuuga, sporting new powers, reporting in! Rest easy, Commander, I'll show you my true post-retrofit power!

305051.name: Great Fox's Respite
305051.desc: I shall be hosting the commander today. Manjuus, I beseech you to help me look my best. I am... *yawn* a bit sleepy... Urghh... what is that ruckus out there? C-Commander! When did you arrive?

305052.name: Guardian Fox's Shining Furisode
305052.desc: Perfect, you have arrived. As long as you are here, the usual moon-watching will prove to be much more enjoyable... Why don't you stay here today and rest for a while?

305053.name: Guardian Fox's Vacation
305053.desc: I heard that it is custom to play a "sport" at this kind of event, involving throwing pillows at others. Heheh, then I shall put the might of the Big Seven on display!

305054.name: Guardian Fox's Procession
305054.desc: Though this is a splendorous dress befitting the occasion, it is too different from my usual attire... Mutsu and Mikasa have nothing but praise for it? If you say so, then perhaps... I can take your word. Hehe.

305055.name: Guardian Fox's Blessed Bonds
305055.desc: C-Commander? What brings you here at such a time? I was just... trying to help everyone prepare for the New Year's celebrations... Ngh, why isn't this red string... coming loose at all?

305058.name: Great Fox's White Gown
305058.desc: It may be presumptuous of me, but please take care of me from now on... Is that acceptable? S-Somehow, it feels a little embarrassing... Ahaha...

305061.name: Warring States Warship
305061.desc: Commander, check it out! "Nothing can stop me!" Urakaze made it for me! Now I can play warring states with her! Heheh, you should know I'm a force to be reckoned with! Can't you come play with us? Why?

305062.name: A Maid's Mis-service?
305062.desc: Hmh? If fah foo, Fummamuh? ...*gulp*. I'm not lazing around! I'm just checking on the pastries that just came in! What are you doing here anyway? To "taste-test?" Or is there something wrong with the pastries? Why?

305121.name: Poolside Persuasion
305121.desc: Refreshing drinks, delicious food, warm sunshine... and a pool to beat the heat? Heh, isn't this the essence of summer?

305081.name: Hometown Zest
305081.desc: An inspection? ...You're awfully gung-ho about your work considering how hot it is outside... Surely you wouldn't have some sort of ulterior motive?

305082.name: A Glimpse of Greatness
305082.desc: Commander? ...You were looking for me? Hah, you have the most atrocious luck. I've just started getting comfortable and I'm not leaving anytime soon. Besides, the banquet will be done in time even without my help... You seem to be enjoying yourself. How about you join me instead of merely staring?

305101.name: Violet Moonglow
305101.desc: "Welcome back, Master." Rather, that's what all the children at the café were saying to you when they greeted you at the door. Hehe, is this some new custom?

305102.name: The Purple Rabbit's Marksmanship
305102.desc: ...Hmph. Hitting such a target is but an easy feat for me... Commander, tell me which prize you want. I'll win it, along with all the other ones I've been asked to get.

305108.name: Purest Wisteria
305108.desc: Commander, the contract has been made according to your wishes. From now on, I will be your new refuge. Now, beloved Commander, are you prepared to live up to MY expectations?

306010.name: Hiyou
306010.desc: Hiyou-class aircraft carrier number one – Hiyou.

306020.name: Junyou
306020.desc: Hiyou-class aircraft carrier number two – Junyou.

306031.name: The Dream of the Autumn Pillow
306031.desc: While everyone slips into sweet dreams from the night's festivities, the sound of gossamer sliding off of smooth skin reaches your ears... Hehe, would you like to spend this night under the stars with me, Master~?

306041.name: Joy Comes on Fledgling Wings
306041.desc: Commaaaaander~! Over here, over here! I'm right here! Chirp, chirp! Commander, come hand out balloons with me! Did you know these balloons can bring you good fortune? Here you go, the first one's for you!

306050.name: Shouhou
306050.desc: First ship of the Shouhou-class aircraft carriers, Shouhou.

306051.name: Patrolling Witch
306051.desc: Waaaah! My candy! Candy is spillin’ everywhere! ...Wh-why are y’all chasin’ me? Commander, help me catch the pumpkin!

306059.name: Shouhou (Retrofit)
306059.desc: Commander, how do I look now that I've grown up? Are ya fallin' in love with me already? Mhm, ye definitely are~

306061.name: Slacking Samurai
306061.desc: *yawn*... Finally, a good night's rest... Now, to pick up where I left off on that RPG... M-m-m-milord, why are you here?! I wasn't slacking off or anything, I w-w-was just... Ughh....

306062.name: Dragon Hunter: Ryuujou's Rise
306062.desc: All right! Steady! Steadyyy! Gottem! Hahahah! Now I'll– M-Milord?! I-I'm just, umm... enjoying an after-school break!

306063.name: The Dragon Slides In!
306063.desc: Milooord! *splash*... Heheh, behold the amusement park's crown jewel – the Meandering Megamanjuu Dragon Slide! If that's too long, it's also known as the Manjuu Octopus Slide. Personally, though, I think the former name is cooler!

307011.name: Paradise Amaryllis
307011.desc: "When you gaze long into the abyss, the abyss also gazes into you." Commander, please do not forget that when you gaze at Akagi~ *giggles*

307012.name: Plum and Snow
307012.desc: Commander will always remain by Akagi's side... Right, "Gods?" Of course... Akagi will deal with the pests.... Ahaha...

307013.name: Ruby-Laced Beauty
307013.desc: Commander, I've been waiting for you~ What a sinful one you are, to tempt Akagi like this for so long... But at long last, nobody will ever get between us again...♡

307014.name: Dawn-Phoenix's Summons
307014.desc: This banquet is my present to you... and your attendance is the greatest reward I could hope for~ Indeed, I shall not grant you leave tonight until you pass out. Ehehe... Ahahaha~♡

307015.name: Precipice of Sweetness
307015.desc: Commander, open up. Say ahh... Heehee, heheheheh... You're like a little baby♪ Receiving a lovely new outfit and seeing a different side of you... How blessed am I?

307018.name: Deep Crimson Poppy
307018.desc: We should send out even more invites... This is the best way to rid ourselves of those pesky vixens all at once!

307021.name: Everlasting Killing Stone
307021.desc: "You only live once?" Where have I heard that saying before... Commander, are you getting excited?

307022.name: White Fox's New Year
307022.desc: One must wear appropriate attire for the New Year. What do you think, Commander? Let me hear your opinion.

307023.name: Exalted White Wings
307023.desc: This statue seems to have been inspired by the teachings of the Iris Orthodoxy. Though I am unfamiliar with this kind of art, gazing upon such majesty... fills one with a sense of piety. Commander, can you feel it as well?

307024.name: Gentle Blossom's Sigh
307024.desc: I never thought you'd end up taking such a long trip with me just to pick up a dress... Though I'm worried about leaving my sister behind at port, I suppose I should take your advice and relax a bit.

307025.name: Dusk-Simurgh's Vigil
307025.desc: What are you doing up here?! Oh, it's you. I thought you went to see my sister? ...You needed a breath of fresh air? That's all fine, but you should return to my sister soon before she does something mad.

307026.name: Snowsilk Fox Dance
307026.desc: I came in expecting to play an assassin, but instead I'm a dancer. Did Akashi come up with this setting? Well, whatever... As long as I get to fight, there's nothing worth complaining about. Commander, hide behind me if you ever encounter a monster.

307028.name: Sacred Blue Lily
307028.desc: "To hold one's hand and grow old together with him"... If it is to be with you, then it won't so bad.

307031.name: The Crane Amidst the Pines
307031.desc: I tried wearing something a bit different from usual, but I'm not sure it suits me... Commander, what do you think?

307032.name: The Counselor Girl
307032.desc: Counselor girl Souryuu! Remedy the school atmosphere and correct your learning attitude, and...well, in short, I protect the discipline of the school.

307039.name: Souryuu (Retrofit)
307039.desc: If I can become stronger through this... Commander, what are you staring at? Don't you still have work to do?

307041.name: After School Bullies
307041.desc: Without girl bullies, there would be no disciplinary girl. So...before sister catches me, let’s cause some mischief at school.

307049.name: Hiryuu (Retrofit)
307049.desc: Retrofit complete! Aircraft Carrier Hiryuu, reporting for duty! Hahaha! I finally got the chance to use that line! I'll be counting on you once more!

307050.name: Shoukaku
307050.desc: First ship of the Shoukaku-class aircraft carriers, Shoukaku.

307051.name: The Crane that Dances With the Wind
307051.desc: I prepared this outfit just for the occasion, so... Commander, you're not going to disappoint me, are you? Hehe~♪

307052.name: Sororal Wings
307052.desc: Hehe, this kind of work is a simple matter for me. Commander, please look forward to my performance~

307058.name: White Crane of Domestic Bliss
307058.desc: Through building this relationship with you, I've made so many happy memories. Now I think it's time to work toward a new goal! Heehee, I was serious about that, you know. Commander, I look forward to many long years together with you♡

307060.name: Zuikaku
307060.desc: Second ship of the Shoukaku-class aircraft carriers, Zuikaku.

307061.name: Ceremonial Crane
307061.desc: New Elite 1st CarDiv, Zuikaku, reporting for duty! Ahh, I've always wanted to give such a cool introduction! Shoukaku would definitely make fun of me if she heard it, but I wanted to try it while everyone is in a festive mood... Commander, what'd you think?

307062.name: The Wind's True Name
307062.desc: Commander, I volunteered to take this job in order to help you out, but this outfit... did it always require such a high degree of exposure...?

307063.name: Zoom Like the Wind
307063.desc: Sis, how's my car lookin'? "All clear, ready to go at any time." Alrighty, just leave the rest to me! Commander, you're about to witness what I can accomplish from the cockpit!

307071.name: Forbidden Fruit
307071.desc: You're taking so long to dress yourself, my Commander. Are you struggling to find something to match my dress? Hehe, it doesn't matter what you wear, you're always perfect to me♡

307072.name: Phoenix's Spring Song
307072.desc: Hehehe, I let Christmas and New Year's slip right by me, that I might use the Dragon Empery's Lunar New Year to capture my Commander's attentions... Oh, My Commander, won't you please enjoy the show I've prepared for you♡

307073.name: Enraptured Companion
307073.desc: Do I make a nice race queen, my Commander...? Hehe. With these proportions, and my fantastic outfit~♡ The others couldn't hope to compare with me!

307074.name: Sweet Time After School
307074.desc: Ehehe~ There is no greater bliss than being with you after classes are over, my Commander~ The kitty here seems to agree♡

307075.name: Seaside Daydreams
307075.desc: A beach date, just me and my Commander... I could walk by your side forever—No, I can't be satisfied by this alone. And neither can you... Right, my Commander?♥

307076.name: Fun on the Baize
307076.desc: Aah... I didn't think you'd agree to my offer for some extra "entertainment" together♡ Just the thought of you using your body to guide mine now... Heehee♡ I'm all yours to command.

307078.name: Temptation on the Sea Breeze
307078.desc: My Commander~ Do you like the location that I've chosen~? We have the entire evening to ourselves, free from the disturbance of anyone else...! Ahhh, my heart is throbbing even more vigorously than the ocean's waves~♡

307081.name: Dreams of the Hazy Moon
307081.desc: The moonlight dims beneath hazy clouds, and the lights of the night sky begin to shine... The moon, and this sake, are both intoxicating... Will you not enjoy this fine evening with me...?

307082.name: Moonlit Chrome
307082.desc: Hnnh... Such clamors of merriment... Would this one be welcome amidst these festivities? Alas... If you so desire, how can this one refuse...?

307083.name: Dreamy White Sands
307083.desc: This world of pristine sand that you have envisioned, a mirage that fits only within the confines of a dream and a reverie... No matter how many times we meet here, this one finds herself drawn to this place again and again...

307084.name: Visions of Fantasy
307084.desc: As a flickering, quivering phantasm... Welcome to the dream this one made for you, Commander. Do you like this magic, in which this one appears in an instant?

312010.name: Akashi
312010.desc:
Repair ship Akashi
Can be built after unlocking

312011.name: Akashi's in the Red, Nya!
312011.desc: Commander, how does Akashi's new outfit look, nya? Isn't it cute? If you like it, then put a ring on it. I mean, everyone's gone out to play... if you don't help empty my inventory, I'll go broke, nya!

312012.name: The Black Cat Cometh!
312012.desc: Heheh, this is what I've been saving up for, nya~♪ A special dress that combines Gothic fashion with Sakura charm! Commander, how about those gems, nya?

312013.name: Welcome to AzurCon!
312013.desc: Ohh, it's Commander, nya. Have you come to buy Akashi's new work, nya? Today's a holiday, so go ahead and enjoy yourself, nya~

312014.name: Welcome to Sofmap!
312014.desc: Hehehe, come on in, nya! Can I help you find something, nya? Your genial and knowledgeable staff, Akashi, will gladly provide her detailed recommendations, nya!

312018.name: White Cat's Repayment
312018.desc: Commander, because of your continued patronage of my shop, I have no choice but to return the favor with my body, nya~! ...Just kidding, nya. Having that said, I really do love you, Commander. Even more than I love gems, nya~

401011.name: "Rebellious" Top Student
401011.desc: Because she’s the Z1, her results will of course be NO.1! Hehe, no matter where she goes, Z1-sama will always be the best!

401019.name: Z1 (Retrofit)
401019.desc: Hmm... So this is a retrofit, huh? Not bad! Rejoice once more, Commander, for no task or enemy is too daunting for the new and improved Z1!

401231.name: Philosophy Sensei
401231.desc: This is going to be on the exam! If you don't take thorough notes, I am going to punish you!

401232.name: Breezy Doubles
401232.desc: Haiyaaah! It's up to you, Ayanami! Oh, Commander! Are you actually keeping score? We might not be having a serious match, but that's no excuse for you to stand around and do nothing.

401233.name: Perfect Smile?
401233.desc: Welcome! A table for one today? Um... Commander, my smile doesn’t look stiff... right?

401234.name: The Banquet's Honor Student
401234.desc: Oh, good evening, Commander. I was just looking for Javelin and the others... Say, would you like to keep me company for a bit?

401235.name: Café Trainee @New Base
401235.desc: Hi, welcome! How may I serve y– It's you, Commander?! Err, well, I'm working as a trainee at this Sakura Empire-style café, you see... What do you think of this outfit?

401236.name: Serious Idol @Acting Manager?!
401236.desc: Jeez... Javelin's got what it takes, but I'm really concerned about Laffey and Ayanami. Oh well, I guess it's up to me to manage them... Commander, please don't forget to support me too.

401237.name: The Eyecatch in the Rye?
401237.desc: Commander, please help hold onto the ladder. I've almost got the book... Just a little more... All right... C-Commander?! Please don't look up!

401238.name: Schwarze Hochzeit
401238.desc: Whew... Sorry to keep you waiting. I was having a hard time deciding which outfit to wear... Ah, um... how do I look?

401239.name: Z23 (Retrofit)
401239.desc: My efficiency should be upgraded along with my performance. Paperwork, battle plans... I can handle them all! Commander, be prepared, we’ll be very busy~

431230.name: Keeper of the Comf-Fort
431230.desc: *sigh*... Taking care of Meowfficers is more work than you'd think... They're awfully needy for support units. Commander, make absolute sure you don't turn out like them.

431232.name: Upgrade Failure?!
431232.desc: N-no way... I lost the gear I worked so hard for because the upgrade failed, and now I'm completely out of gold... Ugh, I'm going to have to go farm the dungeon all over again...

431233.name: Tanz der Blumen
431233.desc: Sure, I've worn black dresses in the past, but this time I decided to incorporate a bit of red and white, per Eugen's suggestion. This is sure to invite the Commander to dance wi– C-Commander?! Did you just get here? I see. Uhh... How do you like my dress?

401251.name: Hot Summer's Cool Breeze
401251.desc: Even at the beach, we cannot afford to be careless! Commander, have you adequately prepared for today's activities?

402039.name: Köln (Retrofit)
402039.desc: Hmm... I feel like I can work even more efficiently than before. Commander, please rest assured, I will never betray your expectations.

402040.name: Leipzig
402040.desc:
Leipzig-class light cruiser, Leipzig.
Can be built after unlocking

402041.name: Storefront Training
402041.desc: Commander, ah, um... We have all new items on the menu, and they're on sale for a limited time only... P-please give them a try! Phew... Th-thank goodness, I managed to not flub it...

402049.name: Leipzig (Retrofit)
402049.desc: I feel like Fishy is a lot more capable than before, but I don't feel much different... M-maybe Fishy was the one to get a retrofit instead of me?!

403010.name: Admiral Hipper
403010.desc: Admiral Hipper-class Heavy Cruiser, Admiral Hipper

403012.name: Sunshine by the Hot Spring
403012.desc: W-well? Does this kimono look good on me? ...R-really? Duh, I know it looks GREAT on me! Who really cares what you think... C-can't be me... No, I didn't say anything!

403021.name: High-Altitude Head Over Heels
403021.desc: Heheheh☆ You're lagging behind, Commander! Pick up the pace or you'll be left behind! Just kidding~ I'll slow down for you so we can stick together!

403022.name: Skyward Burning Love
403022.desc: Heheh☆ I'm Blücher, dragon knight of the Demon King's army! ...Not riding the dragon so much as being dragged along by it? Well, I guess... Whoaaah! The dragon won't obey me! Commander, heeelp!

403030.name: Prinz Eugen
403030.desc: Admiral Hipper-class Heavy Cruiser, Prinz Eugen

403031.name: Unfading Smile
403031.desc: Relaxing on a float, gently licking my lips... is this really the most popular photo pose for the beach? Wales, you’re not teasing me again, are you?

403032.name: Profusion of Flowers
403032.desc: So this is the Sakura Empire's New Year? Hehe, how interesting~ Commander, since it's the New Year, why don't you put aside all those papers and have a drink with me?

403033.name: Cordial Cornflower
403033.desc: ... Huh? Commander, is that you? Me, drunk? No way... *hic*... If I was, Commander, then what are you planning to do to me? Hehe...

403034.name: Final Lap
403034.desc: Viel Glück~ Are you having a good time, Commander? Just know that the only person I'm cheering for... is you~

403035.name: Kindred Evening Spirits
403035.desc: Guten Abend~ So, what do you think? Pretty great view, right? Hehe, I was talking about the night scenery outside, you know~?

403036.name: Brilliant Touchdown
403036.desc: *pant*... Quarterback Prinz Eugen scores a touchdown. I can't believe I'm the one charging in now... Commander, can you bring me water and a towel? I'm getting a little sticky from all this sweat...

403038.name: Symphonic Fate
403038.desc: If fate brought us together, then it has my thanks… I look forward to our future together~

403041.name: Dark Demon Princess
403041.desc: For a servant, your eyes are good... *coughs*... I'm an Ironblood Princess, the Queen of Night, Deutschland! Servant? No. I am the first of my family. Come, kiss the ring of royalty!

403042.name: Service Time?!
403042.desc: One must not neglect sunscreen during the summer... Plebeian, if you wish to serve your master, prostrate yourself and yell "I beg of you, Queen Deutschland" three times, and I might consider giving you an opportunity. Ahahaha~

403043.name: Demon Princess' Dark Hour Banquet
403043.desc: I seem pleased? Of course I am. Why wouldn't I be when my sweet little sister will be joining us at the party? Now shape up and entertain your master, you lowly animal! Ahahahaha!

403044.name: Lantern-Lit Ruler
403044.desc: Why are so many people out and about during a holiday? ...That's it! Lowly animal, was it your idea to prepare all this to surprise me...?! Heh... Hehe, that's right, don't you dare disappoint me!

403050.name: Admiral Graf Spee
403050.desc: Deutschland-class armored cruiser number three – Admiral Graf Spee.

403051.name: Girl's Sunday
403051.desc: I sailed alone, fought alone, and then I was sunk while being alone. Now I found a new beginning... Hmm? Commander, you've been staring and laughing at me since the beginning… do you want to eat this?

403052.name: Peaceful Daily Life
403052.desc: I never dreamt that I'd be able to don this outfit and live a normal, peaceful life... Thank you, Commander...

403053.name: A Novel Anniversary
403053.desc: It's so fancy, so formal... Is this a "party"? I'm not sure I'll be able to fit in... But if you'll go with me, Commander, I'll give it a try!

403054.name: World's♥Cutest
403054.desc: My sister just wouldn't stop bugging me, so I finally caved and agreed to do this... Anyways, all I have to do is get up on stage and sing, right?

404011.name: Panther und Pflaume
404011.desc: A festival, huh? Going for days without fighting is boring, not to mention not my style. C'mon, Commander, isn't there *something* exciting I can do during this "Lunar New Year" festival?

404021.name: Nightmarish Succubus
404021.desc: These Halloween festivities are quite interesting, in a good way. Getting dressed up in these costumes isn't such a bad experience either. Commander, what do you think of my costume?

405011.name: Beacon of the Iron Blood
405011.desc: My sincerest apologies for the delay, Commander. Ah, excuse me... as the fleet leader of the Iron Blood, I'm expected to wear this outfit to various formal occasions. Just putting it on seems to make me inadvertently change the way I speak...

405012.name: Iron-Black Elysium
405012.desc: Welcome, what would you like to order? ...If you want, we can drop this charade. I'm not used to being a waiter anyway, so I prefer it this way. Hehe.

405013.name: Unpacked Surprise
405013.desc: C-Commander? Well, as you see, I was wrapping your Christmas present, but now the surprise has been spoiled. I suppose this moment calls for a "Merry Christmas," hmm?

405018.name: Wedding Dominion
405018.desc: You've arrived, Commander – or rather, my sweetheart in eternal vow. I know I can't wear a stiff expression forever, but when I think about the days to come under your guidance, I feel so needy all of a sudden. Yes, it's like you say... just keep smiling.

405051.name: Crystal-Clear Holiday
405051.desc: Ah, you've already gotten changed, Commander? I'm just... Well, I need to do something about my hair before I go back in the water.

405021.name: Snow-Melting Summer
405021.desc: Summer... In the past, it was always just a hot and stifling season... But now...? Doesn't my outfit tell the whole story? Let's get going, there's bound to be a lot of people on the beach.

405022.name: Iron Blood Snowstorm
405022.desc: I bet Bismarck must've been thinking about how to invite me to the party, but ended up asking you to do it, Commander. Hehe... Let's get going soon. It's best not to keep her waiting.

405023.name: Seasonal Pine and the Frost Flower
405023.desc: They have a peculiar way of wishing a happy New Year in the Sakura Empire. In line with their traditions, I've put on this new outfit. I hope it doesn't... look strange on me. ...You like it? I see... That being the case, I'll keep wearing it for the time

405024.name: A Vase for the Frost Flower
405024.desc: It's all right, I just got here myself. I will say, it's strangely reassuring to know I'm not the only one nervous on this day.

407011.name: Beachside Urd
407011.desc: So the Second Movement is a Lento of the summer and the sea? So be it... Since we will arrive at the Finale eventually, I suppose I can enjoy this moment of fleeting peace with you.

501012.name: Setting Sun, Hearts as One
501012.desc: "Boundless is the beauty of evening's glow, but alas––" ...Oh, that doesn't have any special meaning, I've just been hanging around Hai Tien too much. (*whispers*) But, it's true... Our time together is far too short, just like the evening light...

501019.name: An Shan (Retrofit)
501019.desc: An Shan, retrofitting complete! With this new power, Commander, I'll protect both you and my sisters! But first... Umm, I need to double-check how these missiles work...!

501020.name: Fu Shun
501020.desc: An Shan-class destroyer No.2 - Fu Shun (102)

501021.name: The Unbreakable Baozi Heist
501021.desc: Heh-hey! Just hooked us another baozi~! We're in for one heckuva haul today! ...Eh? Huh, Commander?! Th-this is, uhh... yeah, we're just playing a normal game... totally...

501029.name: Fu Shun (Retrofit)
501029.desc: Fu Shun – retrofitting complete! Reporting in! Commander, if something happens and you need someone reliable, I'm your girl!

501030.name: Chang Chun
501030.desc: An Shan-class destroyer No. 3 - Chang Chun (103)

501031.name: The Joy of Spring
501031.desc: Ta-da! My pajamas are finally finished! Now to snuggle up until I'm all warm! Eh~ Ehhh? But sis, I don't want to get out! Ack, did Tai Yuan purposely make this tail big and thick to make it easier for you?

501032.name: Fortune Arrives in Red
501032.desc: Commander, hurry up and plug your ears! Th-this isn't a joke! Um... Seriously, that big ol' doozy over there is about to blow!

501039.name: Chang Chun (Retrofit)
501039.desc: All done with my retrofit~ Now, time to test out my new toys... Err, I mean, time to test the firepower of my new armaments! Oh, watch your head, Commander! Wouldn't want one of the missiles to lock onto you.

501040.name: Tai Yuan
501040.desc: An Shan-class destroyer No. 4 - Tai Yuan (104)

501041.name: The Golden Dragon's Festivities
501041.desc: O-on behalf of the An Shan class, we wish a prosperous, happy, and healthy new year to Commander, and to everyone here at port... Umm... even though I made this outfit, I feel a bit embarrassed wearing it... Eh? It looks good on me? Um... th-thank you...

501042.name: Two Hearts, One Cushion
501042.desc: Commander? Did Ting An tell you to try out this ergonomic cushion, too? Okay, I'll make room... There, okay! Come lie down with me!

501049.name: Tai Yuan (Retrofit)
501049.desc: Phew... Tai Yuan, retrofit complete. Thanks for supporting me this whole time, Commander. With this new equipment, I'll be able to get one step closer to catching up to my sisters.

502011.name: Paragon of Celestial Grace
502011.desc: I am truly honored to be able to share this wondrous scenery with you on such a festive occasion, Commander. Umm... I'm not just saying that out of courtesy. We rarely get opportunities like this, so I'm somewhat flattered...

502012.name: Pristine Leaves, Rich Warmth
502012.desc: I am honored that you could make time in your busy schedule to accept my invitation... Hmm? There's no need to be so formal? Heehee. Well, the tea happens to be ready now, so please sit down next to me~

502018.name: Coronal Afterglow
502018.desc: Commander, thank you for waiting for me. Though I am unworthy of this honor, thank you so much...

502019.name: Yat Sen (Retrofit)
502019.desc: There's no need to worry, Commander. I will be fine now. Please allow me to serve you once more in this new form.

502020.name: Ning Hai
502020.desc: Ning Hai-class Light Cruiser, Ning Hai

502021.name: Summer Hunger
502021.desc: Summer’s all about the beach! And the beach is all about good food! Commander, let’s find something delicious to eat!

502022.name: Moon Palace Rabbit
502022.desc: Happy Mid-Autumn Festival! I heard that if you pray to the moon today, you’ll become as pretty as the Goddess of the Moon! ...Eh? You’re gonna pray too?

502023.name: Dragon Sisters! -N
502023.desc: We haven't had to worry as much about things like food since we joined the fleet, but that doesn't mean we can just throw money around...! Anyway, I'm the older of the "Dragon Sisters," Ning Hai! Great to be here!

502024.name: Springtime Sojourn
502024.desc: Commander, what are you spacing out for? Over here! They say that you'll have good fortune if you give this thing a shake!

502025.name: Gorgeous Violet
502025.desc: Yat Sen said this look would be best for a party, but, is it really okay? I'm not used to having my hair down like this...

502026.name: Da Bao's Friend!
502026.desc: Good boy. Chew thoroughly before you swallow. I never thought I'd help with a charity event for nature, but Da Bao's made a lot of new friends because of it. Keep up the good work, Commander and Ping!

502027.name: Hectic Kitchen
502027.desc: Woah! Da Bao, lend me a hand here! Don't let that octopus get away! ...Oh, Commander, Happy Lunar New Year! Uhh, the kitchen prep's going fine... Huh? You're gonna help? Heheh~ don't worry about us! Just leave everything here to me 'n Ping!

502029.name: Ning Hai (Retrofit)
502029.desc: Yes! … this feels good. Thank you, Commander. In order to live up to your expectations, from now on, I will be more serious around you, Commander. Hey, don't run!

502030.name: Ping Hai
502030.desc: Ning Hai-class Light Cruser, Ping Hai

502031.name: Summer Vacation
502031.desc: Compared to pork buns, shaved ice is tastier. Compared to shaved ice, fireworks are prettier. Compared to fireworks, what I care for the most is...

502032.name: Osmanthus Moon Rabbit
502032.desc: Happy Mid-Autumn Festival, Commander! Mooncakes, pomegranates, and osmanthus cakes... what a wonderful holiday!

502033.name: Dragon Sisters! -P
502033.desc: Big sister says that even though we have some money now, we still have to save as much as we can. Um... Anyway, I'm the younger "Dragon Sister," Ping Hai. Erm... I'm kind of hungry. Do you maybe have something to eat?

502034.name: Great Gourmet Expedition
502034.desc: The Sakura Empire has lots of delicious food that I've never tried before! Yeah! It's a great place!

502035.name: Delicious Crimson
502035.desc: There's always a lot of delicious food at these parties! But, my sister said I'm not allowed to have any cake until everyone's gotten their slice... Baobao, let's be on our best behavior!

502036.name: Baobao's Buddy!
502036.desc: Cheese! That came out looking good! Hehehe~ I'm really glad to be a part of this charity event for nature, along with you and my sister! Baobao is really glad too!

502037.name: Lively Banquet Preparations
502037.desc: You can't have a hearty banquet without crab meat! Which is why... I'm not letting you get away! Oh, Commander, did you want to lend a hand? It's okay though, my sister and I have got things under wrap here.

502039.name: Ping Hai (Retrofit)
502039.desc: Hi~ya! Hmm... this feels... nothing special. Baobao looks happy though... Never mind, Commander, Ping Hai is hungry!

702011.name: Shackled Saule
702011.desc: "I am Avrora, the princess bound within this tower by a cruel fate... My beloved, please come for me soon..."

702012.name: Not Cut Out For This?
702012.desc: "Muahaha... Now, these streets belong to me..." Sorry, I bit my tongue... Hmm, getting into this role is quite difficult for me after all.

101270.name: Bailey
101270.desc: Benson-class Destroyer - Bailey, Hull Number DD-492!

101271.name: Trickster Black Rabbit
101271.desc: Can you see the ghost next to me? Hehehe— the black witch from Planet Bunny is none other than me, Bailey!

101272.name: Jolly Saint Bunnylass!
101272.desc: Your Bunny Santa has arrived! That's right – not regular ol' Santa, but Bunny Santa! The real Santa's busy, so Bailey from Planet Bunny is here to help out!

101279.name: Bailey (Retrofit)
101279.desc: The day has finally arrived~! Bunnies, are you ready? Bailey's debut show is about to begin! Commander, sisters, come and see my bunny magic!

401461.name: Her First Summer
401461.desc: The bustling beach, clamoring with waves of joyfulness... experiencing this kind of summer is a first for me, but I don't dislike it...

401462.name: Girls' Relay
401462.desc: Through the sweat and tears, striving for your goals. Rejoice in victory, sink within defeat... How fascinating, this "sports meet" may be.

401463.name: Star-Lit★Chocolate
401463.desc: Dancing beams of light, shimmering on-stage; uplifted voices, joined as one by song... Upon this unknown stage, my heart doth flutter... Yet this sensation, is quite refreshing.

401464.name: Jianzhi Fantasia
401464.desc: "Jianzhi," the art of breathing life into works of cut paper... is a world beyond my imagination. If these decorations are said to usher in blessings... are they akin to a coat-of-arms or a holy seal?

401465.name: Chronicles of the Dust Wars
401465.desc: Cast your eyes upon this bit of dust. As I was entrusted with the cleaning, I shall not allow this dust to remain. Will you also join me in this battle?

401466.name: The Bard of Hamelin
401466.desc: Hm? You are following us because you're drawn to the sound of my flute? Ah... Then in exchange for accompanying you on this journey, tell me your story.

301291.name: World's Speediest Bunny Waitress
301291.desc: Hippity hoppity! Grab a glass and have a sippity! Whew, I must say, this outfit was tricky to get into. Still, you made an exquisite pick, Commander!

301292.name: The White Rabbit of Wonderland
301292.desc: Whoa-whoa-whoa! Why'd I end up here again?! Even though I've been running for a whole hour! ...Commander?! Waaaah, I'm so glad to see you! Please, help me get out of heeeeeeere!

301293.name: The Island Wind Rests
301293.desc: You can't keep sprinting across the sea forever. Sometimes, you need to rest and recover your strength. Speaking of, you may use my parasol if you like, Commander!

301294.name: Clumsy Moon Rabbit
301294.desc: Oh no! Commander, look out! ...Phew. That was really close. Apologies for my clear lack of attentiveness! I shouldn't have been in such a rush to deliver all these mooncakes...

301309.name: Kamikaze (Retrofit)
301309.desc: Ohohoho, you must have a sharp eye if you've decided to retrofit me~ Now that I've been chosen, I cannot afford to embarrass you. Now, take a good and thorough look at this veteran's aspirations~

301319.name: Matsukaze (Retrofit)
301319.desc: There we go... My fan is too big, and I'm not used to carrying it around yet... Ah, right, come here for a sec, Commander~ I'll fan you with some cool air~ Come on now, no need to be shy~

301321.name: Mr. Reindeer, Depart!
301321.desc: Commander, Merry Christmas~! I am on my best behavior today as well! Uuu... when is Santa Claus going to come? I'm sleepy...

301322.name: Candy Festival!
301322.desc: Comainder, I put on my yukata just like you said! Ehehe, you should take me to the festival so I can get lots and lots of candy!

301323.name: Spring Festival Sweets
301323.desc: I heard that if I go around telling people "Happy New Year," I can get lots of goodies! Ehehe, I hope they'll give me a bunch of candy!

301324.name: Cotton Candy Dreams
301324.desc: Comainder, you gotta keep up! We still have to eat cake and hot dogs, ride the teacups, go to the haunted house, and... what else was there? Hehe, anyway, let's hold hands and get going!♪

301329.name: Mutsuki (Retrofit)
301329.desc: Comainder, I'm done retrofitting! Have some candy! Hm? You're always nice to me, so I'm giving you some candy!

301331.name: New Year's Wish
301331.desc: Co... commander, Kisaragi's new outfit... How does it look? It's a new year... Kisaragi wants to keep improving...

301339.name: Kisaragi (Retrofit)
301339.desc: Kisaragi... retrofitting complete... I want to be able to help everyone out more...

301350.name: Uzuki
301350.desc: The fourth ship of Mutsuki class destroyer — Uzuki

301351.name: Sleepy Uzuki
301351.desc: Ah... Big sis Kisaragi, big sis Mutsuki, let's sleep together... Commander? You want to come too?

301381.name: Sleepy Fairy
301381.desc: Huh...? Where am I...? What time is it...?

301391.name: Dangerous Kitty Maid?
301391.desc: Nagatsuki the kitty maid is at your service~ Do your best to not fall madly in love with my cute looks~! Hehe~

301411.name: Sweet Zombie
301411.desc: Mikazuki is supposed to be... a jiangshi? Um... hip... hop... Commander, trick or treaaaaat~

301471.name: Soft and Fluffy Therapy
301471.desc: What's the matter, Commander? Oh, this outfit? ...Um, I heard that this outfit would bring you therapeutic benefits and hoped to try it on... Wh-what do you think? Does it feel therapeutic to you?

301472.name: Baby Steps
301472.desc: Commander, it is my pleasure to accompany you today. Umm... What do you think? I decided to go for a different outfit this time... D-do you think it's cute?

301481.name: Now for a Magic Trick!
301481.desc: Voilà! Don't go anywhere, Commander! My magic show will start in just a sec! To start with, let's hear a roar! Roooaar!

301491.name: Monochromatic Interlude
301491.desc: Mhm. Lightweight clothing makes it easier to fight. Thanks, Commander... "It looks cute on me"? W-well, thanks...

301498.name: Unsullied White Fox
301498.desc: This must be the dream you've awaited so eagerly... Of course, I vowed to be with you until the end of our days. I shall take my rightful place beside you and your ideals. We are... together.

301541.name: Festive Riding Hood?
301541.desc: S-sorry to keep you waiting... Yuugure and I picked out this outfit together. She said it "looked very Christmassy," but it doesn't look weird, right? ... Ugh...

301571.name: A Dance for the Coming Spring
301571.desc: Happy New Year, Commander! I am currently on my way to give a Kagura dance at the shrine. If you have time... would you like to come see it?

301581.name: Sports Festival Preparations
301581.desc: It's my turn? Hold on... Umm, could you please not stare at me like that? It's... making me feel uncomfortable.

301582.name: Firecrackers and Steamed Buns
301582.desc: Mmh... Happy New Year. I'm working on hooking my friends up with these firecrackers... The bun I'm eating? I received it as a thank-you for my efforts.

101290.name: Radford
101290.desc: Fletcher-class Destroyer - Radford, Hull Number DD-446!

101291.name: Sweet Magic!
101291.desc: Commander, the sweet magic within my tome lets me turn things into candy! Hehe, that sounds pretty convincing— ...Eh, Commander? Wh-when'd you get here?!

101300.name: Jenkins
101300.desc: Fletcher-class destroyer - Jenkins, Hull Number DD-447!

101301.name: Light of the Holiest Star
101301.desc: Commander, g-good evening...? Right now, I'm bringing presents to Radford and the others...? Could you give me a hand? Th-thank you... Um, your present.. this apple, do you want it?

101310.name: Nicholas
101310.desc: Fletcher-class destroyer – Nicholas, Hull Number DD-449!

101311.name: Nurse Nicholas
101311.desc: I love doing relief missions as a nurse... I don't need to go outside or take part in any training, I just need to look after injured people... What about treating them? No worries, they just need to rest and they'll get better.

101312.name: Surprise!?
101312.desc: Merry Christmas, Commander. I'm your present, probably... Would you mind closing the lid for me so I can sleep a bit more... zzz...

101313.name: Summer Cleaning "Volunteer"
101313.desc: Commander, did you also come to play in the pool? ...Me? Fletcher said I have to help clean up because I was slacking off... Mm, watch your step~

101314.name: After-School Promise
101314.desc: Commander, because you kept your promise and came... here's some chocolate, and a letter for you. Please read it later. No, it's not that big of a deal... Just a little embarrassing...

101319.name: Nicholas (Retrofit)
101319.desc: Commander, what month is it...? I think I overslept a bit... am I taller than I was before? *Yawn*... Gotta be because I slept the whole time...

102120.name: Honolulu
102120.desc: Brooklyn-class Light Cruiser – Honolulu, Hull Number CL-48!

102121.name: Umbrella Girl
102121.desc: If everyone's focusing on the teacher, they probably won't stare at me from up front... As for the umbrella, it's... I know it makes me stand out, but I don't want people to stare at me from behind either...

102122.name: Summer Accident?!
102122.desc: Aaaahh! My sundae! What's up with this stupid hose?! Commander, don't just stand there, help me!

102123.name: Manjuu Mischief
102123.desc: Just where did St. Louis find something like this... such shameless undergarments, if someone found out... Awawawaa! Commander, what are you doing in here? Get out right now!

102124.name: Among the Stalls
102124.desc: Come on, Louis, the goldfish stall is this way! ... W-why are you giving me that weird look like th– Wait... Eeeek! C-Commander?! When did you get here?!

102130.name: St. Louis
102130.desc: Brooklyn-class Light Cruiser – St. Louis, Hull Number CL-49!

102131.name: Blue and White Pottery
102131.desc: What do you think of this foreign dress, Commander? *Giggle* ...Perhaps it's rekindled something within you?

102132.name: Spirits in the Snow
102132.desc: The Sakura Empire's clothes are just so refined. Ahaha... Aren't you cold standing out there, Commander? Sit down with me and have a drink.

102133.name: Luxurious Wheels
102133.desc: Oh my, what a good little commander you've been, waiting here all this time for me. Hop in~ Did you think you would be driving? Hehe, you shouldn't underestimate me~

102134.name: An Afternoon on the Lido Deck
102134.desc: Commander, I've been waiting for you. Lazing about and enjoying the sights here does sound nice, but... Heheh, it just isn't the same without you by my side♪

201240.name: Jupiter
201240.desc: J-class destroyer – Jupiter, Hull Number F85.

201241.name: Fanclub Sleepover
201241.desc: Good evening, Commander. There's a new show on the telly. You want to watch with me?

201250.name: Jersey
201250.desc: J-class destroyer – Jersey, Hull Number F72!

302120.name: Sendai
302120.desc: Sendai-class light cruiser number one – Sendai.

302129.name: Sendai (Retrofit)
302129.desc: Hmh. Guess I won't be needin' these bandages anymore. Commander, how about we find out how strong I've gotten... by having you take one of my punches?

302131.name: The Tactician's Vacation
302131.desc: Hmm? Is it unusual? Hah. Even I require a change of pace to clear my mind every so often. Commander, why don’t you come out and get some fresh air as well?

302132.name: The Gray Wolf's Ploy
302132.desc: "Where do you think you're going so early in the morning, Little Red Riding Hood?" ...Oh, if it isn't the Commander. This might be my own little whim, but I often find myself thinking the same way as this character... If you don't mind, I'd like to hear your feedback about my acting.

302139.name: Jintsuu (Retrofit)
302139.desc: Since I've gotten used to living with you, Commander, I've decided to be more laid-back after receiving my remodel. My dance? Hehe... I can't show that to just anyone so easily.

302140.name: Naka
302140.desc: Sendai-class light cruiser number three – Naka.

302141.name: Foxy Summer Surfer
302141.desc: Ahaha! Another big one's coming~! Phew~ that felt amazing~! Ah, Commander, let's hit the waves together, shall we?

301590.name: Urakaze
301590.desc: The 11th Destroyer of Kagerou class — Urakaze

301591.name: Seasonal Shogun
301591.desc: Before you raise a fuss about it, let me just tell you this - the concept of "Christmas" already existed during the Sengoku period, so there's nothing weird about putting on a Christmas outfit!

301592.name: Sengoku☆Shredder!
301592.desc: Ugh... Even though we finally got all our gear, we still need more band members... Commander! Stop complaining and come hither! From now on, you're a member of the Sengoku Shredders!

301601.name: New Year's Campaign
301601.desc: General, General, look! It's my New Year's outfit! Urakaze made it for me! Let's play a bunch of Sengoku wargames this year as well!

301602.name: Sengoku☆Smasher!
301602.desc: General! I, Isokaze, have done my utmost to prepare the equipment! Now, with Lord Urakaze's presence, our Sengoku☆War-Band is complete! Of course, you are more than welcome to join our ranks, General!

301610.name: Hamakaze
301610.desc: Tenth ship of Kagerou class destroyers, Hamakaze.

301611.name: The Honors Student
301611.desc: Learning is exciting. The joy of acquiring new knowledge, the sense of achievement from solving difficult problems... you'll understand once you try it. So, shall we study together, Commander?

301612.name: The Secret Ingredient is Love?!
301612.desc: I'm experimenting with different flavors since we're running a pop-up café... Alright! I think I'll go with this one! Strap in, Commander, because you're about to do a lot of taste-testing!

301619.name: Hamakaze (Retrofit)
301619.desc: Commander, have you been having more fun since I arrived? ... I see, that's great! Ehehe... Hamakaze, getting hyped!

301621.name: Lost Girl and Labyrinth Butterfly
301621.desc: Little butterfly, little butterfly... Ya! It flew away... Hamakaze~ Hamakaze~ Where are you? Urakaze? Isokaze? We said we were going to play at the seaside. Where is everyone?

301622.name: Sparkly-Clean
301622.desc: Commander, I'm mopping the floor right now. Please watch your step, as it's quite slippery over there... Eek! Owch... I suppose I should've watched my own step... Ahaha...

301629.name: Tanikaze (Retrofit)
301629.desc: I'm Tanikaze, blowing and blustering from the mountaintop! Whoa! Butterflies? Butterflies?! Look, butterflies! For me? Thanks, Commander!

305111.name: Style of the Sakura Capital
305111.desc: I found quite the nostalgic outfit when I was cleaning my wardrobe. Let's see... "Prepare to come with me on a new journey!" How do I look, Commander?

305112.name: Blossom-Viewing Season
305112.desc: It's about time for the flowers to bloom once more. Alas, how the time flies by... Ahem, Commander, let's see, would you like to go blossom-viewing with me?

305113.name: Reverence for Rest and Relaxation
305113.desc: Even I like to dress down and unwind from time to time. Oh? This is new and exciting for you? Well, you are welcome to come see more of it from now on! Hahaha!

305114.name: A Romantic Respite
305114.desc: Welcome to the Sakura Empire's pop-up café... Oh, Commander! Everyone's waiting for you. Now get your butt in here and experience the full extent of our fleet's hospitality! Don't be nervous, now! Hahaha!

305115.name: Beauty in Indigo
305115.desc: I was worried when you said you wanted to go on a trip with me, but... I do like getting to go sight-seeing and try on new threads. Commander, let's enjoy this to the fullest! Hahaha!

305118.name: Untarnished Splendor
305118.desc: I, battleship Mikasa, from now until eternity, pledge to you my undying love and devotion. May we help each other, encourage each other, and walk side-by-side on the same path. I hope to meet your expectations, as unworthy as I may be.

302200.name: Agano
302200.desc: Agano-class light cruiser number one – Agano.

302201.name: Christmas Eve Tease
302201.desc: Even though I'm not really into this whole "Christmas" thing, if it means I get to toy around with your heart by wearing this cute outfit of mine, then I suppose I would be interested. Hehe~

302202.name: Dating Game?
302202.desc: "Oh my, you're also out for a stroll? Hehe, my name's Agano. And what might yours be?" ...Jeez, Commander, take this more seriously. According to the setting, we just met for the first time.

302203.name: Blue Butterfly's Confession
302203.desc: The blunt approach is not my style, but I cannot have Noshiro think I only inch my way to success... Oh, I was just talking to myself, Commander. Hehe, so anyway, would you mind being my partner for tonight's party?

302210.name: Noshiro
302210.desc: Agano-class light cruiser number two – Noshiro.

302211.name: Uncharted Festival Grounds?
302211.desc: Just as I thought, this is the perfect place for watching fireworks. You came here thinking that too, didn't you?

302212.name: Xanadu's Eventide
302212.desc: Commander, what are you standing around for? Did you also need a change of pace? That makes two of us— Come, there's nothing to be afraid of here.

302213.name: Fragrance of the Eastern Snow
302213.desc: Whew... Oh, are you cold by any chance? I have some hot tea for you if you'd like. If you want someone to chat with, I'd be glad to keep you company.

302214.name: Cozy Enclave
302214.desc: Why don't you unwind for a bit before you start reflecting on the day's happenings? I'm sure it'll be far more efficient that way.

302215.name: Hold the Ice
302215.desc: Welcom...?! What are you doing here? Wait, don't leave—I was just surprised, that's all... Well, what would you like to order?

302216.name: Unwinding in the Sunshine
302216.desc: ...Take that! Heehee... Ahaha! Phew... I know you don't like admitting defeat, but I got you pretty good there. I might have tried a bit too hard, but I'm pretty sure you were the one who told me to give it my all.

302217.name: Dressed-Up Date
302217.desc: Commander, what do you have planned next...? You want to just relax and enjoy the date? Understood. Umm, let me just try and get a feel for it... Hmm...

302218.name: A Tale of Two Lovers
302218.desc: Receiving everyone's blessings is truly a deeply moving experience. But for now, let's set everything else aside and partake of our sweet bliss. After all, you're not just a spectator anymore– we're in this ride together, hehe~

302230.name: Sakawa
302230.desc: Agano-class light cruiser number four – Sakawa.

302231.name: The Colors of Love
302231.desc: Welcome! Heehee, you came because you were just so keen to see me, am I right? Then I've got to make you feel real welcome♪

302232.name: Icy Indulgence
302232.desc: Wow, look how far you pursued me. You must have really, reeeally wanted to see me, huh, Commander~? Heheh, want a popsicle?

302233.name: The Keys of Love
302233.desc: Laaa la-laaa♪ Oh, Commander. Here to see me again? I know you're madly in love and want to watch me practice, but people will think you're weird if you keep coming and going constantly. Heehee♪

201261.name: Escort Me Please!
201261.desc: Ah, Commander, over here! Hm, you're going to take care of all the plans for today's date? In that case, I look forward to seeing just how suave you can be! Hehe~

202161.name: Trendy and Vogue?
202161.desc: Did I keep you waiting, Commander? Ahaha... A girl's gotta take her time before stepping out onto the streets, remember? Come on, take my hand, and let's get going! Hehe~

202171.name: Dark Bolt
202171.desc: Hey Boss, you talkin' about my sweet bike? Heh, I made it myself by scrounging up parts from Akashi's place. Pretty cool, huh?

202172.name: Highway Star
202172.desc: Look, Boss, this is the new bike that Akashi sent me. She said she wanted me to be her brand ambassador... Doesn't that job sound badass?

102140.name: Montpelier
102140.desc: Cleveland-class light cruiser – Montpelier, hull number CL-57.

102141.name: Flower of the Snowy Night
102141.desc: So this is Sakura-style New Year's attire... If Cleve was also interested in this... Hm? Commander, were you watching? Um, well, Happy New Year's.

102142.name: Persephone's Throne
102142.desc: As unreliable as you are, I didn't think you'd be too scared to approach a movie prop... You're just "admiring it from a distance?" ...Fair enough.

301631.name: The Transfer Student Underneath the Dancing Petals
301631.desc: My name is Asashio, and I just transferred here today. Pleased to meet you... Even though I might not be able to get caught up with the course work, Mr. Kitty and I will do our best.

301632.name: Snow-Dusted Lynx Tips
301632.desc: Happy New Year, Commander. I am here to spend the New Year with you. Would you be so kind as to first help me down from here?

301633.name: Robes of Dancing Clouds
301633.desc: Commander, thank you for coming to see me. I'm currently rehearsing my program for the Spring Festival performance. I do hope it is to your liking.

301641.name: The Reindeer's Present
301641.desc: Merry Christmas~ Commander, we gotta go hand out presents to them destroyers~ You be Santa, I'll be yer reindeer~

301642.name: Woozy Party
301642.desc: Happy anniversary~ Today's a day to enjoy to yer heart's content, ya know? I'm just havin' fun in my own way, checkin' out cute girls from afar~ I appreciate yer concern though, Commander~

301643.name: Bringer of Fortunes
301643.desc: Should I hang this "fortune" poster here...? Oh, Commander, did ya also want a Spring Festival present from Ooshio here? Just kiddin'~ Hehe, anyway, happy Lunar New Year~

301644.name: Let's 'ave Lunch
301644.desc: Finally we're through with them mornin' classes~ Commander, would ya fancy havin' lunch with me? Heheh, yer wonderin' what I done made? You'll see for yerself soon 'nuff~

301650.name: Michishio
301650.desc: Third ship of Asashio class destroyers, Michishio.

301651.name: Fluttering Fanfare
301651.desc: Hello, Commander. Oh, you think I look good in this fluttery dress~? Thank you very much!

301661.name: The Gentlest Firework
301661.desc: Looks like you found me, Commander. Hehe, want to light some fireworks with me? Spending time together should be more fun than being alone, right?

213040.name: Abercrombie
213040.desc: Roberts-class monitor - Abercrombie. Hull Number F109.

213041.name: Pumpkin Blast!
213041.desc: Kabooom! You thought it was a pumpkin, but it was me, Abercrombie, with my Mark I! Commander, did I scare you senseless? Muahaha!

213042.name: Mischief on the Rocks
213042.desc: Now for a ghost pepper while nobody's looking... Tee hee! Perfect! I wonder who'll be the lucky one to sip– C-Commander?! You didn't see anything suspicious... Right? Tee hee~

213043.name: Hot on Your Trail
213043.desc: Found you! No criminals are escaping on my watch! You have the right to remain silent! Everything you say can and will be used against you in a court of law! Tee hee, now surrender peacefully, Commander!

203090.name: Sussex
203090.desc: London-class heavy cruiser, Sussex. Hull Number 96.

203091.name: Sunlit Tulips
203091.desc: What are you spacing out for? Have you not gotten tired of staring at all the swimsuits yet? Good grief... Are you able to help set up the parasol or the beach chairs at least?

203092.name: Wine and Red Roses
203092.desc: What are you staring at me for? I'm just the same as any of the others... Y-you have a few more hands to shake? Of course...

308011.name: Departure's Gentle Breeze
308011.desc: Aww, do I have to go to school? ... Oh, Commander! Are you here to see me off?

308012.name: Pillowy Paradise
308012.desc: So sleepy... Hey, Commandeeer? Do you wanna nap with me and my torpedo?

308013.name: Blossoming Bunny
308013.desc: I thought I'd try on this bunny costume! Hehehe, do you like it? If you think it's cute, I wanna hear you say it~

308021.name: Deep-Sea Rabbit
308021.desc: Many secrets lie at the bottom of the ocean! Commander, let's go looking for them next time! It'll be like a field trip~ Heheh!

308022.name: Shortly Before the Fireworks
308022.desc: Commander, are you also waiting for the fireworks to start? There's still some time, so let's have a little chat!

408010.name: U-81
408010.desc: Iron Blood Type VIIC submarine – U-81.

408011.name: Soft Serenade
408011.desc: *Ugh*... I figured this bulky dress would be hard to move in... Huh? I look pretty? Aha, ahaha... You're makin' me blush...

408012.name: Lantern-Lit Full Moon
408012.desc: Over here, Commander! I came because you said we were going to go moon-viewing together! I even brought tea and mooncakes.

408020.name: U-47
408020.desc: Iron Blood Type VIIB submarine – U-47.

408021.name: Rookie Rider
408021.desc: I haven't seen much of the world on land... Commander, want to explore it with me?

408022.name: Eigenen Raum
408022.desc: Sigh... I'd much rather be in a nice, quiet place like this over the din and clamor of the venue... Wouldn't you agree, Commander? I see. Well, come sit here then.

408023.name: Urban Maid
408023.desc: Coming through! Steer clear! Oh, it's you, Commander. Talk to you later – I've got coffee to deliver.

408024.name: Sanguine Moon Sojourn
408024.desc: An empty study with a cushy couch. The perfect place to relax. Whew... Go ahead and read a book if you want, Commander. If that'll be all then I'm gonna take a nap.

408025.name: Hook, Line, and Sinker
408025.desc: Nice. I've found a legendary luck-bringing carp, like... Oh. I almost had it, too... Sorry, Commander.

408030.name: U-557
408030.desc: Iron Blood Type VIIC submarine – U-557.

401351.name: Projekt Kirschblüte
401351.desc: Commander, and all my fellow friends of the fleet, Happy New Year's! This time, your favorite idol Z35 will be presenting a brand new Sakura-themed collaboration, "Projekt Kirschblüte!" Everyone, thank you for your continued support!

401352.name: Liebender Engel
401352.desc: "Welcome, my beloved Master♡ Heehee, I've been waiting here for you for sooo long!" Heheh, did you get good pics this time? My beloved Master♪

401353.name: Himmel: Beyond Love's Boundaries
401353.desc: In pursuit of being an even greater idol, I prepared this new outfit! "With my magic and passionate heart, I'll bring you joy☆" Heheh, did you like that one, Commander?

801021.name: Fleur Blanche
801021.desc: It's good to be able to stop and smell the roses every now and then. Um, Commander, would you be able to accompany me a bit longer?

801022.name: École de Chevalier
801022.desc: Even though I'm an Iris Libre squire, I'm currently working hard to have a rich student life. Um... maybe this is a bit too laid back?

801023.name: Feast of Champagne
801023.desc: Good evening, Commander. I am currently enjoying the party in the company of my friends, as my duties as a squire entail. Um... I've had a bit too much to drink? R-really...?

801028.name: Fleur de Mariée
801028.desc: At long last, this wonderful day is here. It feels like I'm dreaming... I'm so happy, I just... Forgive me, I promised myself I wouldn't cry... I, Forbin the squire, shall remain by your side for the rest of my life!

801029.name: Forbin (Retrofit)
801029.desc: My hard work has finally paid off! Commander, thank you for your guidance all this time! I'll return the favor by bringing you even more honors in battle!

802011.name: Côte d'Azur
802011.desc: Commander, does my swimsuit pique your fancy? I'm actually quite proud of my fashion sense. *Giggle* Now, let's enjoy midsummer together~

802012.name: Maid Fantastique
802012.desc: I heard of this romantic concept of maid outfits, and thought I'd try one on to see how it feels~ What are your thoughts, Commander?

802013.name: Gilded Dance
802013.desc: Modest though it may be, isn't this a lovely little garden? Come, Commander! Let us dance surrounded by Mother Nature~

802019.name: Émile Bertin (Retrofit)
802019.desc: Émile Bertin, retrofit complete! I feel like a completely new person! To show my gratitude, Commander, I'll perform a brand new dance for you!

808011.name: Shopping Time!
