808011.desc: Hmm? Commander, are you shopping as well? If so, why don't you come along and take a look around? ... Huh? Of course you can't climb on. That'd be illegal.

808012.name: Loisirs Balnéaires
808012.desc: Mmmh~ Bonjour, Commander~ Nothing feels better than the waves lapping at your skin~ Oh, Commander, why don't you come lie down and experience it for yourself?

901011.name: Été Brillant
901011.desc: It's summer~! Summer is here, Commander! Let's head down to the beach to play! I'll show you why I'm feared in water gun fights!

901012.name: Écolière Heureuse
901012.desc: Hey! Over here! Hehe. I didn't expect to run into you at school, Commander. What are you doing here?

901013.name: Splendorous Debut
901013.desc: Commander, thanks for coming to pick me up! I don't often get the chance to wear formal clothes, though it is a little hard to move around... Oh, but I can deal with it!

901019.name: Le Mars (Retrofit)
901019.desc: Retro~ fit~ com~ plete! The new and improved Le Mars is at your service~!

904011.name: Summer Sucré
904011.desc: I've been waiting so long for summer... and it's so worth it - the sun, the sand, the waves, and everyone's laughter. Commander, why don't we take this opportunity to enjoy some crullers together?

904012.name: Afternoon Venus
904012.desc: Don't you simply adore the atmosphere in this place? It's one of my favorites. The desserts here are to die for. Would you like a taste?

905011.name: Uninhibited Bloodstone
905011.desc: The guest of honor shouldn't be wandering around looking for girls drinking alone... Hmph, might as well have a drink while you're here anyway.

905012.name: Private Après Midi
905012.desc: You damn scalawag... You don't just sneak into someone's hideaway without consequences, ya know. Though, I found this place by pure chance too. Don't go tellin' anyone else about it!

905013.name: First Snow Upon the Cutlass's Edge
905013.desc: Bonne année... Or rather, I should say "Happy New Year" here, yes? A year of peace and prosperity passes, and we are here to welcome another... and I must thank you for making that possible.

905014.name: Springlight Étoiles
905014.desc: What're you starin' daggers through me for? Are ya that excited about this new outfit? Alright, then feast your eyes on my fashion sense. Yeah, I didn't put it together just for your sake this time – more like to demonstrate my tastes.

105190.name: Massachusetts
105190.desc: South Dakota-class battleship – Massachusetts, Hull Number BB-59.

105191.name: Dressed to Impress
105191.desc: Hey... Is this outfit that strange to you? Thought it looks just like what my sister's wearing... so what are you staring at? I don't get you at all...

101330.name: Bush
101330.desc: Fletcher-class destroyer – Bush, Hull Number DD-529.

101331.name: Budding Painter
101331.desc: Tadaaah! All done! How does it look? I think I'm pretty talented as an artist!

206041.name: Beachside Undine
206041.desc: Even though I see the ocean every day, changing into this swimsuit gives me a totally new outlook on it. How about you, Commander? Don't you feel at ease?

206042.name: Sprightly Spring Wind
206042.desc: I never imagined you would give me such a splendid dress, Commander... I think it's called a "qipao..." is it? I'll try it, revealing though it is. Wh- what do you think...? Do I look... nice?

107090.name: Essex
107090.desc: Essex-class aircraft carrier – Essex, Hull Number CV-9.

107091.name: A Trip Down Route 66
107091.desc: I'm not trying to go anywhere in particular; I just want to enjoy the scenery along the way. Commander, let's go experience the thrills of the road together.

107092.name: Craft Fairytail
107092.desc: Commander?! Ah, um, no, I'm not drunk! ...I, uh, just had a bit too much to drink... just a bit! Please don't tell the others though!

107093.name: Brush and Ink
107093.desc: The Dragon Empery's attire and tools of calligraphy... I see, just wearing this outfit makes me feel more scholarly and artistic! I shall put forth my best effort to prepare for the port's Spring Festival!

107094.name: Detective Essex
107094.desc: My eagle has gone missing... Just as Enterprise said, there's something strange going on in this port–– Wait, I definitely smell a case in the making! Commander, let's get to the bottom of this together!

107095.name: Crossbones Especial
107095.desc: "Anchors aweigh! Arr, pirate aircraft carrier Essex be ready for battle! Nothing in the seven seas will escape my grasp!" Hic... Hehehe... I wanna be a piraaate...

107096.name: The Gale of Course 88
107096.desc: Cooldown lap completed! Did you see me on the racetrack, Commander? Heehee. Thanks for everything, from setting up the race to assigning racers and supporters!

108020.name: Albacore
108020.desc: Gato-class submarine – Albacore, Hull Number SS-218.

108021.name: Beneath the Black Dress
108021.desc: Oopsie! I totally just dropped something by mistake~! I'd better pick it up quick! Hmm? Saw something you shouldn't have, Commander? Hehehe~ That makes you my partner in crime now!

108022.name: A Catty Surprise!
108022.desc: Surpriiiise! I was in the box all along! ...Did I really freak you out that much? Heehee~ Here, have this voucher as an apology. Come see me later to use it~♪

801031.name: Summery Temeraire!
801031.desc: Commander, I've finished changing into my swimsuit! Heheh~ let's head down to the beach and enjoy ourselves as much as we can!

801032.name: Dreamy Dolce
801032.desc: How do I look? These pajamas are super cute, aren't they? Ehehe, I really like this one! It even matches with Opiniâtre's!

801033.name: Cheering Star
801033.desc: Let's go, let's go! Allons-y! Whew... Heehee, you here to watch me rehearse, Commander? Okay, and how was my performance just now? Did that manage to motivate you?

102160.name: Memphis
102160.desc: Omaha-class light cruiser – Memphis, Hull Number CL-13.

102161.name: Casual Vacation
102161.desc: Oh my, do I really look so unusual in this outfit? I want to be able to enjoy my day off as well, you know? Hehe, don't you think it feels nice to just sit back and take in the ocean breeze?

102162.name: Mystical Night
102162.desc: We have to work hard if we want to play hard, isn't that right, Commander? Are you ready for our happy Halloween?

102163.name: A Breath of Fresh Air
102163.desc: Oh, what a wonderful breeze. Maybe the windows ought always to be open during class... Commander? What are you standing around for? There's a vacant seat right here for you.

202191.name: Hibiscus Garments
202191.desc: This outfit makes me stand out a bit too much... But, as long as it makes you happy, I'm just as pleased.

202199.name: Newcastle (Retrofit)
202199.desc: I've got an all new outfit here. Does it please you...? Hehe, seeing you all giddy like that is going to rub off on me as well.

101360.name: Hobby
101360.desc: Benson class Destroyer— Hobby, hull number DD-610.

101361.name: Little Idol Schoolgirl
101361.desc: Here comes the debut of school uniform Hobby~ Commander, how do I look? Hobby is all grown up~

101370.name: Kalk
101370.desc: Benson class Destroyer— Kalk, hull number DD-611.

101371.name: Snow Fairy Schoolgirl
101371.desc: Kalk, reporting in once again, now with a new outfit! Hehe... Commander, will you walk me to school?

103130.name: Minneapolis
103130.desc: New Orleans class Heavy Cruiser— Minneapolis, hull number CA-36.

103131.name: Wild Huntress Schoolgirl
103131.desc: Textbooks, pencils and erasers... hey, must students always pay attention in class... Commander? Can you arrange for us to get more extracurricular activities?

103132.name: eXtreme Games
103132.desc: Oh crap! Move outta the way, Commander! Come on, man, look out next time! You'd have gotten hurt if I'd slammed into you!

103133.name: Holy Night Ride
103133.desc: Merry Christmas, Commander! Right now, I'm Santa Claus! And this guy over here is my partner in delivering presents! Right, this is a present for you. C'mon, go ahead and take it!

103138.name: Trapper White
103138.desc: Commander, why's that Quincy so happy to see me in this outfit? It's hard to move around in, and there's all this stuff flapping around that makes it hard to hunt. What do you think of this outfit?

101340.name: Hazelwood
101340.desc: Fletcher-class destroyer – Hazelwood, Hull Number DD-531.

102180.name: Concord
102180.desc: Omaha-class light cruiser— Concord, hull number CL-10.

102181.name: Red Apple Candy
102181.desc: Apple candy, Taiyaki, and fried noodles~ The Sakura Empire’s Temple Fair really is something~ Hehe Commander, do you also want to take a bite of my apple candy? Here you go~

102182.name: Sweet☆Christmas
102182.desc: Merry Sweetsmas, Commander! Today, I get to eat as many sweets as I want without anyone saying things about it~♪ Hmm, I already eat this much every day? I guess so~

304050.name: Amagi
304050.desc: 1st Ship of the Amagi-class Battlecruisers, Amagi

304051.name: Wending Waters, Serene Lotus
304051.desc: Commander, are you here to pay me a visit? ...Ah, there is no need to be concerned about me. I made a promise to both you and Akagi that I would be mindful of my health.

304052.name: Red Kite Respite
304052.desc: *munch*... Ah. Commander, the banquet isn't over yet. What brings you here? When a host sneaks out, that causes trouble for the person cleaning up after them... Heehee, I didn't say NOT to, now, did I?

301801.name: Time for School!
301801.desc: All right, everything looks good! I'm super excited and my batteries are fully charged! I'm heading out~!

202201.name: White Rose
202201.desc: My dear, I changed into the new outfit as per your request. I would be most grateful were you to offer me words of praise, Master.

202202.name: Scorching-Hot Seirios
202202.desc: I've received ample advice from my colleagues in the Maid Team regarding swimwear etiquette. My honourable Master, are you pleased with my appearance?

202203.name: Azure Horizons
202203.desc: I have heard it is part of a maid's duties to dress to her honourable Master's liking over the holidays. Would this outfit happen to... satisfy the honourable Master's wishes?

202204.name: Rabbit of Paradise
202204.desc: To you, Honourable Master, I dedicate this dance of paradise. It is something I have spent a great deal of time practicing... I do hope that it is to your liking.

202211.name: Eastern Grace
202211.desc: As I am but a maid, it is a great honor to be able to wear such a gorgeous outfit… How do I look, Commander? "Not sure where to start feasting your eyes?" Oh my... Commander...

202219.name: Curacoa (Retrofit)
202219.desc: It is my honour to be of everyone's service. Light cruiser Curacoa takes it upon herself to continue serving you, Master.

202221.name: Rhythm of the Dragon Empery
202221.desc: You can feel the profound heritage and culture of the Dragon Empery from all these customs and outfits for the Lunar New Year's Festival… It seems to be ever more necessary to study the traditions and etiquette of this wondrous culture.

202229.name: Curlew (Retrofit)
202229.desc: I am now more capable than ever of demonstrating the Royal Maids' style. Though I am not as talented as my sister, Curacoa, I sincerely hope you will find my service satisfactory. It is a great honour to work for you.

101382.name: Style of the East
101382.desc: While wearing clothes from the Dragon Empery, I can't help but reminisce about those days... Hehe, Commander, do you prefer me in Empery-style clothes, or Union-style clothes?

101392.name: Eastern Etiquette
101392.desc: What's with the weird look, Commander? Ah, I got this outfit while studying abroad in the Dragon Empery. Umm... does it suit me?

206051.name: The Way of the Dragon Empery
206051.desc: Does this dress from the Dragon Empery not suit me well? Though I was born in the Eagle Union and raised by the Royal Navy, my time in the Dragon Empery also left a deep impression upon me. Why don't we have a chat about their profound culture and tea? Hehe~

206052.name: Gamer Style
206052.desc: Heck yeah! Another achievement down! ...Huh? Good day, Commander. Is there something wrong with my appearance? Hehe, I'm from the Eagle Union after all, of course I'd know a thing or two about entertainment~♪

107220.name: Independence
107220.desc: Independence-class light aircraft carrier – Independence, Hull Number CVL-22.

107221.name: Transfer Student From Afar
107221.desc: So this is my new school, huh? Hmm... gotta put my stuff down first before checking in with the teacher.

107222.name: The Independent Line
107222.desc: Hmm... Isn't this one a bit too garish? Mm... What if we pair it with a necklace or some sort of purse? ...Commander, your thoughts? C'mon, don't just stare at me, give me something to work with here...

107223.name: Liberty and Leisure
107223.desc: Whew... A bit of stretching helps keep the body flexible. Hm? I'm in loungewear, what about it? I'd appreciate it if you wouldn't stare too much, though...

107224.name: The Tailwind of Opportunity
107224.desc: Just need to feed it a coin, then operate the crane with the joystick... Oh! I got one! That was easier than I expected.

107229.name: Independence (Retrofit)
107229.desc: Light carrier Independence reporting. Retrofitting complete. I'm ready to take on harder, more vital missions. Leave anything like that to me.

107380.name: Shangri-La
107380.desc: Essex-class aircraft carrier – Shangri-La, Hull Number CV-38.

107381.name: Utopia's Collector
107381.desc: Commander, welcome to my "Utopia." Here, you can find my prized collection. Now, where should we start our detailed tour?

107382.name: Explorer of the Lost World
107382.desc: This specimen looks to be fairly ancient... You could watch from behind me, or you could join me for an up-close examination; we can enjoy our time here however you wish.

401021.name: High-Rise, High-Style
401021.desc: Commander, I do wonder if your order to "come dressed in new clothes" was simply your way of saying "I want to see you in a casual outfit." No matter the case, I'm happy to oblige.

401022.name: Of Koi and Evening Hues
401022.desc: Being able to see you all flabbergasted makes changing into this outfit worth it. Are you going to keep standing there like a scarecrow? Come over here~ Who knows, we might even be able to see the fireworks from this spot.

107170.name: Bunker Hill
107170.desc: Essex-class aircraft carrier – Bunker Hill, Hull Number CV-17.

107171.name: Mission Relaxation
107171.desc: Mission complete. Next up, a new recommendation from Long Island... Oh, Commander? Come make yourself comfortable.

317010.name: I-13
317010.desc: Type A Mod. 2 cruiser submarine – I-13.

303170.name: Suzuya
303170.desc: Mogami-class heavy cruiser number three – Suzuya.

303172.name: Midnight Care
303172.desc: Suzuya, the Mogami-class heavy cruiser, will be the nurse taking care of you today. Heehee, let's have fun with this nighttime examination, shall we?

304060.name: Hiei-chan
304060.desc: Fast Battleship, second ship of the Kongou-class Hiei.

408040.name: U-556
408040.desc: Iron Blood Type VIIC submarine – U-556.

408041.name: Party Knight!
408041.desc: It's me, U-556, all prettied up! Eheheheh, we're gonna have lots of fun at this party, Commander! Come on, let's go!

408042.name: Prairie Knight
408042.desc: I'm still Parzival of the Seas, even on land! Lord Bismarck entrusted me with these goods and I'm gonna keep them safe! Now step up and try your luck, hooligans!

408050.name: U-73
408050.desc: Iron Blood Type VIIB submarine – U-73.

408051.name: Science Rules!
408051.desc: It's time for science class with U-73! Now, Commander, let's try out an exhilarating and positively fascinating experiment!

408052.name: New Year's Chemistry
408052.desc: In today's chemistry lesson, we'll learn how to make a warming cup of tea and an optional concoction to enhance its flavor! Will you do the honor of taste-testing it, Commander?

202230.name: Swiftsure
202230.desc: I am Swiftsure, a light cruiser of the Royal Navy... If it is not too much for one such as myself to ask, I would like to support your fleet in whatever way I can.

202231.name: Study Hall Cyclamen
202231.desc: Commander, why are you here...? Me? Yes, as you can see, I'm still studying... I figured that acquiring knowledge would be the best way to make up for my lack of experience on the actual battlefield.

202232.name: Beauty of White Jade
202232.desc: I agreed to try on this outfit, but... I know these fancy outfits don't suit me... H-huh, I look gorgeous?! ...Thank you very much. Even if you're just trying to make me feel better, I appreciate it...

202233.name: Midsummer Special Service
202233.desc: W-welcome! ...Ugh, I'm still way too nervous... Ah, um! H-how may I serve you today, Commander...?

901111.name: Sleepy Sunday
901111.desc: Morning, Commander~ Mm, the Sabbath is the day of rest, so I shall not budge from my sacred charge even if you were to call Triomphant over. I solemnly swear to do absolutely nothing today.

901112.name: Mercredi at the Secret Base
901112.desc: I must commend you for being able to find my secret base, Commander... but unfortunately for you, I refuse to return to the office today. Just... *yawn*...let me spend the whole day sleeping here...

901113.name: Listless Lapin
901113.desc: Zzz... zzz... Huh? Commander? I was in the middle of a nap... Oh, this outfit? It's cool, comfy, and cute. If you don't need anything from me, I'm going back to sleep...

801041.name: Beachside Magician
801041.desc: It is said that the summertime sea holds an extraordinary enchantment over people... but the only supernatural thing I'm feeling is this accursed heat... Am I missing something?

308041.name: Coral Reef Bunny
308041.desc: Hi there, Commander. Oh, this outfit? I'll be wearing it to school today. By the way, did you want to come sit in on my class?

308042.name: Sweet Wine of Celebration
308042.desc: Commander, Happy Lunar New Year. Would you like some sweet wine to celebrate? Oh, be careful not to drink too much~

308050.name: I-56
308050.desc: Type B3 Mod. 2 cruiser submarine – I-56.

308051.name: Wallflower in the Corner
308051.desc: School... is pretty nice. I can quietly stay in this corner and mind my own business...

308061.name: Festive Mood!
308061.desc: I look different from usual? That's obvious, isn't it... All right, all right, I was just giving you a hard time. We're at a festival, so we might as well enjoy ourselves!

408060.name: U-101
408060.desc: Iron Blood Type VIIC submarine – U-101.

408061.name: Ironbrass Trombonist
408061.desc: Commander, welcome to the school band! Why'd I join the band? The reason's simple - there's no Motorbike Club at school, haha! Just kidding~! Actually, I'm quite fond of music as well, heh.

408070.name: U-522
408070.desc: Iron Blood Type IXC submarine – U-522.

105200.name: Alabama
105200.desc: South Dakota-class battleship – Alabama, Hull Number BB-60.

105201.name: Untarnished Silver, Silken Gold
105201.desc: Hrmm... Lotta orders to work through... Runnin' a Dragon Empery restaurant ain't easy. Hmm? You here for some chow too, Commander? Then how about... I put you ahead in line?

108030.name: Cavalla
108030.desc: Gato-class submarine – Cavalla, Hull Number SS-244.

108031.name: Convenience Store Raid!
108031.desc: You're late, Commander! ... What's all this? Heheh, it's loot I got from the stop n' rob's bargain bin! Here, have some bread!

108032.name: Colorful Ceremony
108032.desc: Look at all the cute balloons and flowers, and the delicious food as well! Hehe! Parties are the best!

107290.name: Bataan
107290.desc: Independence-class light aircraft carrier – Bataan, Hull Number CVL-29.

107291.name: Comfy Cotton Jammies
107291.desc: Yaaaaawn... Huh!? Commander!? You scared me... I was just going to lie down and... Um, yes, with little Hellcat here... Goodnight...

102220.name: San Juan
102220.desc: Atlanta-class light cruiser – San Juan, Hull Number CL-54.

102221.name: The Longing Princess
102221.desc: All right, dress looking good. Now just to check my makeup... Need to be thorough, so I don't embarrass myself in front of– What?! C-Commander?!

102230.name: Birmingham
102230.desc: Cleveland-class light cruiser – Birmingham, Hull Number CL-62.

102231.name: Rider of Red
102231.desc: Good morning, Commander. Unfortunately, this bicycle only seats one person, but I could dismount and lead it along as we walk together.

102232.name: Fruitful Snow of an Auspicious Year
102232.desc: Happy Lunar New Year, Commander. I'm trying out Dragon Empery fashion for a change, though this dress will some getting used to. Hey, uh, do you want to join me under the umbrella? For cover against the snowfall, I mean.

102233.name: To Where the Wind Blows
102233.desc: The wind and the waves are great today. You wanna try windsurfing after this, Commander? It's a lot of fun and I can teach you the... Hang on, there's a good wind coming and I've got to catch it!

101400.name: Aylwin
101400.desc: Farragut-class destroyer – Aylwin, Hull Number DD-355.

101401.name: Sunday Aquarium Visit
101401.desc: So this is an aquarium... What a novel experience! Oh, also, I won't be your guide today as it's your turn to escort me around, Commander. Please don't get us lost, okay? Ehehe~

101350.name: Bache
101350.desc: Yoohoo~! You the Commander? You look kinda weaksauce, though~! Name's Bache! I'm joining this fleet, starting today! I'll take good care of you, so just kick back and get ready for my greatness!

101351.name: Gorgeous Speed-star
101351.desc: Ahaha~! Are you seeing this, Commander? This sturdiness, this gorgeous paint job, and these special accessories hand-picked by yours truly! Muahaha! I am the true speed-star of this port!

101352.name: Showy Sports Star
101352.desc: Tada! Your favorite tennis superstar, Bache, is right here! ...Hey Commander, you're supposed to cheer for me like you're one of my fans in the stands!

202240.name: Black Prince
202240.desc: Err, you're... the Commander, yes? You don't know who I am? Ah, right, I've yet to introduce myself... I'm Black Prince of the Royal Navy... Will that suffice?

202241.name: White Princess
202241.desc: Sorry to keep you waiting, Commander. Thank you very much for taking me on vacation. Standing in front of you like this... is a little embarrassing... Nevertheless, what do you think of... my swimsuit?

202242.name: Fair Maid Spring
202242.desc: A "qipao," is it? So this legendary dress from the Dragon Empery... Putting it on and enjoying some nostalgic music, makes me... Ahhh... Commander, might we relax like this a bit longer...?

202243.name: Pop the Cork
202243.desc: You can't have a party without champagne, right? Now, if I remember right, you're meant to give it a good shake before popping the cork... Oh no! Look out, Commander!

202244.name: Addled Attendant?
202244.desc: Oh... Welcome, Commander. Can I take your order...? Or maybe, you just wanted to kick back and relax? ...Either way is fine with me.

101410.name: Stanly
101410.desc: Fletcher-class destroyer - Stanly , Hull Number DD-478.

605021.name: The Glory of Naples
605021.desc: A visit to the beach with me? Then you must try your hardest to stand out. Otherwise the eyes of the world will be on me alone.

605022.name: Calabria Aurea
605022.desc: Welcome to Littorio's personal suite. Are you here to issue me a challenge of who can romance the most girls? Hahahah, I'm joking of course! There'd be no fun in a game I would win every single time.

605023.name: Lounging Emerald
605023.desc: Hello there. You'll have to forgive the loungewear; I have scarcely any reason to wear extravagant clothes in my private space away from the public eye.

605024.name: Sitting in the Rain
605024.desc: Talk about bad luck, we're caught in a rainstorm right now. Unfortunately, it seems we'll have to wait it out here, Commander.

605050.name: Conte di Cavour
605050.desc: Conte di Cavour-class battleship – Conte di Cavour.

605051.name: Fierce Beachside Battle
605051.desc: Commander, take this. Good, for the time being, you are a now a disciple under my command. It is time for us to mete out punishment to the unruly.

605060.name: Giulio Cesare
605060.desc: Conte di Cavour-class battleship – Giulio Cesare.

605061.name: Fitness Master
605061.desc: Both exercise and war are at their core about willpower! Now, get ready, Commander! We're not finished until you're dripping with sweat!

605062.name: High Tide Under the Sunlight
605062.desc: Tired already? For goodness' sake, I thought you'd be more reliable than this. Don't go burning all your energy at once, we still have a whole day of recreation ahead of us.

603021.name: Poolside Coincidence
603021.desc: Phew... It's a perfect day for swimming. Oh my, Commander, did you come to swim too? Or... perhaps you had something else in mind? Ehehe~♪

603011.name: Summer's Hotness?
603011.desc: The summer's scorching heat is alleviated by the ocean~ Commander, why don't you set aside your worries and... cut loose a bit~?

601021.name: Refreshing Sundress
601021.desc: Lady Veneto advised me to enjoy my time off by changing into something befitting the occasion... Um, Commander, I d-don't look strange, do I?

408080.name: U-110
408080.desc: Raaaawr. U-110 is a shaaaark. Fear meeee. Mess with me and I'll bite yooouuu.

408081.name: Kleiner Hai
408081.desc: Whenever I play games with Bulldog, I always end up losing. Frustratinggg. That's why... I'll study hard. One day, I'll winnnn.

408082.name: A Cute, Sharky Reverie
408082.desc: I have to wear beautiful clothes to a party, or so Bulldog said. So, I had everyone help me pick out beautiful clothes. Commander, I'm beautiful, right? Eh... cute?

408083.name: Garnished Supershark
408083.desc: The horned idol U-110 splashes onto the staaage. I'll sing all the baddies to obliviooon. I'm scaaary. Raaawr. Raaawr♪

408084.name: New Year, Small Shark
408084.desc: Commander, happy new yeeear. I'm no bunny, I'm a shaaark. Not a cute shark, but a crimson, scaaary shark. Raaawr.

408085.name: Springtime Shark
408085.desc: I'm gathering mushrooms, not garlic cloooves. The edible ones are gonna go in a hearty hot pot that'll warm me and my frieeends. Raaawr.

101420.name: Smalley
101420.desc: Destroyer Smalley, reporting in. Interests: kickboxing.

101421.name: Candy Courier
101421.desc: I am the courier of the night. In other words, it's my job to bring stuff straight to you, Commander. Here you go, this jack-o-lantern is for you.

905030.name: Gascogne μ
905030.desc: Gascogne module change process complete. New directive: sing for the world. Master's order is my will.

999011.name: Tropical Environs Acclimation Service Equipment
999011.desc: Gascogne uniform change complete. Directive assigned: have fun on the beach with Master. Requesting detailed instructions for how to "have fun on the beach."

307100.name: Akagi μ
307100.desc: With the magicks of the Sakura Empire, changing my form like this is a trifle... Hehehe, Commander? Does this Akagi please you?

307011.name: Paradise Amaryllis
307011.desc: "When you gaze long into the abyss, the abyss also gazes into you." Commander, please do not forget that when you gaze at Akagi~ *giggles*

307012.name: Plum and Snow
307012.desc: Commander will always remain by Akagi's side... Right, "Gods?" Of course... Akagi will deal with the pests.... Ahaha...

307013.name: Ruby-Laced Beauty
307013.desc: Commander, I've been waiting for you~ What a sinful one you are, to tempt Akagi like this for so long... But at long last, nobody will ever get between us again...♡

307014.name: Dawn-Phoenix's Summons
307014.desc: This banquet is my present to you... and your attendance is the greatest reward I could hope for~ Indeed, I shall not grant you leave tonight until you pass out. Ehehe... Ahahaha~♡

307015.name: Precipice of Sweetness
307015.desc: Commander, open up. Say ahh... Heehee, heheheheh... You're like a little baby♪ Receiving a lovely new outfit and seeing a different side of you... How blessed am I?

307018.name: Deep Crimson Poppy
307018.desc: We should send out even more invites... This is the best way to rid ourselves of those pesky vixens all at once!

102240.name: Cleveland μ
102240.desc: Light cruiser Cleveland, right here! I'm new to this whole idol biz, but I'll go with the flow and give it my all! Oh, and I'm counting on your support, Commander!

102091.name: Reaper Fever
102091.desc: There's room for two on this pumpkin. C'mon, hurry and get on... Ah, that reminds me! I've got some pumpkin pie as well. Wanna try some, Commander?

102092.name: Gentry Knight
102092.desc: Why am I stuck with this tuxedo when everyone else is wearing a dress?! ... Though it does feel slick, so I guess it's pretty nice. So, weren't we gonna go to the party, Commander? Then it's about time we head out!

102093.name: Road Trip!
102093.desc: Good timing! I was just about to take my little buddy here out for a road trip! Commander, there's room for two if you want to come!

102094.name: New Year's Challenge!
102094.desc: Happy New Year's, Commander! I heard everyone from the Sakura Empire was dressing like this, so... Hehehe, think this looks good on me? I thought I'd ask for your impression first, Commander.

102095.name: Southbound Journey
102095.desc: Isn't it real exciting visiting a place you don't normally get to go? We don't often get opportunities to travel like this, so let's go look for delicious food and spectacular scenery!

102096.name: Golden Conductor
102096.desc: Ahem... I, Cleveland, am your conductor for tonight! Whoa, the echo really IS faint! How did I not know we had such a fancy concert hall at the port? ...Oh, you wanna shout something too, Commander?

102097.name: Knight of the Pop-Up Shop
102097.desc: Commander, you're early. There's plenty of time until the pop-up shop opens. But this is a good opportunity to ask – what do you think of the outfit I made just for this occasion? ...G-girly and cute? Woohoo! That's exactly the reaction I wanted!

102098.name: Heartfelt Moment
102098.desc: Man, this is so embarrassing... C-Commander, w-w-what do you, umm, like, think of my d-d-d-dress...?

202250.name: Sheffield μ
202250.desc: I am Sheffield, from the Royal Maids. I will explain how this transpired to you, so please stop looking like the world has turned upside down.

202081.name: Cloak and Dagger
202081.desc: ... Did you find out about my undercover identity? You leave me no choice. Master, I cannot allow you to leave this room... Of course I'm jesting, it's merely a hobby.

202082.name: A Moment's Respite
202082.desc: The Sakura Empire's summer festivals... they're quite noisy. It will be difficult to keep things clean with so many people around... Despite that, I'm still having a good time. Is there a problem?

202083.name: Black Crow's Finery
202083.desc: The fact that you're asking your own maid to be your partner at the ball shows a concerning lack of gumption as a human being... However, if you go and make a fool of yourself, it will reflect poorly upon my standing as a maid. Therefore, I have no choice but to accompany you.

202084.name: Bulletborne
202084.desc: Allow me to warn you ahead of time, Master. I will not come to your rescue if you spring another trap, so please mind your step henceforth... Just kidding. It is a maid's duty to aid her master, after all.

202085.name: Occult Clash
202085.desc: (Bang!) As usual, you fail to guard your back. This may just be a game, but I won't abide carelessness, Master. Let's clean this zone and hurry to the next.

403070.name: Admiral Hipper μ
403070.desc: Huh? Why are you staring at me like I'm some weirdo? I'll have you know, it's not like I wanted to do this or anything!

403012.name: Sunshine by the Hot Spring
403012.desc: W-well? Does this kimono look good on me? ...R-really? Duh, I know it looks GREAT on me! Who really cares what you think... C-can't be me... No, I didn't say anything!

202261.name: A Maid in Class
202261.desc: Y-ye said ye wanted ta see me wear something different, so... But this is not "cosplay" or somesuch! I do actually go to school...! D-do ye like it?

301811.name: New Year's Comfort
301811.desc: Warm and comforting clothes... Warm and comforting red bean soup... Ahh, I love New Year's.

301812.name: At School with Foo
301812.desc: Kasumi and Foo are excited about the new semester. Are you too, Commander?

301819.name: Kasumi (Retrofit)
301819.desc: Kasumi thinks that her outfit has gotten a bit breezier. Foo said the same thing.

305140.name: Suruga
305140.desc: Battleship Suruga, reporting for duty. It would seem that some threads of fate connect me to this port... No, don't mind my rambling. Please disregard that.

305141.name: Hundred Flowers' Auspice
305141.desc: Good morning, Commander. Everyone else seems to be dressed up on this day of celebration, so this shouldn't be a problem, right?

305142.name: Straightfaced Model Student
305142.desc: Oh. Fancy meeting you here... Walk to school together? Uh, sure! I know the way, so please just follow me.

305143.name: Uneventful Holiday Greetings
305143.desc: This should do it. With how unremarkable my present is, I doubt it'll make any waves when the... Ack! Commander?! Why are you here?!

306071.name: Firebird's New Year Dance
306071.desc: Commander, everyone seems to be busy with end-of-year preparations. If there is anything I can do to help, please let me know.

101430.name: Halsey Powell
101430.desc: Fletcher-class destroyer – Halsey Powell, Hull Number DD-686.

101431.name: Spring's Lucky Star
101431.desc: Halsey Powell is making her debut as your lucky star for the Spring Festival! Commander, if you show me a fun time, you'll be blessed with good luck this year!

102250.name: Biloxi
102250.desc: Cleveland-class light cruiser – Biloxi, Hull Number CL-80.

102251.name: Dapper Gangstress
102251.desc: We're celebrating an overseas holiday, hence my not-so-casual outfit today. Heheh, what do you think? Looking slick?

102252.name: Empress in the Silk Seat
102252.desc: "Hehe... Now that you've finally fallen into my hands, why don't we take the day to get to know each other real well, Commander?" Oh my, was my acting a bit too realistic~?

102253.name: Night Sky's Brilliant Blue Blossoms
102253.desc: I heard that this place is famous for its festivals with beautiful fireworks, so I made sure to come dressed for the occasion... What do you think? ...I'm even more beautiful? Well, I couldn't let the fireworks be the only things leaving an impression upo

102254.name: Romeo or Juliet?
102254.desc: The cast is all here. So, what do we rehearse first? The part where we elope and live happily ever after? Hahahah!

301720.name: Uranami
301720.desc: Special Type I-class destroyer number 10 – Uranami.

301721.name: Snow Vanguard
301721.desc: It's snowing...! I've finished rallying the forces... so let us advance!

701021.name: Bad Bunny Behind Bars
701021.desc: Comrade Commander, are you here to see my room? Hm? That Шутки isn't funny? Then how about... did my room come to see you, comrade Commander?

701022.name: Bunny Remodeling Plan?
701022.desc: Hmm... If I tweak Królik around a bit like this... But, it'll probably be a problem if I don't finish this in one go... Guess I'll think about it while I eat. Mhm.

701023.name: Shadowy Syndicate Showdown
701023.desc: Our shift starts now. Królik, Pirožkí, Manjuus – form up! Let us realize our Manjuu comrades' dreams!

701024.name: Tea Party with Królik
701024.desc: *burp*... Now I think I get the appeal of tea. Why is the cup so small, though? Do you have a bigger one on hand, Comrade Commander?

701025.name: Bunny in the Banya
701025.desc: Uughh... Ooohh... Królik is melting... *gasp*! I'm getting lightheaded... Comrade Commander, fetch me some ice...

701031.name: Thunderous Jailor
701031.desc: You've violated the Minsk Protocol, comrade! Therefore, the sentence appropriate for you is imprisonment! Until when? Obviously, until your jailor is satisfied~♪

701041.name: The Bound Cruiser
701041.desc: ...*Sigh*, I never thought I'd get captured by these little guys... Dear comrade, does Tashkent really have to play along with this?

701042.name: The Blue Snoozer
701042.desc: Urrk... Who dares disturb Tashkent's slumber? ...Oh, it's you, dear comrade? Um, in that case... I can always get more rest later. Is something the matter?

701043.name: The Sprite's Snapshot
701043.desc: Mmph. There you are, dear comrade. I've been waiting... Oh, yeah. I'm not done yet, so... do you wanna relax with me for a bit before you go?

702021.name: Caged Minx
702021.desc: What kinda exercise is this?! Nobody said I'd become a dang showpiece! Come on, get this thing off me, NOW!

702022.name: Sweet Cherry Memories
702022.desc: Mmmh~ I sure could get used to this life~ Oh, Commander, thanks for being my gofer~♪ Ah, you can leave the cherries right over here!

702023.name: Chic and Cheeky
702023.desc: Aaand send DM to Rossiya... Finally you showed up, Commander! So, where are you taking me, hmm?

702024.name: Mercurial Chocolate Love
702024.desc: Happy Valentine's Day~♪ Did you come here to enjoy my chocolate? Then, try guessing where I hid my chocolate – if you get it right, I'll give it to you~♪ Is it here... or maybe over here? Ahahaha~♡

702025.name: Pick and Choose!
702025.desc: Over here! So, Commander, which outfit do you think looks cuter – the left or the right one? Heehee – you better choose carefully, 'cause I'm gonna wear it!

702029.name: Pamiat' Merkuria (Retrofit)
702029.desc: My retrofitting is done! Look forward to seeing how both my cuteness and combat potential have been upgraded!

702041.name: Blend R
702041.desc: Comrade Commander, you've come at a good time. I've recently taken a liking to this blend of coffee. Want some as well? No need to be shy.

702042.name: Drifting Justice
702042.desc: Halt! You have nowhere left to run!! ...Well done, Comrade Commander, what a thrilling chase we had on our hands! What, you think I'm well-suited for this job? You tease too much, bahaha!

702043.name: High Jump Star
702043.desc: ...Hmph! Just short of a new personal best, huh? But make no mistake, Comrade Commander. Keep watching me and your patience WILL be rewarded with a breathtaking record!

702031.name: The Captive Cavalier
702031.desc: Commander, what's going on? Did I... do something wrong...? This was all just... meant to be an exercise, right?

702032.name: White Cavalier's Respite
702032.desc: Phew... Oh my, Commander, I'm sorry I didn't welcome you at the door. You don't have to be so tense - I already know not to try doing anything weird with you. Hehe~

702033.name: Indigo & Lantern-Lit Summer Night
702033.desc: You've been looking for me? Heehee, sorry if I made you worry, I just had to feel the night breeze in my hair for a bit. Why don't you stay and enjoy it with me?

702034.name: Melody of the White Cavalier
702034.desc: Why are you here... Oh, that was rude of me to ask. Maybe you just wanted a change of scenery, or you were drawn by the music. Or maybe my feelings have reached you... I think I like the sound of that one the most. Hehehe.

705011.name: Imposing Warden
705011.desc: You have my thanks for this exercise, comrade! I shall gladly carry out the important duty of judge, jury, and rehabilitator!

705012.name: Keeper of the Firewater
705012.desc: ...Bwahaah! I've had all kinds of liquor, but nothing beats the stuff back home! Comrade, let's have a toast to the coming off-duty days!

705021.name: Skyfall Agent
705021.desc: This is Agent Sovetsky Soyuz, codename Polyarnaya Zayats, commencing infiltration. I'd hate to spend long on breaking through the security, so please just surrender now. It's not too late.

705041.name: Relaxation Stratagem
705041.desc: To pass the time by proactively reading, or by passively enjoying the company of others... Ah, good morning, Comrade, I've been expecting you. Hahaha!

705042.name: Ripples and a Fluttering Veil
705042.desc: Haha! Did you not expect this to be our rendezvous spot? Oh please, even I wish to unwind in the sand sometimes. Since you're here, accepting my invitation, won't you keep me company to kill some time, Comrade?

705051.name: The Lackadaisical Lookout
705051.desc: "Situation normal in all sectors of the facility..." Oh, it is you. I was just giving Minsk the daily report. Do you have something?

107110.name: Intrepid
107110.desc: Essex-class aircraft carrier – Intrepid, Hull Number CV-11.

107111.name: One Intrepid Pitch
107111.desc: There's been a lot of inter-port meets recently... But before I can join a team with my other Eagle Union colleagues, I've got to up my game first! So, Commander, mind training with me?

103240.name: Bremerton
103240.desc: Baltimore-class heavy cruiser – Bremerton, Hull Number CA-130.

103241.name: Scorching-Hot Training
103241.desc: *pant*... *pant*... Man, it's so sunny today... Commander, or should I say, "Coach," could ya lend me your parasol? I'm starting to feel my brains melting away...

103242.name: Kung Fu Cruiser
103242.desc: "Stop right there, evildoers! You've managed to evade justice all this time, but the hour of judgment is finally upon you!" ...Hmm, making the perfect flashy debut is pretty tough, isn't it?

103243.name: Day-Off Date
103243.desc: I reckon we've done enough shopping for the moment. Let's stop and chill here for a bit, then have another look around~♪

103244.name: Relaxation Consultation
103244.desc: Welcome to Bremerton's counseling corner! Actually, I came up with this idea just for you, since you're always working so hard... Tadaaah~! I've prepared us some matching sleepwear~♪

103245.name: Pillowed Counseling
103245.desc: Hold still, Commander! You gotta relax in this position or else I can't do my thing. Take it easy and let me handle them weary bones. Alright, from your hands to your arms, then to your neck and shoulders, time to press down!

103248.name: Joyride of Love
103248.desc: Three, two, one, go! Did you get a pic of me tossing the bouquet, Commander? Ahahah! I'm postin' this to Juustagram later, so you should do the same! It'll be like... retaking our pledge of love♪

101440.name: Cooper
101440.desc: Allen M. Sumner-class destroyer – Cooper, Hull Number DD-695.

101441.name: Blazing Tennis Battle
101441.desc: 30 to 15... Next match will be mine, you hear! Oh, Commander, are you here to play a round of tennis?

101442.name: Heartwarming Holiday Hearth
101442.desc: Hm? I'm just wrapping up some presents! Can't just present them as-is, and all that. Hehe~ I could sure use a little help, Commander!

102260.name: Reno
102260.desc: Atlanta-class light cruiser – Reno, Hull Number CL-96.

102261.name: Biggest Little Cheerleader
102261.desc: This really is a huge clash of all the biggest names from all the factions. It's one exciting match after another! I gotta cheer my hardest too. Eagle Union, go get 'em!

102262.name: Summer Spin-off
102262.desc: "Superhero spin-off! The superhero who saved the world is enjoying a hard-earned vacation on the afternoon beach with the sidekick!" ... Hehe, Commander, a tagline like that sounds pretty cool, doesn't it?

102263.name: Reno Bunnino
102263.desc: Come on in, Commander! Don't you recognize me? I'm Reno Bunnino – cutesy bunny girl by day, villain-vanquishing superhero by night! Pretty neat concept, am I right?

102264.name: Spring's Inspiration
102264.desc: Check this out, Commander! Hehehe, I added a little firework launcher to my superhero gadgets. Cool, huh? ...Your interest lies more in my new look? But... the firework...

108040.name: Bluegill
108040.desc: Gato-class submarine – Bluegill, Hull Number SS-242.

108041.name: Up-And-Coming Infielder
108041.desc: Look out for Bluegill's ultra-reliable defense, Intrepid! Hehehe, Commander, stay here and see the results of Bluegill's special training!

106550.name: Casablanca
106550.desc: Casablanca-class escort carrier – Casablanca, Hull Number CVE-55.

106551.name: Cheer Squad on Break
106551.desc: Phew... Can't train hard if you don't stay hydrated! Oh, Commander, good day! Did you come to watch us practice?

102270.name: Marblehead
102270.desc: Omaha-class light cruiser – Marblehead, Hull Number CL-12.

102271.name: Boxing Girl!
102271.desc: After trying out a whole bunch of activities, I settled on joinin' the boxing club in the end. Everyone wants to exercise now and then, right? Come along, Commander, and we'll have a fun workout together~

102272.name: Charmer in the Snowy Reflection
102272.desc: Whoa! Talk about a stunning view! You like, totally know all the best spots in the city, Commander~ Hehe, okay, so... Merry Christmas!

102273.name: Moongazing on the 29½th
102273.desc: The annual moon gazing festival's upon us again~ Ah, so you know a thing or two about the Mid-Autumn Festival, Commander? Then I reckon you know what we're doing tonight, right~? ♡

102274.name: Not-So-Serendipitous Rain
102274.desc: Phew... Should be in the clear now. Oh, hey, Commander. Whatcha doing here? Waiting for a cutie to show up or something? Surely it can't be a coincidence... right?

301821.name: Morning Moon, Beachside Flower
301821.desc: I've heard some say that summer is the season of cherry blossoms, lotus petals, and sunflowers, but... If you ask me, being able to leisurely enjoy the breeze with you feels pretty good too. Hehe~

301822.name: Blossoming Spring, Resplendent Moon
301822.desc: What kinds of flowers should I decorate the office with for the Lunar New Year...? Ugh, I just can't decide! Um, Commander, will you be inspecting the interior? I'll show you around! Phew...

301831.name: Long Waves of Happiness
301831.desc: Akashi pushed me into getting this outfit, saying that it would surely make you happy, but... What do you think...?

301832.name: Long-Awaited Warmth
301832.desc: There's still some time before the banquet begins, and I'm afraid I'm feeling a little sleepy... W-would you mind if I took a nap? Thank you...

301833.name: Nestling Up for the Long Nights
301833.desc: I wanted to help you relieve some stress, so I thought I would read some folk tales to you... When I mentioned that, Akashi suggested these clothes to me... Wh-what do you think?

301834.name: Heartmelting Warmth
301834.desc: Commander? You stopped eating. Does it taste too bitter...? Oh no, if you don't like the chocolate I made, I... I-I can still make you happy in other ways!

301838.name: Waves of Eternal Love
301838.desc: Now that the big day is here, I'm awfully nervous... I-I'll be in your care now and forever, okay?

901021.name: Overthinking Summer
901021.desc: Commander, you're not going to get into the water? ...Ah, I'm fine right here. To tell you the truth, I once got washed away by the waves, and then got laughed at by Vauquelin... so I'm perfectly fine right here.

805011.name: Fleuron of the Waves
805011.desc: This swimsuit... Yes, the one Émile picked out for me, seems a bit skimpy... I didn't think she'd be the type to trick me into wearing something like this, but... Commander, where are you looking?

805012.name: Evergreen Prophecy
805012.desc: Commander, I wish you a Happy New Year. May you avail yourself of the period of repose that follows the culmination of the year's duties. I pray that you and everyone else may receive the blessing of the Heavens.

802021.name: Saintess of the Sea
802021.desc: "O chosen hero, I bestow this sword upon you so that you may clear any obstacles in your path..." Commander, how did that sound?

802022.name: Patron Saintess of Celebration
802022.desc: Oh, Commander, would you like to release a lantern? I hear they're a way to send wishes into the heavens above... May our Lord bless our companions and bring peace and joy to all.

903021.name: White Sand Paradise
903021.desc: Oh my, hehe... Are you enjoying the warmth of the sunlight here? I'm glad that you're finding some time to relax here, but wouldn't you rather come play with everyone else?

903022.name: Red Queen's Decree
903022.desc: Oh my, it seems that the one who ended up coming wasn't little Alice, but you instead... Do you plan to defy me as well, Commander? If so, I'll have to put you on trial for your sins... How was my acting just now? Hehe~

902010.name: La Galissonnière
902010.desc: La Galissonnière-class light cruiser – La Galissonnière.

902011.name: Pristine Piscene
902011.desc: Summertime means pool time! Oh, hey, Commander. What are you waiting for? Come over and let's have fun!

902012.name: Lush Spring Dreams
902012.desc: Happy New Year, again! So, you wanna try sharing this "cross-cupped wine?" What, it's not a drinking game? Welp, I guess I've still got a whole ton to learn about the Dragon Empery's customs~

902013.name: Black Cat of All Hallows' Eve
902013.desc: If you ignore me, I'll use my black cat magic to turn you into a pumpkin! Is that Halloweeny enough? Ahahaha! I'm just messing! C'mon, let's go do somethin' fun tonight, Commander!

901031.name: Innocent Summer Knight
901031.desc: Commandeeer! What are you doing? It's our day off! Turn the work part of your brain off and just have fun! C'mon, let's enjoy ourselves on the beach!

901032.name: One-Girl Orchestra
901032.desc: Yes, the strings... I can hear the celebratory melody... Now, follow my lead and we'll take this song to greater– Oh, Commander? What's all this, you ask? Uhh... You know... Ahahaha...

901033.name: Otherworldly Adventure
901033.desc: *crash*! Found another coin! Check it out, Commander! I got all these from smashing pots! ...Breaking the law? Heheh! The one law among thieves is that there are no laws♪

807011.name: Summer Lifeguard
807011.desc: Are you perhaps feeling unwell, Commander? Oh, I see, you're just looking for a shaded place to rest? Acknowledged. In that case, you may sit here if you'd like.

207090.name: Little Illustrious
207090.desc: Illustrious-class aircraft carrier – Illustrious, Hull Number 87.

201320.name: Eskimo
201320.desc: Eskimo, Tribal-class Destroyer, is here! Oi, this fleet's not half bad! Nice to meet you, Commander!

201321.name: Parkaless Prankster
201321.desc: Oh woe, nobody wants to play with me because they're all too busy~ ...Oh, hello little Manjuu... Heheh, maybe I'll play a prank on you instead!

205090.name: Howe
205090.desc: King George V-class battleship – Howe (HMS Howe.)

205091.name: Noble Rouge
205091.desc: Sorry to keep you waiting, but now I'm ready to– Commander? What's the matter? It'll get dark soon if you keep standing around like that.

205092.name: Pastry Princess
205092.desc: "Please, Master, save meee." ...Ugh, I can't get into the role. What sort of tone should I be aiming for, love?

205093.name: Evening Marvels
205093.desc: Thanks for your patience, love. I've looked forward to this evening's party for a long, long time. Hopefully George, York, and company won't laugh at me after how much effort I've put into this ensemble... What do you think of it, Commander?

206060.name: Perseus
206060.desc: Colossus-class light aircraft carrier – Perseus (HMS Perseus.)

206061.name: Unfamiliar Duties
206061.desc: I'm Perseus, I will be your nurse today. Use this button to call for me if you need anything... Yes? Did you need something?

206062.name: Spring's Lackadaisical Leisure
206062.desc: Whew. Lunar New Year... Easy to grasp in various ways. Both the holiday and your tastes, I mean. Heehee.

202271.name: Pure White Angel
202271.desc: My, what brings you here, Commander? Are you feeling unwell? That's no good... Why don't you come sit over here first? I'll start by taking your temperature...

202272.name: Pure White Holiday
202272.desc: Commander, I've brought the chair. If you don't want to get in the water, feel free to sit here. ...Hm, me? Of course, I will remain by your side.

202273.name: Graceful Afternoon Tea
202273.desc: Would you care for some afternoon tea, Commander? Heehee~ This is one of my little hobbies when I'm not performing my maid duties.

202274.name: Pristine Herbalist
202274.desc: How are you feeling, Commander? Hehe, I'm not wearing my usual nurse's gown right now, but I suppose this isn't much different~

202275.name: Winter Dearest
202275.desc: Commander, umm... Happy Valentine's Day! What do you think of my outfit? Hehe, it's perfect for a date, isn't it?

202278.name: Dawn's Oath
202278.desc: I'm so happy to have come this far with you, Commander. May this gorgeous sunrise watch over us for all time... I love you, Commander.

205101.name: Mischievous Little Nurse
205101.desc: Hehe~ As this medical facility training is crucially important, a charismatic leader such as myself would be best suited to instruct everyone on– Wait a moment, what's with this outfit?! You there, explain the meaning of this at once!

205102.name: Queen Valiant I
205102.desc: Why the astonished look on your face? You heard me correctly! On this day, I am not merely Valiant, I am the regal and royal Queen Valiant!

201331.name: One-Week Medical Experience?
201331.desc: This is a special exercise for our on-site medical facilities! Well, that's what they said anyway, but isn't this kind of weird...? I feel like I'd rather be taking care of others, not the other way around...

201332.name: Nereid's Discovery
201332.desc: "Let's go explore the ocean together! What special things will we be able to find today~?" Hehe, how's that, Commander?

201333.name: At Your Service
201333.desc: I hope your work's going well, Commander! I've been here playing with these kitties since finishing my duties. Here, I brewed some fresh tea to help you recharge~

401261.name: Sharing is Caring
401261.desc: Commander, welcome to my pad! Ah, give me a sec, let me go grab all the snacks and drinks and games!

408090.name: U-96
408090.desc: Iron Blood Type VIIC submarine – U-96.

408091.name: Secret Gaming Session
408091.desc: Nice timing. I just finished an intense battle. The result...? Of course I won. What? Did you want to have a match against me?

408092.name: How Heavy Are Those Barbells?
408092.desc: Mmgh... Guh... Ahhh! These things are heavier than they look... Oh, there you are. You work out too, do ya? Feel free to join me if you've not just come to tease me.

408093.name: Wolfen Dolly
408093.desc: Sup. If it isn't our Commander. Got bored already because you shattered all your previous records? Or, did you run into some mechanical issues? ...Huh, you're here to ask for my support? Did the butterscotch get to your brain or what? Despite the way I look, I've been on the sidelines cheering you on this whole time.

301841.name: Suzutsuki, Beachside Attendant!
301841.desc: Commander, over here! We're about to start without you! Ahaha, what would you like to do, Commander? Beach volleyball? Sandcastle building? We can also go relax in the water if you'd like!

301842.name: Suzutsuki, Hanetsuki Adept!
301842.desc: I, Akizuki-class destroyer, Suzutsuki, shall not allow you to pass through these arches! Hwuh?! I missed the return again...!

303180.name: Kumano
303180.desc: Mogami-class heavy cruiser number four – Kumano.

303181.name: Fancy Waves
303181.desc: It's time for Kumano's sexy swimsuit debut~! Just kidding~☆ Hey Commander, just where~ are~ you~ staring~? Ahaha~♡

303182.name: PJ Poker Party
303182.desc: Now it's your turn, Commander! Which one's it gonna be~? You suuuure you wanna pick this card? ...I hear you, Suzuya! Stop tellin' the Commander what the cards are!

303183.name: One Thousand and One Nights' Wishes
303183.desc: Tadah! Get a load of my... dancer outfit! So, whaddya think? Ahaha~♡ Hey, Commander, where are those eyes wandering? Did ya see something ya like?

306081.name: Summer Shine
306081.desc: An order of coconut milk... and grilled sausage. Mm, that should do it. ...Hm? Commander? Are you here to place an order, or to get away from the heat?

306082.name: Mosaic of Blending Colors
306082.desc: I had this outfit custom-made just for today... Do you like it, Commander? Um, that's good then... (*whispers*) Booyah.

306091.name: Shimmering Surf
306091.desc: Hehe~ If you don't have any other plans, then your only task... is to enjoy a holiday by the sea! Commander, have you switched into vacation mode yet?

319011.name: Hot Springs Relaxation
319011.desc: Ack... Owww... My apologies, Commander, I seem to have slipped on something... At times, it's hard to notice things I'm about to step on... Ugh...

319012.name: Maid for Mayhem
319012.desc: Hyah?! U-Umm, I can't get out... Oh, Commander?! I'm sorry! I tripped while I was cleaning, and I ended up stuck in here! Umm... What do I do now...

319013.name: Robust Floral Strings
319013.desc: ♪~ Commander, how'd that sound? Hmm... I just started learning last minute, so I guess things aren't coming together after all... But, why do I sound off-pitch even though I'm playing everything exactly the way I was taught...?

319014.name: Fresh and Sweet
319014.desc: W-welcome... A bottle of milk is just as good after swimming in the pool as it is after bathing in a hot spring... Umm, should I really be wearing this? You seem to be blushing, Commander...

107231.name: Seaside Training
107231.desc: Commander, are you also here to swim? ...Ah, this here? I brought it with me to the ocean to get some practice in.

107232.name: Lolipop Paradise
107232.desc: You're finally here? ...Ah, well, I only just got here as well, so don't worry about it. Anyway, shall we get going?

107233.name: Gift-Wrapped Reindeer
107233.desc: I'm done changing... Is this supposed to be a "reindeer" costume? It feels a bit too risqué... Oh, Commander, since you're already here, come get your Christmas present.

307110.name: Taihou μ
307110.desc: With these clothes, and upon this stage... Ahaha... Ahahaha... Fate has ordained that my Commander shall fall for me here... Commander, please listen to the song of my love until the very end~♡

307071.name: Forbidden Fruit
307071.desc: You're taking so long to dress yourself, my Commander. Are you struggling to find something to match my dress? Hehe, it doesn't matter what you wear, you're always perfect to me♡

307072.name: Phoenix's Spring Song
307072.desc: Hehehe, I let Christmas and New Year's slip right by me, that I might use the Dragon Empery's Lunar New Year to capture my Commander's attentions... Oh, My Commander, won't you please enjoy the show I've prepared for you♡

307073.name: Enraptured Companion
307073.desc: Do I make a nice race queen, my Commander...? Hehe. With these proportions, and my fantastic outfit~♡ The others couldn't hope to compare with me!

307074.name: Sweet Time After School
307074.desc: Ehehe~ There is no greater bliss than being with you after classes are over, my Commander~ The kitty here seems to agree♡

307075.name: Seaside Daydreams
307075.desc: A beach date, just me and my Commander... I could walk by your side forever—No, I can't be satisfied by this alone. And neither can you... Right, my Commander?♥

307076.name: Fun on the Baize
307076.desc: Aah... I didn't think you'd agree to my offer for some extra "entertainment" together♡ Just the thought of you using your body to guide mine now... Heehee♡ I'm all yours to command.

307078.name: Temptation on the Sea Breeze
307078.desc: My Commander~ Do you like the location that I've chosen~? We have the entire evening to ourselves, free from the disturbance of anyone else...! Ahhh, my heart is throbbing even more vigorously than the ocean's waves~♡

701050.name: Tashkent μ
701050.desc: How do you like my outfit, dear comrade? ...Is that so? After all of Tashkent's work to become an idol, that's how you react? Hmph. Just you wait. My next concert will rock your socks off.

701041.name: The Bound Cruiser
701041.desc: ...*Sigh*, I never thought I'd get captured by these little guys... Dear comrade, does Tashkent really have to play along with this?

701042.name: The Blue Snoozer
701042.desc: Urrk... Who dares disturb Tashkent's slumber? ...Oh, it's you, dear comrade? Um, in that case... I can always get more rest later. Is something the matter?

701043.name: The Sprite's Snapshot
701043.desc: Mmph. There you are, dear comrade. I've been waiting... Oh, yeah. I'm not done yet, so... do you wanna relax with me for a bit before you go?

202280.name: Dido µ
202280.desc: I am the light cruiser, Dido, currently taking part in idol activities as part of the experimental Muse System. I learned more or less what idols are supposed to do from the others, so p-please... keep a close eye on me!

202041.name: Anxious Bisque Doll
202041.desc: It is so audacious for a lowly maid to dress herself in such finery and stand at her master's side... Still, I will go to my master and... M-M-Master...?!

108050.name: Albacore μ
108050.desc: Lights! Camera! Albacore! Ahaha, don't worry about it, I'm just getting fired up over here! Oh, did you come up with a better idea? Tell me, tell me~

108021.name: Beneath the Black Dress
108021.desc: Oopsie! I totally just dropped something by mistake~! I'd better pick it up quick! Hmm? Saw something you shouldn't have, Commander? Hehehe~ That makes you my partner in crime now!

108022.name: A Catty Surprise!
108022.desc: Surpriiiise! I was in the box all along! ...Did I really freak you out that much? Heehee~ Here, have this voucher as an apology. Come see me later to use it~♪

103250.name: Baltimore μ
103250.desc: The name's Baltimore, Eagle Union heavy cruiser. Whoops, right, I'm not just a soldier anymore, but an idol as well. I agreed to do it, and I'm gonna do it as best I can. We'll be counting on your support, Commander.

103161.name: After-School Ace
103161.desc: Oh, you wanna observe my club activities, Commander? Ahah, as you can tell, it's just a sports club with the goal of making you sweat. Nothing suspicious about that, is there...?

103162.name: Black Ace
103162.desc: Heya, you here to watch the game? Heh, heavy cruiser Baltimore, the passerby solver of troubles, here to play it cool!

103163.name: Evening Breeze Minuet
103163.desc: Damn, that Bremerton... What did she make me wear this time... Even though I was the one to ask her for advice... Um... Ugh... This doesn't look too weird, right...?

103164.name: Ace's Travel Journal
103164.desc: "Our meeting here must have been preordained by fate. Hail to you. I am a passing traveler by the name of Baltimore." ...Hahah, it's nothing. Just some lines I came up with to match my traditional getup. Did they do the trick, Commander?

103165.name: Finish Line Flagbearer
103165.desc: Heya, Commander. You here to spectate the race? Strap in, 'cause it's gonna be wild... My getup? They asked me to help out the grid girls, so yeah. Just hope I'll do a good job of building hype for the race.

103168.name: When the Breeze Blows
103168.desc: The scenery is even prettier on days like today... Huh? What do I mean? I mean our w-wedding, obviously... Ugh, quit teasing me already!

403080.name: Roon μ
403080.desc: Heavy cruiser Roon, reporting for idol activities and associated experimental equipment testing. Today, we fight not with fire and sword, but with the power of song.

499011.name: Dark Red Grin
499011.desc: Such a delightful party with our wonderful friends in this peaceful harbor... It's wonderful, really... But, it's all so boring...

499012.name: Viridescent Lullaby
499012.desc: It's so nice getting away from the bustling party hall and being alone with you, Commander. I'm eager to see what we'll do now as your idea of a... "break"~

207110.name: Illustrious μ
207110.desc: I am the newest addition to the Muse System, Illustrious. Through my songs, I shall spread the light of love and peace— Don't you think that's a wonderful thing?

207031.name: Never-Ending Tea Party
207031.desc: Sun kissed skin, scrumptious snacks and delicious black tea. It’s as if both my mind and body have been rejuvenated— Commander, care to join me for some leisurely chit-chat?

207032.name: Illustrious Ball
207032.desc: An invitation to the ball? Hehe, I would be honored to go... as long as you don't decline, Commander~

207033.name: Resplendent Hibiscus
207033.desc: This is my first time wearing such exotic fashion, hehe~. Commander, if you like how I look, how about showing me off a little~?

207035.name: Maiden Lily's Radiance
207035.desc: It is my honour to get to wear another faction's garments. However... this traditional Dragon Empery dress feels rather tight around the chest area...

207036.name: Lambent Melody
207036.desc: A gentle melody for a peaceful celebration. Today, Commander, I offer this tune to you and the people of the port. May my melody please your ears♪

207037.name: Our Private "Study" Session
207037.desc: Oh, Commander? It's a pleasure to see you. Umm, I'm currently going over some... "extracurricular studies." If you have some time to spare, would you mind joining me?

207038.name: Morning Star of Love and Hope
207038.desc: The end of sorrow, the beginning of happiness, and the desire for eternity.

237030.name: Sweet Afternoon Teatime
237030.desc: Commander, come and try this cake I made... Oh? Heehee, of course I know. That's the ring that symbolizes our eternal vow. I promise to cherish both you and the ring forever...

901120.name: Le Malin μ
901120.desc: I am the Iris's shining sword, Le Malin. As the shimmering idol who chases the waves, may your souls be healed by my songs of prayer.

901111.name: Sleepy Sunday
901111.desc: Morning, Commander~ Mm, the Sabbath is the day of rest, so I shall not budge from my sacred charge even if you were to call Triomphant over. I solemnly swear to do absolutely nothing today.

901112.name: Mercredi at the Secret Base
901112.desc: I must commend you for being able to find my secret base, Commander... but unfortunately for you, I refuse to return to the office today. Just... *yawn*...let me spend the whole day sleeping here...

901113.name: Listless Lapin
901113.desc: Zzz... zzz... Huh? Commander? I was in the middle of a nap... Oh, this outfit? It's cool, comfy, and cute. If you don't need anything from me, I'm going back to sleep...

407030.name: Peter Strasser
407030.desc: Graf Zeppelin-class aircraft carrier – Peter Strasser.

407031.name: Chronos's Kalendae
407031.desc: Eugen, you said that this was is a ceremonial outfit from the Sakura Empire? Surprisingly, it does seem to suit me rather well. Oh, I'm supposed to offer my well-wishes for the New Year at this time, yes?

407032.name: A Moment Frozen in Pure White
407032.desc: You already know, don't you? Since I spent so much of my precious time changing into a dress for your sake... Heh, I'll be taking plenty of your time in return. Hehehe.

407033.name: Lustrous Jade of the Golden House
407033.desc: Heheheh, it may be a new year, but don't forget to be punctual. Just as you've refurnished this study into a Dragon Empery style, I've changed clothes to match. This little book club is just for the two of us, and I mean to suit the mood.

403091.name: Fireworks and Tapestries
403091.desc: Phew... Changing into these clothes took quite a long time~ So, how does it look? A fine mixing of different cultures, wouldn't you agree? Ahaha, Happy New Year, Commander!

403092.name: Rabbit on Watch
403092.desc: *ptwee*! Remember: safety first! Commander, you've got to do your stretches before going in the pool! Be thorough, or I'll get mad at you!

403093.name: Secret Boss o' the Underworld?
403093.desc: Listen up, Commander! I'm the one in charge of this school's seedy underbelly here at this port, so you'd better do what I tell you to! In return, I'll offer you my protection! Ahaha~♪

403094.name: Heinrich on Stage
403094.desc: Alrighty, I'm gonna sing a song for you now! Surprised by how jazzy and womanly I can be, are you? Ahahah!

408100.name: U-37
408100.desc: Iron Blood Type IXA submarine – U-37.

408101.name: New Year's Nightingale
408101.desc: Now then, please lend your ears to this song I shall offer you... Wait, Commander, are you spacing out again? Even though I went through all this trouble to learn this song from my friends in the Sakura fleet... Please pay attention, okay? I'm starting ov

406011.name: Obsidian Elegance
406011.desc: I've been waiting for you, Comander. As per my sister's recommendation, I've put on this Sakura Empire kimono. It was very tricky to get into, I might add... That aside, how do I look? ...Good enough, I hope?

406012.name: Urbane Onyx
406012.desc: Ah, I've kept you waiting. I do apologize that it took so long to get changed into this outfit. Now, Commander, won't you come show me your chivalry and escort me down these stairs?

406013.name: Wave-Washed Paradise
406013.desc: I've been waiting forever for this season to arrive. It's a perfect time, the waves wait for nobody, so I'm off for now. I'll make sure to teach you how to surf later, so look forward to it.

406014.name: Offtime Cafe
406014.desc: Oh, welcome, Commander. As you can see, I'm just taking a break. Nobody thought you'd come right now. So... How would you like to be served?

402051.name: Spring Wanderer
402051.desc: Since you so readily accepted my invitation to go on a vacation together, you must be planning to... Ahh, what I meant is, we can leave at any time if you're ready...!

401241.name: Festival-going Fiend
401241.desc: Come, human! The rite of festivities is upon us! Come hither, and let us revel in this foreign holiday together!

401242.name: The Devil on the Court
401242.desc: Heh heh... As expected, you couldn't even last for a second! Winning too easily takes all the fun out of it... You, the mortal over there, I'll give you the honor of being my next opponent!

401243.name: Blood-Red Dance Beneath the Moon
401243.desc: "Sing your praises to the Fiend of Crimson Darkness, Z24!" ... Hmm, maybe I should go with "Bow down in astonishment!"... Ah, yes! Mortal, you've come at a most opportune time! Hurry and tell me what you think of my new catchphrase! ...Actually, get me down from here first!

401281.name: New Year Smorgasbord!
401281.desc: Commander, Happy New Year! Is there anything you'd like to do on New Year's Day? Say, why don't we try doing all of that stuff, all at once~?

401282.name: Sylvan Celebration
401282.desc: Prosit, Commander! I think these wild animals were attracted by the champagne's aroma. But they're well-behaved and like being petted. Do you want to be petted too, Commander?

603031.name: Seaside Coincidence
603031.desc: Zara, how dastardly of you to spike the ball at such a time– Eek?! Commander?! Why are you in a place like that?

601032.name: Fair Lady's Invitation
601032.desc: "To refuse a fair signorina's invitation would be most uncouth"... Hehe~ Now, Commander, would you like to partake in some refreshments? Rest assured, they're all non-alcoholic♪

701061.name: No Snow No Life
701061.desc: It sucks not being able to play in the snow... Oh well! I'll play some games instead! Commander, let's play something fun together!

701062.name: Nurse on the Night Shift
701062.desc: Huh?! Commander, why did you walk here?! If you're feeling bad, just press the call button... Ugh, you can't walk around at night when you're sick! Grrr!

408110.name: U-410
408110.desc: Iron Blood Type VIIC submarine – U-410.

408111.name: Spring Festival Scheme
408111.desc: Happy Lunar New Year. Have you cooked up a scheme for this year's festival? Hehehe~ I'm of course talking about giving out New Year's gifts and hanging up decorations. I've devised a master plan of my own.

408112.name: Practice Makes Perfect
408112.desc: And for my finishing move... maybe something like this? Heehee. What do your eyes think, Commander?

502040.name: Ying Swei
502040.desc: Chao Ho-class protected cruiser – Ying Swei.

502041.name: Snowy Pine's Warmth
502041.desc: Happy New Year, Commander. I've come to deliver you blessings for this coming year... Next, you're going to ask for a red envelope, right? Hehe, just teasing~

502042.name: Frolicking Flowers, Verse I
502042.desc: Commander, Happy New Year! Chao Ho and I are preparing for this year's Spring Festival, and as you can see... we're in the middle of a little "intermission." Hehe, don't worry, there's nothing you need to help out with. Just take a seat over there and enjoy the show~

502043.name: Blue Waves, Limpid Summer
502043.desc: Heehee, if it isn't the Commander. Your timing is perfect~ I was thinking I might take a break here... While you're here, why don't you rest in the pool with me?

502050.name: Chao Ho
502050.desc: Chao Ho-class protected cruiser – Chao Ho.

502051.name: Plum Blossom's Illumination
502051.desc: Happy New Year, Commander! This red envelope is my gift to you... after all, that's my responsibility as a big sister! Anyway, hurry up and take it!

502052.name: Frolicking Flowers, Verse II
502052.desc: Happy... New Year... Commander... Gah, this isn't the time for pleasantries! And you, help me catch the dumb fluffball that ran off with our ornaments! Jeez, why is this happening when I'm in the middle of getting ready for the Spring Festival?!

202291.name: Ruby-Red Boudoir
202291.desc: Aurora chose this outfit for me because... the Spring Festival represents a time of celebration in the Dragon Empery, and red is the color that best symbolizes that. What do you think? Does this outfit... make you feel more festive?

202292.name: Salty Maid
202292.desc: Welcome, welcome. I've been working here as a maid, just as you told me to. Umm... Call for me only when you're ready to order.

703011.name: Nostalgic Pilsner
703011.desc: What, you've never seen the inside of a shipgirl's room? It's not like you're here on official business, so stop standing around already. Find a place to sit and relax.

703012.name: As You Say, Ma'am!
703012.desc: You've reached the Bureau of Investigation... Oh boy, another case. Commander, finish up your paperwork ASAP. We've got witnesses to interview.

701071.name: A Daytime Delight is in a Book
701071.desc: Wh-who gave you the right to just barge in? ...I did? Huh. Well, seeing as you're here, I guess we could read a book together. Mm, that's all.

702061.name: Sceneries of Pure Snow
702061.desc: ...Achoo! Uhh, good morning... Snow? Yeah, it is snowing today... Woah, it's really coming down hard... Ahaha~

702062.name: Chamber of Fragrance
702062.desc: Hello there, Comrade Commander~ Come take a deeeep breath of this. Sniiiff... Can you smell this room's fragrance? Hm? You can't tell? Oh. Uh, my incense may have stopped burning.

701081.name: Morning's Beckoning
701081.desc: Comrade! The morning is already here! Look how high the sun is in the sky!! C'mon, a wonderful day is calling to us~!!

605011.name: The Flower of La Spezia
605011.desc: Nngh, haah... It's awfully sunny today... How long was I asleep, Commander? Oh, it's already lunchtime? In that case, I'll get started on some food. Would you like something as well?

602010.name: Duca degli Abruzzi
602010.desc: Duca degli Abruzzi-class light cruiser – Luigi di Savoia Duca degli Abruzzi.

602011.name: Lustrous Onyx Sirenetta
602011.desc: Good evening, Commander. Here to unwind after a day's work, I take it? Even dignitaries desire a bit of luxury sometimes. Hahaha.

607011.name: Sardegnian Shallows and Sunshine
607011.desc: Good day, my Commander. We have the day off to enjoy the sea breeze and the ocean waves~ Hehe, would you like to help yourself to some fruit?

607012.name: A Sip of Sardegnian Elegance
607012.desc: Oh, my Commander? I didn't expect to meet you here! Fortune smiles upon me today. Hehe~ If you have a minute to spare, would you care to join me for a cup of tea?

608011.name: Shady Seaside
608011.desc: Hehe, hehehehe... We have this little c-corner of the beach all to ourselves... Now, what should we do first... Hehehehe...

601041.name: Lonesome Beachfarer
601041.desc: It's way too crowded on the beach... I'd much rather be– Oh, Commander? Are you not good with crowded places either...?

601051.name: Beachbound Southwestern Wind!
601051.desc: Libeccio's heading towards the sea! Commander, let's go to where all the excitement is!

601061.name: To a Smashing Voyage!
601061.desc: I know this one! It's that Sakura Empire watermelon-smashing game! Just put the melon over there, Commander! ...Relax, it'll be fine! Have some faith in my navigator's intuition! Ready? Then let's go!

301851.name: Summer Dedication
301851.desc: Commander, have you also come to play on the beach? You're telling me to be careful? Hmph, what misfortune could possibly befall me from a game of watermelon splitting... Gwaah?!

301852.name: Jet Ink, Silver Quills
301852.desc: Happy New Year to you, Commander. To celebrate the season, I had these garments tailor-made for me, using traditional Dragon Empery clothes as a basis. I don't look... childish, do I?

101450.name: Allen M. Sumner
101450.desc: I'm Eagle Union destroyer Allen M. Sumner! Just call me Allen! It's a pleasure, Commander! Anyway, I've heard you've got yummy food and cushy work here at this port. That true?

101451.name: Charming Rabbit
101451.desc: Welcome, Commander! I would fetch you our menu, but I've had a teensy accident here... Don't worry, I'll fix this somehow!

101452.name: Two Faces of Justice
101452.desc: Heheh! Policewoman who protects the city's order by day, vigilante who takes from the rich and gives to the poor by night! She is phantom thief Miss Terious, or PhantoM for short! Your riches are now mine! Your dumb little traps wouldn't catch me in a hundred years!

101460.name: Stephen Potter
101460.desc: Fletcher-class Stephen Potter here. You've probably met a million of my sisters already, so I'll spare you my life story. See you around.

101461.name: Chillaxation Station
101461.desc: Welcome to my private retreat, where you can skip work and veg out all you want. And by "skip work" I mean "enjoy your regularly scheduled day off." Anyway, make yourself at home, Commander.

304070.name: Amagi-chan
304070.desc: 1st Ship of the Amagi-class Battlecruisers, Amagi

107140.name: Ticonderoga
107140.desc: Essex-class aircraft carrier – Ticonderoga, Hull Number CV-14.

107141.name: Show Stopper!
107141.desc: It's showtime! The stage is all set for the performance! Let's enjoy this perfect evening together, Commander~!

107142.name: Sunshine Princess
107142.desc: Hi! Thoughts on my swimsuit, Commander? Does it suit your tastes? Heheh, thanks! If you had to leave a comment, what would you say? ...Where did you learn how to tease people so well?

103140.name: San Francisco
103140.desc: New Orleans-class heavy cruiser – San Francisco, Hull Number CA-38.

103141.name: Funny Bunny!
103141.desc: Music! Lights! Refreshments! We're all set! Welcome to San Francisco's party! Come and enjoy yourself!

103142.name: It's Showtime!
103142.desc: Good evening, Puddin'! Welcome to my pole dancing show! You aren't going home tonight 'til you're head over heels for me♪

108060.name: Archerfish
108060.desc: Balao-class submarine – Archerfish, Hull Number SS-311.

108061.name: Coquettish Bunny
108061.desc: You're our lucky guest today, Commander~ You get a taste of my secret concoction... Excuse me, I meant to say "cocktail!" Relax, it won't do anything weird to you~ Probably. Ahaha~

108062.name: The Devil Next Door
108062.desc: Would you look at that – we're sat next to each other in class. Looking forward to doing some "extracurricular activities" with you this term. Hehehe~

102290.name: Boise
102290.desc: Brooklyn-class light cruiser – Boise, Hull Number CL-47.

102291.name: Sheepish Sapphire
102291.desc: Huff... Puff... Deep breaths... I'll never get used to wearing this outfit in front of others... I think...

102292.name: Castle Tales
102292.desc: Um, I decided to try on a costume, since it's Halloween and all... Do you think I got that witchy look down...?

102293.name: Jade Mermaid
