102293.desc: Huff... Puff... These Dragon Empery clothes look good on me? It's rather revealing and breezy, and makes me feel self-conscious... but if you like it, I suppose it's fine...

102294.name: Flawed but Delectable
102294.desc: Commander, did I get ketchup on you? Sorry... Huff, puff... Th-this is the first time I'm letting you see me in a maid outfit, so I'm a little nervous...

101470.name: Morrison
101470.desc: Fletcher-class destroyer – Morrison, Hull Number DD-560.

101471.name: Sleeping Bunny
101471.desc: Zzz... Commander? S-sorry, I fell asleep for a bit... Uh, umm, what would you like me to do...?

107990.name: Little Enterprise
107990.desc: Yorktown-class aircraft carrier – Enterprise, Hull Number CV-6.

301861.name: After-School Melody
301861.desc: Toot~♪ Oh, Commander, did you hear me practicing my recorder? Umm, I'd appreciate it if you didn't tell the others.

301862.name: Placid Waves, Passionate Heart
301862.desc: *lick*... Oh, Commander, y-you're here for the fireworks? ...Want to watch them with me, then? I've got drinks. My ice cream? Umm... You can't have it.

301863.name: Diligent Domestic Discipline
301863.desc: I'm doing lots of training. Gardening, making tea, stuff like that. Here's an example... Umm, do you want dinner, or a bath, or... Hm? I shouldn't practice that one?

101480.name: Ingraham
101480.desc: Allen M. Sumner-class destroyer – Ingraham, Hull Number DD-694.

101481.name: Fixin' for a Mixin'
101481.desc: Hmm... Could use a little more sweetness, and a splash of the secret ingredient... Oh, you're here? Great. I appoint you as my first dedicated taste-tester, Commander. We're gonna come up with some novel and fresh drinks, you and I!

108071.name: Afternoon Stretches
108071.desc: Phew~ Standing for a long time really wears you out... Hwah?! Commander, when'd you get there? Um, if you'd like, would you like to come exercise with me?

108072.name: Shining Blossom in the Deep Blue
108072.desc: Commander~ Ehehe, can I introduce you to some of my new friends? Here's Miss Tropical Fish, and Mister Manta Ray... Oh, and Mister Dolphin too! Oh, umm, this friend here can be a bit mischievous at times, and often causes quite a bit of trouble...

307121.name: Night-Illuminating Festival
307121.desc: It's– summer– festival– time–!! Uhh, well, maybe it's a bit too late for a "summer" festival, so maybe a regular festival is fine? Well, the important thing is that you have lots of fun, Commander! Because I sure as heck will!

307122.name: Shallow-Water Leisure
307122.desc: Mmmh~ When it gets real hot, whether you're a shipgirl or an ordinary person, the place to go to cool down is always either the mountains or the beach, right? But what if I told you, that when you're at a rooftop pool, you not only get the great views of climbing up a mountain, but also the refreshing coolness of splashing around in the water? Am I right or am I right, Commander? ...Heeeey, are you even listening?!

103121.name: Evening Agricole
103121.desc: To your prestige, and to your continued victories, Commander. Hehe, I do find myself in the mood for rum tonight. Care to keep me company for a while?

801070.name: Le Terrible
801070.desc: Le Fantasque-class large destroyer - Le Terrible.

801071.name: Silence, Slumber, and Solace
801071.desc: Zzz... Commander...? Sorry... for showing you this unsightly side of mine... I'm just, not a morning person... Zzzzz...

801072.name: Sunlight, Seaspray, and Sanctity
801072.desc: How goes your day, Commander? Hehe, are you looking for my clever sister, Le Malin? If so, you would do well to search somewhere less... popular~♪

801081.name: The Noble Knight's Last Stand
801081.desc: H-h-halt, intruder! Thou art intruding in the domain of an Iris Libre Templar Knight, a crime punishable by... Eek! I'm begging you, spare my life! ...It's you, Lord Commander?!

801082.name: Sugary Sabbatical
801082.desc: Enjoying sweet pastries in a lovely dress – heehee, such bliss! ...I care not how unbecoming this is of a knight! I saved these desserts for my holiday! Let me enjoy myself, would you!

903011.name: Rainbow Rendezvous
903011.desc: Yo, Commander, did I keep you waiting? Sorry 'bout that. You know how it goes, sometimes it's really hard for a girl to pick out the right thing to wear. Anyway, let's get going~♪

903012.name: Majestic Majordomo
903012.desc: How are you today, Master? Your humble butler Foch patiently awaits your orders... Hahah! I sure look the part, don't I?

402061.name: Cat Café Cleanup
402061.desc: You little...! Look what a damn mess you made! And I'm the one who's gotta clean it up now! ...Oh. Perfect timing, Commander. Could use a hand with the floor here, after what this little turd did.

402062.name: Gone Fishing
402062.desc: Here's an idea – how 'bout putting down the camera and actually enjoyin' the open sea? I'll move the swim ring so you can chill in the breeze with me!

406021.name: Time to Show Off?
406021.desc: Thank you all for waiting! Large mugs of Iron Blood beer, just as ord–– W-waaah?! Nnngh...! Phew, somehow managed to not spill anything... Wh-what's your deal?!

406022.name: Pure-Hearted Bad Girl
406022.desc: Still not here yet...? Geez, I'll give the Commander what-for for coming later than me... Huh? C-Commander? N-no, I happened to come an hour early, is all...

403101.name: After-Hours Service
403101.desc: Zzz... Huh? Did I doze off? I just meant to rest my eyes for a sec after closing up, but look how long I slept... Hang on, why are you still here, Commander?

403102.name: Bathroom Slip-Up
403102.desc: Oh, good timing. Pass me the shampoo bottle over– Whooooaaaa! Ow, oww... Hey, uh, Commander, could you help me get back up on my feet?

408120.name: U-1206
408120.desc: Iron Blood Type VIIC submarine – U-1206

408121.name: Maid Just for You
408121.desc: Welcome! Oh, Hey, Commander! Heheh, so how do you like my maid getup? Looks pretty nice, if I do say so myself!

405031.name: Mayhem Maid
405031.desc: *sigh* Do you really have to bother me during my break? ...It's a joke, no need to take it so seriously. I was looking for someone to kill some time with anyway.

405032.name: Ignition Matrician
405032.desc: That was a pretty good race – reckon you'll get first place next time, though? ...Hmh. Easier said than done. You know they won't settle for second place – and hopefully neither will you, Commander.

405033.name: What Comes After the Bell
405033.desc: Hm? You look like you've seen a ghost... Oh, you thought I'd have gone home by now? Heh... Who cares? It's not like I've got anything better to do.

202301.name: Red Chamber of Healing
202301.desc: *Pats thighs* Master, you poor thing~ Look how hard you've been working~ Hehe, hurry and come here so that I can pamper you~

202302.name: Brilliant Belle
202302.desc: Tis a pleasure to see you, Master. I am delighted to be your partner for today. ...Oh, I was just trying to sound prim and proper! You don't need to look at me with such pity in your eyes!

202303.name: Prim Sea Breeze
202303.desc: As you can see, today's theme... is a seaside pampering, or something like that~ Heehee. I know you're no stranger to the sea, Commander, but today, we're here to play, not work. Just take it easy, and unwind~♪

502070.name: Hai Tien
502070.desc: Hai Tien-class protected cruiser – Hai Tien.

502071.name: Verse-Weaver at the Water's Edge
502071.desc: What a serendipitous meeting this is, Commander. I was simply searching for a place where I could leisurely enjoy my poetry manuscript. Since fate has brought both of us here, why don't we accompany each other for a while?

502072.name: Soaring Apsaras
502072.desc: Through dance of gossamer silk, the apsaras' grace soars... Oh, I'm simply reciting something I just happened to pick up on. What do you think, Commander? If I've captured your attention, I suppose this was worth our while~

502073.name: Autumn Night of Wandering Spirits
502073.desc: Sorry to keep you waiting. It took quite some time to prepare my dress as well as this lantern... Yes, when you said we would go on a "night stroll," I made some preparations in accordance to what my ancestors once did. Now then, shall we set off?

502074.name: Baker of Heart into Sweets
502074.desc: Welcome back, Commander. I made some tasty pastries for you. ...Huh? You want the one in my chest? Th-that doesn't count.

502078.name: Luan-Feng's Everlasting Duet
502078.desc: "Dragon-shaped jade comb in hand, tied is her hair with gold ribbons and phoenix's hairpin" ...Thank you for waiting for me, Commander. Long have I dreamt for this moment to come true... Please allow me to remain by your side forevermore. N-now then, I believe the next thing for us to do is... c-consumate... *blushes*

502080.name: Hai Chi
502080.desc: Hai Tien-class protected cruiser – Hai Chi.

502081.name: A Dance Among the Lotuses
502081.desc: Look, Commander! I've become a goddess from the Dragon Empery's folklore! Hehehe! Let me perform for you a song and dance number I just learned!

101490.name: Bristol
101490.desc: Allen M. Sumner-class destroyer – Bristol, Hull Number DD-857.

101491.name: Tales from the Empery
101491.desc: Happy Lunar New Year, Commander! The time's finally come to look into the age-old legends from the Dragon Empery! The truth behind these legends is bound to be as fascinating as the legends themselves!

101492.name: "Head" Investigator
101492.desc: Heheh! You're finally here, Commander! My current investigation is into this thing in my... Correction – into that thing that's chasing me! We gotta run, like, now!

506011.name: Vestibule of Wonders
506011.desc: You're here, Commander, just as promised. How do you like the atmosphere in here? Hehe, take a seat and enjoy the tea slowly. After all, we have plenty of time~

506012.name: Cerulean Ripples
506012.desc: Oh my, if it isn't the Commander... Have you also come to escape the heat? What a serendipitous meeting... Or, did you perhaps have some other goal in mind? Heehee...

506013.name: Sylvan Garden's Embroidery
506013.desc: Oh, Commander, have you come to see me? Yes, as you can see, I've been studying the art of embroidery– Just like Go, it helps me organize my thoughts and see things from a broader perspective. Why don't you give it a try as well, Commander? Heehee~

506019.name: Chen Hai (Retrofit)
506019.desc: Just as promised, I present myself before you in a brand new form. Heehee... Since we have plenty of time, why don't you come take a seat, enjoy the fragrance of tea with me, and envision our future?

701101.name: Backstreet Silver Sonata
701101.desc: Seeing you here puts me at ease. I know this stakeout will go smoothly as long as you're here. Mhm, all is fine.

701102.name: Víla of the Crystal Lake
701102.desc: Since you're a beginner at this, Commander, let me show you the ropes. Somehow... it feels like I skate better than usual when you're around. I'm pretty good at ice skating, aren't I? This... should be fine, right?

705061.name: Grandiose Getaway
705061.desc: Your choice treasure now belongs to master thief Arkhangelsk! Think you can arrest me? Then stop gawking and come get me!

705062.name: Supporting Sorceress
705062.desc: I am Arkhangelsk, the royal sorceress who resides in the tower to the north. So, you wish to study magic to defeat the Demon King? Very admirable... You're deserving of the title of "Hero." I will be equally sincere and impart my teachings to you sternly.

701091.name: The Machinery of Life
701091.desc: Yes, these data and results are quite interesting... Though they mean nothing to me! I am a genius mechanic, not an analyst! Ahh-ha-ha-haah!

707011.name: An Irresistible AR Adventure
707011.desc: Volga here. I'm currently tracking an important witness. *gurgle* ...Is my stomach rumbling because this AR game requires so much stamina? Ugh, lost track of the witness just now...

718011.name: Begin the Rush!
718011.desc: Listen up, assholes! We have you surrounded! I'm Kronshtadt, squad leader of the Northern Parliament Special Forces! You have only one option: come out with your hands in the air and surrender!

607021.name: Languid Librarian
607021.desc: Seems school uniforms are all the hype. Veneto picked this one out for me. What are you dressed as, Commander? A teacher? A classmate?

601071.name: Quaver Daydream
601071.desc: *yawn*... Nothing's impossible when you've got Captain Pompey... Hmm? Commander? Wait, I fell asleep? Seems I did... Drat, I forgot what I even came here for...

603041.name: Rooftop Lunch Break
603041.desc: Oh my, are you done with your errands already? Surely, you didn't skip work just to eat lunch with... Ah, sorry for doubting you. Alright, let's go. Trento is waiting for us.

603042.name: Amore Termico
603042.desc: Whew... I'm getting dizzy... I'll rest in the breeze for a moment. You okay, Commander? Step out if it's too hot. See, someone will worry about you...

603043.name: A Brush of Springtime Ink
603043.desc: Commander? As you can see, I'm putting into practice the calligraphy knowledge you taught me before. The problem is, I can't seem to nail it... Could you watch for a bit and guide me?

404031.name: Heir of the Vampire Killer
404031.desc: There it is – Dracula's Castle, brought into this world by chaos itself... On my honor, I swear I will put an end to the divine bloodline!

404032.name: Floral Liberation
404032.desc: How do I look, Commandant? I thought you may like seeing me in a dress, however I don't know if this is what you desired or not...

404033.name: An Officer's Streetwear
404033.desc: Salutations, Commandant! ...You think I look like a totally different person? Haha! You're right – I decided to change up my look for once. Oh, today looks like a hot day, so I brought drinks. Take one!

404041.name: Everlasting Blood Banquet
404041.desc: "Have you come to accept your fate, human? Heehee~" ...Don't just stand there, Commander. Say something!

404042.name: Steaming-Hot Treat
404042.desc: Om, nom... Hmm. Hey! This is pretty good! I mean, of course it's good – it's Empery cuisine! Commander, open wide and I'll give you a dumpling alley oop. Say "aah"!

404048.name: Sleeping White Beauty
404048.desc: *yawn*, finally, I get to lie down. Tell you what, I'm gonna have a nap... Hm? The ceremony's still not over? Hrmh... Look, it's not important. You should just come lie next to me, Commander!

405041.name: Tidying in the Moonlight
405041.desc: You, mop the floor. You, take care of the windows. Once that's done... Ah, Commander. Excuse us, we're in the middle of cleaning the area. If you have need of me, I must ask you to wait.

403111.name: Breaker under the Blood Moon
403111.desc: "Foolish, pitiable creature. Kneel before your Goddess!" Heehee! Hahahah, ahahahaha♥ You're the Commander, silly. You don't need to play along unless you want to.

403112.name: Late-Night Companion
403112.desc: This is armored cruiser Yorck, and I'm ready for a night with you, Commander. My "armor" today – my outfit, if you'd prefer – is made to be enticingly light AND stimulate your desire... Heehee, don't expect to get away from me easily tonight♥

402071.name: White-Black Partita
402071.desc: Raise your head, my darling human. O lost soul, you have three options – become Emden's meal, become Emden's prisoner... "Or become Emden's vassal. Our vassal♥"

402072.name: Moonsilver Union
402072.desc: Welcome, my darling human. Are you looking for something? If it is Emden you seek, you have already found her. "We, Emden, are before your very eyes."

402073.name: Duet of Guiding Stars
402073.desc: Welcome, my darling human. We are Emden, the receptionists that shall guide your way. You can go anywhere you'd like... as long as you give us an offering♡ "Even to an unsullied paradise that is not of this world"♥

402081.name: The Throne of Misfortune
402081.desc: As the mistress of this manor, I c-command thee to kneel... No, of course. I mean, what authority do I have to issue commands? I'm better suited to be a maid than a mistress...

402082.name: Sleepless Night's Wishes
402082.desc: Are you also having trouble sleeping, Commander? I-I thought so... It must be because I was praying for you to have sweet dreams... Look what I've done – now, neither of us can fall asleep... Urgh...

402083.name: Beauty Beneath the Spring Limelight
402083.desc: G-good day, Commander. I'm ready to be your model... Ugh, there's probably going to be an accident if I wish that you'll take cute photos... Better clear my head just to be sure.

403120.name: Little Prinz Eugen
403120.desc: Admiral Hipper-class heavy cruiser – Prinz Eugen.

201341.name: Fluttering in the Fair Breeze
201341.desc: Phew... That about does it. Next on the agenda is... Huh, Commander? What are you doing here?

202311.name: Armed to Clean
202311.desc: My liege... No, excuse me, I should be calling you Master, right? Bellona of the Royal Maids, reporting in. My, you seem quite lost for words... I'll explain the situation to you later, so don't worry about it.

207121.name: Ms. Motivationless Maid
207121.desc: *Sigh*... I thought changing into maid attire would break up the monotony, but just getting into these clothes has tired me out... Oh, Commander? You came at a good time. Shall we slack off together?

205111.name: The Maid-Knight Charges Forth!
205111.desc: Hrmm... *sigh*... Looks like I bungled this one too... I sure hope the Commander doesn't see me like th– Hwuh?! C-Commander? P-please give me a moment! I'll straighten this out right away... Waaah!!

907011.name: Ensorcelled Snow White
907011.desc: Were you planning on freeing me from this spell? Then I suppose you're prepared to lock lips with me. Even though I'm already awake, um... that's just part of the ritual.

907012.name: Sublime Elysium
907012.desc: Do you feel refreshed? Even without a holy ritual, the Iris would be happy to know that I've managed to soothe you with this bath. Was it not enough? Then... Shall we go back in?

907013.name: Blessings' First Flight
907013.desc: Commander, have you prepared yourself adequately for this race? I hope your machine is able to perform to its full potential... and of course, the same goes for you too.

901131.name: Little Red Riding Hood's Worries
901131.desc: What a farce, making a proud Templar Knight portray a helpless little girl... Why am I lying here, you ask? Hmph. Because Le Malin asserted this is the best way to get in touch with my "vulnerable side"...

901132.name: Temp in Low Temperatures
901132.desc: Hmm... Traveling by foot from here would be quickest. Ah... It's snowing. Hmph! A little snow and wind can scarcely faze a noble Templar Knight! I'll be back shortly!

608021.name: Riverside Pirouette
608021.desc: Here to watch me rehearse just like these deer, Commander? Isn't it wonderful being surrounded by the beauty of nature? For a performance based on a fable such as this one, ambiance is key. Ehehe~♪

602020.name: Giuseppe Garibaldi
602020.desc: Duca degli Abruzzi-class light cruiser – Giuseppe Garibaldi.

602021.name: Noble Ivory Plumes
602021.desc: I am the evil swan Odile! Where oh where is my prince? ...Oh, it's you, Commander. My lines aside, pretty good performance, right?

603051.name: A Flutter in the Moment
603051.desc: I've never had a knack for dancing or exercise unlike Zara and her sisters... but if asked, I will dance as best as I can! Please keep your eyes on me, Commander!

603052.name: Tempting Treasure
603052.desc: So... The premise is that you and I were shipwrecked and ended up on a desert island... Is that right, Commander? I see... But if we weren't actually shipwrecked... what is this treasure, then?

605031.name: White Heron of Darkest Night
605031.desc: You seem to have known that I would be here. Then stay and spend the night with me. Just the two of us.

605032.name: Vacation Upon the Tiber
605032.desc: I see, so this is the kind of vacation you meant. It's quite pleasant, feeling like the queen of the world even when I'm doing nothing. That said, simply sitting here is not enough. Come, Commander, and entertain me as best you can.

601081.name: Vivacious Vivace
601081.desc: Found you, Commander! How would you grade this outfit of mine? ...No, no, I wasn't asking if it looked cute or pretty, I wanted to know if I was wearing it right in the first place! You know what though, I think I'll take those compliments~

601091.name: Backstage Blunders
601091.desc: Eek! Wh-why are you guys tugging at my stockings... P-please stop that... C-Commander, please... Hurry and come help me! Waah...

401161.name: Guaranteed Grand Slam!
401161.desc: Heh heh! Count your lucky stars, Commander, because you're just in time – to witness the one-and-only Z16 knock this thing right outta the ballpark!

404051.name: Grain-Seizing Grani
404051.desc: Hah! This donut now belongs to Brünhilde! Alright, now for the finish line... C-Commander? Sorry, but there's no time for chit-chat... I'll be going now!

301881.name: Slapdash Blue Sparrow
301881.desc: Oh nooo! Look out, Commander! ...Oh, phew... I'm glad I didn't mess up your clothes because of my carelessness! Please forgive me for my blunder! I'll clean the floor up right away!

301882.name: Blue Sparrow Heralding Spring
301882.desc: Blue Sparrow Wakatsuki is here! ...Commander, why are you just staring—Oh, no! I'm caught on the curtain... Aaaah!

403130.name: Little Spee
403130.desc: Deutschland-class armored cruiser – Admiral Graf Spee.

201351.name: Fright-Night Scaredy-Cat
201351.desc: D-don't worry, Janus... There's no such thing as Halloween ghouls... Hyeep?! A c-cat?! *whimper*... Jervis, Commander, please come save me...!

201352.name: Fear of Changing... Clothes
201352.desc: It's okay, Janus. You're just getting dressed, so do it like usual, and everything will be fine... Hwuh? Commander? S-sorry! I'm the one who told you to keep your eyes closed, so why did I go and talk to you?!

201353.name: Don't Turn Off the Lights!
201353.desc: It'll be alright, Janus! Nothing bad's going to happen to you just because the light went out and you're all alone... Umm... Hyeep?! C-Commander? D-did you come to pick me up because you were worried...?

201354.name: A Lesson in Billiards
201354.desc: Don't worry, Janus, they'll leave you alone soon... Hwah?! C-Commander? I-I'm sorry! I didn't come up here on purpose. These kitties just, umm, chased me...

201358.name: Oath under the Morning Sun
201358.desc: Keep cool, Janus. Just smile... Today's the most important day of your life. I-it's just... Commander, I'm scared of heights...

206071.name: Silvermoon Faerie Princess
206071.desc: Ah, umm... If you keep staring at me like that... Oh, um, Commander, this is supposed to be a Royalty of the Night costume, right? In that case... Would you mind kneeling for me first?

206072.name: Scent of Spring in the Red Pavilion
206072.desc: Hand brushing my hair behind my ear, eyes toward the camera... Mm, filming promotional material isn't easy... Commander, will this do?

206073.name: A Fairy-Tale Breakfast
206073.desc: Good morning, Commander. Umm... I was excited to prepare a perfect breakfast for you, but I made some mistakes. Please wait a moment. I'll remake it in no time!

9600011.name: Treats from the Deep
9600011.desc: Tonight's dessert is not a cake or a pastry... What are you looking around for? YOU'RE my dessert! Heheh, scared you, didn't I?

9600012.name: Eyes on the Prize
9600012.desc: Hell of a proposition, this. Keeping an eye on your booty for the whole day so nobody steals it. But I said I'd do it, and a real Tempesta always keeps her word. You're all mine for today♪

107120.name: Hornet II
107120.desc: Essex-class aircraft carrier – Hornet II, Hull Number CV-12.

107121.name: Racing Across the Waves!
107121.desc: The title of fastest in the port is miiiine, hahaha! Commandeer, did you see how badass I was just now? There's a whole lot more I'd like to show you, but it'll hafta wait 'til the next race... Well, I'll let you ride with me later, so look forward to it~♪

107071.name: Bubbly Anniversary!
107071.desc: Congratulations! You did it, Commander! Now let's pop the champagne and celebrate! It's party time!

107072.name: Freshly-Baked Bonding!
107072.desc: Mmmmm... Nothing beats pizza straight outta the oven! Here, Commander, wanna give it a try? We're gonna have to recommend this to Enty next time!

107073.name: Cheering Justice!
107073.desc: Let's keep it up, everyone! One more point, and we can make a comeback!!! ...Hah... *gulp gulp*... Whew~! Thanks a billion for the drink, Commander! And thanks for watching over us as well!

107270.name: Langley II
107270.desc: Independence-class light aircraft carrier – Langley II, Hull Number CVL-27.

107271.name: On-the-Clock Vacation
107271.desc: Pheeew... Being able to kick back and relax on such a sunny day is just the best! Oh, Commander! If you'd like to come chill with me, I have watermelon and cold drinks!

107100.name: Yorktown II
107100.desc: Essex-class aircraft carrier – Yorktown II, Hull Number CV-10.

107101.name: Bright-Sky Mermaid
107101.desc: How does this look? ...Ah, it's nothing to worry about. Do you think I should adjust the string a bit...? Hmm... Eek!!! I'm so sorry, Commander... A-are you alright...?

107051.name: Evening I Can't Remember
107051.desc: Hey, Commander, are you lost? How about a drink? ... Huh? Drunk? Me? Oh, Commander, you're such a card. This is just grape juice... isn't it?

107052.name: Saintly Wings
107052.desc: Across seven steps, in a tower atop a hill, you'll find the king's resting place... Hehe. Will you come with me to Utopia, Commander? I'm joking, of course, but I am very glad we could make this journey together.

107058.name: Towards Tomorrow's Brilliant Breeze
107058.desc: This wedding dress, brimming with light, flutters like a feather in the wind... I'm sure that I'm still in a long, deep, slumber... That's right, Commander. The two of us are surely sharing a blissful dream together, heehee.

103260.name: Northampton II
103260.desc: Oregon City-class heavy cruiser – Northampton II, Hull Number CA-125.

103261.name: Swimming Star
103261.desc: Whew. How many laps have I done since my last break...? Oh. Commander, are you here to hone your swimming skills too?

103262.name: Comfy Crane Amidst the Clouds
103262.desc: Phew... This getup does help me get into the festival mood. It looks nice, and it's supremely comfortable, but I can't shake this embarrassment... Huh? Commander? When did you get here?

101500.name: Hammann II
101500.desc: Edsall-class destroyer escort – Hammann II, Hull Number DE-131.

101501.name: Another Rebellious Summer
101501.desc: Hmph! I only promised to come to the beach because I was worried you'd be lonely! There's no deeper meaning—w-wait! What are you doing?! Stooop!

101251.name: Rebellious Summer
101251.desc: I'm not really happy at all! But since you're bonding with me for once, I have to say... thank y... H-hmph! I didn't say anything!

101252.name: Prideful Fairy of the Ballroom
101252.desc: Hmph! I'm only here because you pleaded so desperately for me to come! Don't get any funny ideas! ...Why did I take so long to pick out my clothes? It... it's not like I was trying to impress anyone! I definitely wasn't looking forward to this party or anything!

101253.name: Hammanyan Pawnch!
101253.desc: Ughh... These gloves are so heavy and the dress is too revealing. Why on earth did I decide to put these on... I can't show myself to Yorktown like this!

101254.name: Holy Night Surprise!
101254.desc: I-I'm nobody's surprise! Ugh, I should've never listened to Sims... Stop staring already and undo these ribbons around my arms!

101255.name: Blushing Fellow
101255.desc: Wh-why do I have to dress like this just to cheer for the Commander... Why not just let me dress how I want? Ugh... It's embarrassing, but everyone else will tease me if I run away, so what do I... Huh?! C-Commander?!

702051.name: Maestro of Sterling Strings
702051.desc: ...Thus marks the end of this tune. The Dragon Empery has graciously allowed me to perform in their Spring Festival celebration. Are you here to listen, Commander? In that case... How did you like the song? Heehee.

206081.name: New Year's White Plumage
206081.desc: Steaming hot manjuu buns, ready to be served! Let us have a big feast then gather rosebuds, Commander. Oh, a "holiday gathering" doesn't involve literal gathering?

506021.name: The Festive Undead
506021.desc: I am Hwah Jah, now in zombie form. It is an honor to see you– hmm? What's wrong, Commander? Everyone else is getting dressed up for the occasion, so I figured I'd get in on the action too... Is there something wrong with that?

506029.name: Hwah Jah (Retrofit)
506029.desc: As you can see, Commander, I've completed my retrofitting. So, umm, are you surprised by my new appearance? Don't worry, though. I'll always be the same Hwah Jah you know and love~ Though, if I had to pick something different about myself... I might be a bit more open towards some fun and exciting things~♪

519011.name: Tender White Jade
519011.desc: I see, so this is how you're supposed to knead dough... Hmm? Commander? As you can see, I'm currently trying to make baozi. Would you like to help out?

519012.name: Undercover or Uncovered?!
519012.desc: Umm... Alright, time to take a photo in the on-set mirror and send it to Commander... And there. Just as Commander said, it'd be disastrous if my new swimsuit's design were to get leaked... B-but if I don't do this, our plans will totally be ruined!

207071.name: Shepherd of the "Lost"
207071.desc: Oh my... It seems I've shown you a rather unseemly side of me. Would you help me clean up here, Commander? You know... before any of the other girls find out. Heehee~♥

205141.name: Bashful Oak
205141.desc: Commander? Oh, what a coincidence... Were you slacking– err, I mean, taking a break, too? I can make some room for you if you'd like?

206021.name: A Hundred Sleepless Eyes
206021.desc: Yaaawn... Umm, did I doze off again? Oh no... Organising school events gets so hectic I always end up working right up until curfew... Just give me one more minute, please...

206022.name: Cerulean Enthrallment
206022.desc: "Gaze upon this glorious dress. Admire its brilliance, tremble, and..." If you don't mind, would you please take Argus' hand?

202331.name: Femme Fatale Fresher
202331.desc: Did you come all this way just because I asked you to, Master? Or... would you prefer I call you "Senpai" here? If we're at school, then there's no reason for me to act maidly, now is there? Heeheehee♪

202332.name: Bathed in the Limelight
202332.desc: Good evening, Master of mine. I hope I didn't make you wait long. Oh? That look on your face... Were you excited to walk on the red carpet with me, arm in arm?

202333.name: A Maid's Judgment
202333.desc: Welcome, my dear Master – no, I suppose you're just a traveler at this moment? I'd like to say, "All who pass through here must be judged," but I wouldn't be against simply letting my Master through.

201361.name: The Devil Wears Knee-Highs
201361.desc: Morning, Commander. Looks like our desks are right next to each other~ Whee~☆ Hmm? What's up? Is there something on my skirt? Teehee~♪

703021.name: Lone Wolf Amid the Steam
703021.desc: This steamy hot spring... is a rather novel experience. I left a spot for you, so come sit down already – Wait, why haven't you taken your clothes off yet?

703022.name: Beauty and the Hunter
703022.desc: I prefer talking face-to-face, but if you really insist... Heavy cruiser Kursk sits in an office chair, donning a Dragon Empery dress. What's next, Commander?

705071.name: More than a Little Drunk
705071.desc: Phew... This is... Comrade Commander? Fancy meeting you at this time of night. Me? Heh, heheheheh... You wouldn't believe me if I said I got too drunk and went in first, would you?

702071.name: Devoted as the Warm Snow
702071.desc: Comrade Commander, is the bath to your liking? I'm glad. Heehee, it's a good thing I trusted that "Top 10 Dates for Snowy Days" article and chose this secluded hot spring.

702072.name: The Nurse's Special Rehearsal
702072.desc: Don't move, please. You're playing the patient, and I'm playing the nurse, so it's only natural that the distance between us is different from usual... Hm? What does that have to do with this pose? Ahem. Now that you mention it, umm...

401991.name: Hunter Becomes Hunted
401991.desc: Hmph! You really think this brainless trap can keep me entangled forever? I don't need your help! I can break free by myself! ...Umm, what the hell? Why can't I do it?!

406031.name: A Lick of Summer
406031.desc: *lick*... Hmm. The fact that you can just stand there must mean that you don't mind the heat. It's okay, though. If you don't come in, I'm more than happy to have this pool all to myself~♪

406032.name: A Good Girl's Magic
406032.desc: That's right, I'm the witch Jade, the most famous idol in all the world! Did you come running when you heard my name, hero? I was just about to broadcast my new song, so you'll be the perfect helper. Heheh♪

402101.name: Dark Dragon, Brilliant Beach
402101.desc: Wanted to feast your eyes on this, didn't you? Haha, there's no point trying to deny it. All your petty desires are clear as day to me, so why not just be honest about it?

402102.name: The Dark Dragon's Dungeon
402102.desc: Hmm... Who knew this stuff was in a warehouse, of all places? Heh, I think this will help quite a bit with disciplining that rigging that gave you so much trouble.

405051.name: Crystal-Clear Holiday
405051.desc: Ah, you've already gotten changed, Commander? I'm just... Well, I need to do something about my hair before I go back in the water.

405011.name: Beacon of the Iron Blood
405011.desc: My sincerest apologies for the delay, Commander. Ah, excuse me... as the fleet leader of the Iron Blood, I'm expected to wear this outfit to various formal occasions. Just putting it on seems to make me inadvertently change the way I speak...

405012.name: Iron-Black Elysium
405012.desc: Welcome, what would you like to order? ...If you want, we can drop this charade. I'm not used to being a waiter anyway, so I prefer it this way. Hehe.

405013.name: Unpacked Surprise
405013.desc: C-Commander? Well, as you see, I was wrapping your Christmas present, but now the surprise has been spoiled. I suppose this moment calls for a "Merry Christmas," hmm?

405018.name: Wedding Dominion
405018.desc: You've arrived, Commander – or rather, my sweetheart in eternal vow. I know I can't wear a stiff expression forever, but when I think about the days to come under your guidance, I feel so needy all of a sudden. Yes, it's like you say... just keep smiling.

605071.name: Have a Safe Flight
605071.desc: "I'm your stewardess, Andrea Doria, here to ensure you have a pleasant flight"... Did I sound natural, Commander? ...Still a bit on the stiff side, huh? *sigh*, this job really isn't easy for first-timers...

601100.name: Attilio Regolo
601100.desc: Capitani Romani-class large destroyer – Attilio Regolo.

601101.name: Castle of Inspiration
601101.desc: Welcome to my humble abode! Bunnies, kitty-cats, and the Commander... The gang's all here! Today's tale is gonna be a wild one!

601102.name: Angel from Above
601102.desc: I wanted to try making a fairy-tale entrance. Did I look good, Commander? When you saw me come down from the sky, did you sense destined romance?!

603061.name: Unrequited Office Love?
603061.desc: These stockings are so annoying to wear... Mmrgh... *sigh*. You can't give up already, Gorizia. If you want the Commander's attention... this is what you have to do!

902021.name: Fighting Angel's Regimen
902021.desc: Alright, aim at this part of the ball, and drop my hips... Nngh?! I, I'm alright! The fighting angel, Marseillaise, will not be defeated by this... Hyeep?!

807021.name: Team Stretching
807021.desc: Phew... Commander...? Would you like to... hnnngh... stretch with me? Don't worry, it won't hurt. We have plenty of time, so we can take it slow...

807022.name: Fresh and Fortunate
807022.desc: Mm... Aah, that hits the spot! I just hope my prayers are answered and it suits the Commander's tastes... Heehee, maybe if I personally feed–eep?! C-Commander? D-did you just hear that...?

803011.name: Impulsive Incident
803011.desc: Hm? The door's open! ...Commander? Oh, ahaha... Silly me, I should've put up a card with "occupied" on it... Then again, I... I guess I don't mind if you're the one who sees me~

803012.name: Unrivaled Winsomeness
803012.desc: Oh, Commander. Were you waiting for little old me? You've gotta take your time sorting out your dress if you wanna look snazzy! Heheh, feast your eyes on this cute little kni– Uhh, how are you supposed to tie this thing?

901041.name: Reverent Runner
901041.desc: Phew... Commander? So the Iris brings us together once again... I-I'm sorry for being so sudden, but... Would you like to join me on my run?

901042.name: A Saint's Mercy Can Do No Wrong
901042.desc: C-Commander, p-please hurry and stop this creature! Otherwise! You might! Get hurt! ...WoooooOOOOAH! Phew... That was a close one... Haah... Praised be the Holy Iris... Urgh...

805021.name: Paired Exercise
805021.desc: Mmh... Pilates may be easy to learn, but it seems difficult to master... Are you still okay, Commander? Me? I-I can keep going...

802031.name: Sorcière on Ice
802031.desc: Advanced technology is indistinguishable from magic—and that goes for this icy stage, too. Commander, please enjoy this demonstration of our heaven-bestowed sacrament until the very end~♪

905021.name: Splendid Breeze
905021.desc: The skies are blue and the wind is calm, a perfect day for golfing... Commander? I didn't bring you here just to watch the scenery, you know? Brace yourself, because you're in for a long day with me.

303191.name: Sojourn Through Clear Seas
303191.desc: Commander~ Come over here~♥ Heehee, you look surprised... I don't think I'm dressed strangely at all. Or... is this swimsuit not enough to satisfy you, Commander?

305131.name: Shimmering Forsythia
305131.desc: I love hammocks and water beds 'cause they make you feel like you're floating on waves. It's the most relaxing thing ever~♪ You oughta hop on and try for yourself, Commander~

305132.name: My Wish is For Love
305132.desc: Welcome, guest, to the Dwelling of Demons. I own this place. I will grant you any wish in exchange for a suitable price... Yeah! Recited it all in one go! I'm so goated!

301891.name: August's First Romance
301891.desc: Peace~♪ Do I look good in the pic? Don't I look so adorable you'll never wanna delete the photo, and have to stare at it every day to feel at ease? Heehee♪

301892.name: Luxurious Celebration Time
301892.desc: You said anything's fine as long as I think it's good, right? Well, tadah! I'm going to give you a delectable, delicious drink! Watch closely now!

301901.name: Lulled by Rough Seas
301901.desc: *yaaawn*... Goodness me, there I go falling asleep. You understand how pleasant the sea breeze is, don't you? YOU calling ME a slacker!

102310.name: Houston II
102310.desc: Cleveland-class light cruiser – Houston II, Hull Number CL-81.

102311.name: Ready to Serve!
102311.desc: Thank you for waiting! Houston is here and ready to serve! Mm... I've never worn a costume like this. It's kind of embarrassing... And is it just me, or is it a size or two too small?

9600031.name: Forlorn Femme Fatale
9600031.desc: How do you feel about this look, my darling? ...Not scary enough? How odd... I thought Mary Celeste had the right idea. Wait, I know~ What if I hold this axe, hmm? ♡

9600041.name: Grim Night's Reaper
9600041.desc: I am Mary Celeste, the silent reaper of the moonless night... Aye, this attire befits a ghost ship such as I.

9600061.name: Carnival Under the Blood Moon
9600061.desc: "Ahahahah! I've finally found yooou, Master! Dinner is ready, so just follow me to the... You're not hungry? Aww, but the meat is fresh off the bone..." Commander? Why are you backing away?

9600021.name: The Golden Shadow
9600021.desc: Here you see the opposite side of the retainer of the golden light. Be not afraid. I am still me, and my feelings and my beliefs have not changed. Still, if it unnerves you, perhaps you should get to know me again?

9600051.name: Lazy Pirate Angel
9600051.desc: You've summoned the angel of tricks and treats... Huh? Why am I dressed like this? Meh, it's too much of a pain to answer that... In any case, gimme candy or else! Commander, time is of the essence here. The sooner I can go home, the sooner I can continue my gaming session...

101510.name: Laffey II
101510.desc: Allen M. Sumner-class destroyer – Laffey II, Hull Number DD-724.

101511.name: Sleepy on a Busy Day
101511.desc: Laffey's helping out around the pop-up shop... Commander, sit wherever you want... Any open seat is probably fine.

101172.name: Snow Rabbit and Candy Apple
101172.desc: Mmph... The waistline is too high... and a little too tight... The sleeves are too breezy cause they're so big... It's not like I wanted to change clothes, but... what do you think, Commander?

101173.name: White Rabbit Welcomes the Spring
101173.desc: Have a happy and auspicious New Year? Uh.... can I go now...? I'm feeling a bit sleepy, so can I go back to sleep?

101174.name: Bunny Clerk?
101174.desc: I'm done changing... how is it? Today, I’m supposed to call you “valued guest?” Um... I don’t really get it...

101175.name: Picnic Adventure?
101175.desc: Commander, ahhn... Umm, Commander, Laffey does not need to be fed... Rather, Laffey should be the one feeding you...

101176.name: Bunny Idol @Unmotivated
101176.desc: "Laffey came from Planet Bunny..." Umm, I forgot that line Benson told me to say... In any case, everyone, please give me lots of support... Actually, just a little support is fine... Uhh, I have to do it again with more motivation?

101177.name: Sleep to Clean Another Day
101177.desc: Yaaawn... Laffey's cleaning her room, Commander... If you don't wanna help then just find a place to sit... Anyway, back to cleaning... Zzz...

101178.name: White Rabbit's Oath
101178.desc: Laffey seems to have changed a bit... Commander, do you like how Laffey is now?

131170.name: Sleepy Teriyaki Twister
131170.desc: Welcome. Would you like to try a Teriyaki Twister? I could go for a nap right now inside a nice, warm tortilla... Probably.

131171.name: Sleepageddon
131171.desc: Zzzzz... Good night... Laffey, is leveling up... Huh? Commander? Where'd all the monsters go...?

131172.name: Lazy Days
131172.desc: Oh, Commander? I wasn't waiting for you here... Nope, totally wasn't. But now that you're here, how about we hang out...?

118020.name: Guam
118020.desc: Alaska-class large cruiser – Guam, Hull Number CB-2.

118021.name: Stage-Setting Charmer
118021.desc: Bunny idol, on the stage♪ Commander! You're in for a banger performance, so just forget about everything else and keep your eyes on me!

104010.name: Constellation
104010.desc: Lexington-class battlecruiser – Constellation, Hull Number CC-2.

104011.name: Galaxy's Finest
104011.desc: Welcome, Commander. If you want me to take your order, please subscribe for one month to my horoscope reading on Juustagram... Heehee, I'm joking. If you have any questions, I will gladly answer.

107300.name: San Jacinto
107300.desc: Independence-class light aircraft carrier – San Jacinto, Hull Number CVL-30.

107301.name: Flavor of the Day
107301.desc: Would you like me to recommend a drink? Hmm... You're quite the drinker, Commander~ Let's see if you can handle my favorite♪ Heehee!

103270.name: Louisville
103270.desc: Northampton-class heavy cruiser – Louisville, Hull Number CA-28.

103271.name: An Order of Dreams
103271.desc: Commander, here's your order of... Umm, it's written on the ticket, right... Huh? Where did I put that thing? Oh no, I'm in real trouble if I mess up the Commander's order...

108080.name: Flasher
108080.desc: Gato-class submarine – Flasher, Hull Number SS-249.

108081.name: Tearjerking Service
108081.desc: W-welcome, Commander... I-I as the manager will be serving you today, so l-let's hear your order... *sniffle*... I'm so tense it's making me cry...

504010.name: Huan Ch'ang
504010.desc: 1913 Naval Expansion Project 26,000-ton battlecruiser – Huan Ch'ang.

504011.name: Dance Beneath the Moonlight
504011.desc: Happy New Year, Commander. Hmm? I look a bit different from usual? Why of course, it's because it was chosen to suit your tastes by none other than Chi An. Even this mask is brand new. I look "like a fairy from the sacred mountains," you say? I wonder... who taught you to say something like that?

502090.name: Chi An
502090.desc: CNT Shipyard 1,800-ton small protected cruiser – Chi An.

502091.name: Lanternlit Stroll
502091.desc: May blessings reach you this coming spring. Hm? My outfit? Heehee. Since the ever-so-busy Commander came to see me on this special occasion, I naturally had to put in some effort too– Now then, set aside all your worries, and come enjoy this wonderful evening with me~♪

502092.name: Exotic Dreamland
502092.desc: Phew... Fancy seeing the person of my dreams AFTER I've woken up! Heehee, if this is as fate decrees... Weary traveler, come to me and rest your tired legs.

501050.name: Lung Wu
501050.desc: Vulcan Stettin 1,000-ton torpedo destroyer – Lung Wu.

501051.name: Ascendant Dragon's Spring Feast
501051.desc: Happy New Year, Commander... Having that said, the others said they had a surprise for me, but then ended up banning me from the kitchen... I didn't do anything bad, did I? I'm real worried... Can't I at least take a look at what's going on there? Ugh... How about you go check it out in my stead? P-pretty please, Commander!

501052.name: Invitation to Jade Seas
501052.desc: Woah, the corals look so pretty as they swish and sway... There's a whole world of color underneath the sea... I can come visit again any time I'd like? Thank you so much, Commander!

501060.name: Hu Pen
501060.desc: Vulcan Stettin 1,000-ton torpedo destroyer – Hu Pen.

501061.name: Prancing Tiger Welcomes the Spring
501061.desc: Let's usher in the New Year with the sound of gongs and firecrackers~! Whaddya think? Lion dances are pretty awesome, aren't they? So, Commander, who's got more oomph in their dance steps? Me, or Lung Wu? C'mon, hurry up and decide~!

501071.name: Flying Clouds, Flailing Pranks
501071.desc: H-Happy New Year, Commander... Umm, uhh... C-could you please help me down first? ....Waah, I promise I won't have any more "adventures" in the kitchen...

701111.name: Blue Nova
701111.desc: I'm Ognevoy, the newest policewoman on the block! I've come to arrest you, fugitive! Give yourself up now! I'm going to– Ah! Oh gosh! ...Can I please get a cuter role instead?

701121.name: Rebellious Artist
701121.desc: Let's hear it for the graffiti master that's taken the world by storm – Svirepyyy! You people are in real luck, gettin' to witness the birth of my new piece! And if you ain't got any taste, watch yourself!

705081.name: Meeting the Mafia Queen
705081.desc: Heehee... Oh, are you ready for your audience with me? Remember the important thing – minding your manners. Queen Poltava's time is very, very precious indeed.

201371.name: Normal Potion Maker
201371.desc: I'm Nubian, the master concocter of magic potions! What kind of potion do you want, Commander? ...Huh? It's been so long since you visited a normal potion maker who brews using a cauldron so you don't know what to order? ...Come again?

201372.name: The Modern-Day Clumsy Maid Escapade
201372.desc: Uh, teehee! I was trying to make chocolate, then I slipped for some reason! ...Hang on a minute! How did I slip? Even a modern clumsy maid wouldn't blunder like that... Would she?!

202341.name: Breeze of Blessings
202341.desc: Holy Wind! Blow them away! ...Oh no! The wind's so strong it's lifting up my dress! Um, Master, y-you didn't... see anything, did you?

203131.name: Sadistic Demon
203131.desc: Roleplay mode engaged. "I am Devonshire, the greater demon who controls this land. If you understand the difference in our power levels, you will leave and train yourself in a beginner dungeon for three hundred years. Adventurers such as you will never make it through here alive."

207140.name: Formidable μ
207140.desc: Commander, third ship and idol of the Illustrious class, Formidable, humbly makes your acquaintance. Please do enjoy the show... Heehee, doesn't that just make you shudder with excitement?

207051.name: The Lady of the Beach
207051.desc: Good day, Commander. I am Formidable, third ship of the Illustrious class. Pleased to make your acquaintance.

207052.name: Timeless Classics
207052.desc: Yes, this will do wonderfully! Thank you, ladies. Phew... Getting dressed is so dreadfully time-consuming... Ahem! How silly of me. I must not whine in the presence of others.

207053.name: The Lover's Heart Flutters On Duty
207053.desc: Good afternoon, Commander. Why am I still in class during lunch break? Heheh, as you can see, I'm on duty. Commander, won't you spend some time with me while I prepare for the next class?

207054.name: Rockin' Encore
207054.desc: Phew... Finally got the scissors... Wait, C-Commander?! Why are you here already?! Close the door quickly and look away... N-no, actually, come and help me untangle this ribbon!

207055.name: Anniversary Memories
207055.desc: To both express my eternal love and gratitude to you and celebrate the wonderful days we've spent together, I will be joining in the port's celebration. ...Ahem, Commander? Tell me the next part!

403150.name: Prinz Eugen μ
403150.desc: I am heavy cruiser idol Prinz Eugen, a participant in the Muse System experiment. You look interested in my outfit, Commander. Heheheh... You can expect my usual exploits and more!

403031.name: Unfading Smile
403031.desc: Relaxing on a float, gently licking my lips... is this really the most popular photo pose for the beach? Wales, you’re not teasing me again, are you?

403032.name: Profusion of Flowers
403032.desc: So this is the Sakura Empire's New Year? Hehe, how interesting~ Commander, since it's the New Year, why don't you put aside all those papers and have a drink with me?

403033.name: Cordial Cornflower
403033.desc: ... Huh? Commander, is that you? Me, drunk? No way... *hic*... If I was, Commander, then what are you planning to do to me? Hehe...

403034.name: Final Lap
403034.desc: Viel Glück~ Are you having a good time, Commander? Just know that the only person I'm cheering for... is you~

403035.name: Kindred Evening Spirits
403035.desc: Guten Abend~ So, what do you think? Pretty great view, right? Hehe, I was talking about the night scenery outside, you know~?

403036.name: Brilliant Touchdown
403036.desc: *pant*... Quarterback Prinz Eugen scores a touchdown. I can't believe I'm the one charging in now... Commander, can you bring me water and a towel? I'm getting a little sticky from all this sweat...

403038.name: Symphonic Fate
403038.desc: If fate brought us together, then it has my thanks… I look forward to our future together~

302240.name: Noshiro μ
302240.desc: Agano-class ship number two, Noshiro, will now begin the Muse System test. I'll put my all into both my idol work and my mission, so you have no reason to worry.

302211.name: Uncharted Festival Grounds?
302211.desc: Just as I thought, this is the perfect place for watching fireworks. You came here thinking that too, didn't you?

302212.name: Xanadu's Eventide
302212.desc: Commander, what are you standing around for? Did you also need a change of pace? That makes two of us— Come, there's nothing to be afraid of here.

302213.name: Fragrance of the Eastern Snow
302213.desc: Whew... Oh, are you cold by any chance? I have some hot tea for you if you'd like. If you want someone to chat with, I'd be glad to keep you company.

302214.name: Cozy Enclave
302214.desc: Why don't you unwind for a bit before you start reflecting on the day's happenings? I'm sure it'll be far more efficient that way.

302215.name: Hold the Ice
302215.desc: Welcom...?! What are you doing here? Wait, don't leave—I was just surprised, that's all... Well, what would you like to order?

302216.name: Unwinding in the Sunshine
302216.desc: ...Take that! Heehee... Ahaha! Phew... I know you don't like admitting defeat, but I got you pretty good there. I might have tried a bit too hard, but I'm pretty sure you were the one who told me to give it my all.

302217.name: Dressed-Up Date
302217.desc: Commander, what do you have planned next...? You want to just relax and enjoy the date? Understood. Umm, let me just try and get a feel for it... Hmm...

302218.name: A Tale of Two Lovers
302218.desc: Receiving everyone's blessings is truly a deeply moving experience. But for now, let's set everything else aside and partake of our sweet bliss. After all, you're not just a spectator anymore– we're in this ride together, hehe~

304080.name: Kongou μ
304080.desc: I'm Kongou, with the Muse System unit Cyanidin. You'll witness my elegance and idol charms, Commander. Heheh, get ready, because you'll never forget the sight of me on stage.

304011.name: The Beauties of Nature
304011.desc: We must fully live in the present, whether during work or during leisure - this is my mantra. Commander, shall we go for an outing together?

304012.name: Hospital Talent
304012.desc: "Celebrity Endorsement of the Port Medical Facilities"... Hehehe, you've made a wise decision picking me. Commander, I can leave the ad shoot to you, right?

304013.name: Breezy Commute
304013.desc: It would be a shame to pass on this lovely weather, Commander. Why have a dull commute by train when you can enjoy a leisurely bicycle ride in the sunlight, hm? Heehee♪

304014.name: Troubled Seas
304014.desc: That was a big wave... I need to balance better on my board, or else... Commander, can I take your hand – Hm? What's slippery? I have no idea what you're... Hyah?! My swimsuit?!

801090.name: Le Téméraire μ
801090.desc: I am the Le Hardi-class destro– Wait, no! Right now, I'm Tem, AKA Le Téméraire, an idol with the unit Cyanidin! Keep your eyes peeled for my debut performance, Commander!

801031.name: Summery Temeraire!
801031.desc: Commander, I've finished changing into my swimsuit! Heheh~ let's head down to the beach and enjoy ourselves as much as we can!

801032.name: Dreamy Dolce
801032.desc: How do I look? These pajamas are super cute, aren't they? Ehehe, I really like this one! It even matches with Opiniâtre's!

801033.name: Cheering Star
801033.desc: Let's go, let's go! Allons-y! Whew... Heehee, you here to watch me rehearse, Commander? Okay, and how was my performance just now? Did that manage to motivate you?

102320.name: Boise μ
102320.desc: I'm Cyanidin light cruiser, Boise... Huff, puff... Umm, does this outfit get your attention better? Good...

102291.name: Sheepish Sapphire
102291.desc: Huff... Puff... Deep breaths... I'll never get used to wearing this outfit in front of others... I think...

102292.name: Castle Tales
102292.desc: Um, I decided to try on a costume, since it's Halloween and all... Do you think I got that witchy look down...?

102293.name: Jade Mermaid
102293.desc: Huff... Puff... These Dragon Empery clothes look good on me? It's rather revealing and breezy, and makes me feel self-conscious... but if you like it, I suppose it's fine...

102294.name: Flawed but Delectable
102294.desc: Commander, did I get ketchup on you? Sorry... Huff, puff... Th-this is the first time I'm letting you see me in a maid outfit, so I'm a little nervous...

307140.name: Shinano-chan
307140.desc: You... are the one this one has seen in my dreams. Wonderful... This one feels relaxed around you... But it seems you need this one's guidance, don't you?

403140.name: Friedrich Carl
403140.desc: I am Friedrich Carl, P-class armored cruiser and the embodiment of love. Come, little one – let us get to the core truth of love and bring happiness to the whole world.

403141.name: A Game of Love
403141.desc: Alright, little one! Now that we have some time off, why don't we play a game? If you win, I might just give you... the reward of love♥

403142.name: Tender Summer Care
403142.desc: Are you ready, my beloved little one? I'm giving you all of me, so apply your love – the sunscreen – ever so thoroughly, so gently, please.

805031.name: Heat-Beating Summer Sacrament
805031.desc: Thish one ish battleship Alsace – a-artifact of the unifuh... guardian of the Holy See, donning summer clothes... One's frame is overheating and the only fix is submersion in water... Aahhh...

901071.name: Locker Room Lechery
901071.desc: Commaaander! I'm struggling with my swimsuit. Come and give me a hand. Oh, that's fine – I locked the door as soon as you came in here. Don't be shy, I'm all yours now... Heheheh♥

901072.name: Olfactory Nursery Call
901072.desc: Commaaander♥ You pressed the call button, so here I am... You don't remember that? Heehee♥ Do you have a fever or something? Gosh, you poor little thing...♥

803021.name: Musician on Blade's Precipice
803021.desc: Swordbearer, you've come at the perfect time. I need your help. Hm? What's with that look on your face? You didn't expect it would be a difficult feat to arrange the clothes you requested I wear, did you...?

901051.name: Up All Knight to Get Lucky
901051.desc: Welcome, welcome! I'm Fleuret, your game master. Are you ready to make a wager? Heehee!

901061.name: Poor, Lonely Knight
901061.desc: Oh, wh-what do I do now... Fleur and the others are doing so well, and I can't even clean a table without messing up... If I worry the Commander, then... Whah?! C-Commander?!

404061.name: Muspel's Torrid Secrets
404061.desc: Oh, Commander. You may have noticed that the air conditioner is busted. I surmised from its volume levels that it was at its limit, but now that it's broken... life has become a struggle.

401471.name: Young-Again Filter
401471.desc: Mandy, you getting distracted? No looking around on my watch. I've put down my phone for once, and I want you to only look at me while we're on the see-saw.

408131.name: Let's Go Home
408131.desc: Why I didn't leave after classes were over? 'Cause I wanted to wait for you to come pick me up, duh! And I waited a looong time! Heehee, now that we're alone... maybe we could do something fun together!

401431.name: A Secret Base For Two
401431.desc: Why can't I wrap this damn bandage... Hnnngh! Ow, ow, ouch! ...Huh? Comma–A-Augur of Destiny, help me! My magic-suppressing bandages have taken on a mind of their own...!

904021.name: Faerie of the Race Circuit
904021.desc: Commander? I can't believe you found me... As you can see, I'm finishing up this car's pre-race checks. If you have time to spare, would you mind lending me a hand? Oh, and of course, keep this a secret between the two of us. I can count on you for that, yes?

901141.name: Protector Beneath the Parasol
901141.desc: Urgh... As a Chevalier, I simply cannot get used to wearing an outfit like this. But, if I tell myself it's for the Commander's sake... Alright! I shall complete today's sacred duties to the utmost of my abilities!

903031.name: Final Check
903031.desc: Good timing, Commander. There are some parameters I need you to check... Come on, this is safety we're talking about. As an inspector, I can't just ignore them. Anyway, come sit next to me so we can get started.

103280.name: Pittsburgh
103280.desc: Baltimore-class heavy cruiser – Pittsburgh, Hull Number CA-72.

103281.name: The Bartender's Gambit
103281.desc: Welcome to the saloon, Commander. Be it drinking juice, or playing games of chance, I'm happy to join you. And I offer more special services, too...

102330.name: Fargo
102330.desc: Fargo-class light cruiser – Fargo, Hull Number CL-106.

102331.name: Dairy in the Dreary Sun
102331.desc: Milk the cows? Okay, I'll give it my best shot. Firsthand experience helps me better emulate emotions, after all... Although, isn't it way too hot outside for milking?

108090.name: Herring
108090.desc: Gato-class submarine – Herring, Hull Number SS-233.

108091.name: The Town With No Shade
108091.desc: Well, well. I was wondering who owns this polite little horsy – surprise, it's you! How about you trade me 'em for a blown kiss? And if you catch up with me, you can have the rest of me for free♪ Mwah♡

101520.name: Bell
101520.desc: Fletcher-class destroyer – Bell, Hull Number DD-587.

101521.name: Saloon Mishaps
101521.desc: Welcome to our saloon... Oh, no! I can't hold all these mugs! ...C-Commander? Why are you here?

307151.name: Throne of Fallen Petals
307151.desc: So you've finally come, Commander. I have been waiting for you— Ahem. Heehee, please step forward. In this castle of dreams, this throne... belongs to you and me equally.

302251.name: Garments of Everlasting Magic
302251.desc: Commander! Oh... Umm, perhaps it would be more fitting to address you as "Milord" for this occasion? Since, you know, the two of us have the evening together... Now, if you don't mind, your hand please — Heehee, make sure to sit tight!

302261.name: A Glimpse of the Moon Rabbit
302261.desc: C-Commander?! ...H-huh? It's already p-past the scheduled time? Awawa... B-but, I still haven't finished changing yet... I, umm... P-please give me just a minute!

301911.name: Winter Beauty's Ball Gown
301911.desc: Sorry for calling you here this early, Commander... I was just hoping you could check if I'm wearing my dress right. I'm not a dress person, so...

9600071.name: Mermaid in Distress
9600071.desc: You heard my song? Thank goodness... Someone has finally come for me! Say, could you please remove the seal on me?

9600081.name: Grave of Your Liking
9600081.desc: Oh... You've found me. This is horror fashion, and I've heard it's pretty popular. Boo. Scared?

9600091.name: Friendly Franken
9600091.desc: Well, well, look who's got nowhere left to go. Kidding, kidding. I win again, so I'll be taking your treasure! Follow me down if you're brave enough to jump.

9600101.name: Adventurous Surprise
9600101.desc: Wait, Commander?! You're here way ahead of time! N-no, this is NOT what my special surprise is supposed to be!

9600111.name: Incantation of Revival
9600111.desc: *yaaawn*... Was it you who awoke me? Heehee, thanks. Oh, don't be scared! Sure, rising out of a coffin is a bit creepy... but still, I'm not going to hurt you. Promise.

407040.name: Fritz Rumey
407040.desc: Grossflugzeugkreuzer (large aviation cruiser) A Type II – Fritz Rumey.

407041.name: Schwarzes Kaninchen
407041.desc: Hm? It's you. Surprised by my appearance? Hmm... My apologies. I was thinking about how to rectify discipline inside the shop. At any rate, welcome.

401521.name: The Rapid Rabbit
401521.desc: Let's see... Where's the shop again? It should be... Oh, Commander! I'm not late, am I? I ran here as fast as I could!

402111.name: Endurance Training (Gone Wrong)
402111.desc: C-Commander... Huh? If we're training, I should call you Master...? M-Master... You don't have to stare. Let's just get started, please...

401091.name: Teary Cocktail
401091.desc: Commander, umm... Would you like to try our new drink? It's very sweet and tasty... Ahh, why am I so nervous? I need to do better...

401110.name: Z11
401110.desc: Type 1934A destroyer – Z11 Bernd von Arnim.

401111.name: Service, Sincerity, and Insolvency
401111.desc: I wanted to help at the pop-up shop so I could buy a special-edition game, but I ended up in debt somehow. Commander, help... I'll do anything...

503011.name: Dressed for Just Tonight
503011.desc: There's still time. Let's set out once I've finished adjusting my dress... If you have nothing better to do, at least put on some tea.

503012.name: Dressed for Just Tonight
503012.desc: Don't just stare – help me... Look, I meant that in the "help me balance" sense... Are you trying to take my shoes off?

502100.name: Hai Yung
502100.desc: Hai Yung-class protected cruiser – Hai Yung.

502101.name: Maple Impressions
502101.desc: Very well, Commander, I'll leave the photography to you. I entrust you to capture my grace and elegance and record it into memory! Just so you're clear though, th-this is just an outfit that's in vogue... It's not like I chose to wear it for you or anything!

501081.name: Cozy Spring Cleaning
501081.desc: Oh, Commander~ Please give me a moment; Fei Yuen, Fu Po, and I are still finishing up our spring cleaning. Why don't you come inside for now and have some warm tea?

501082.name: A Sky Blue Eclipsing Jade
501082.desc: Commander, this is the new Ru-ware tea set I just purchased. Absolutely beautiful, isn't it? We have a custom to bring out the best things for those you care about, which is why I decided to invite you~♪

501091.name: Mischievous Tidings
501091.desc: Oh... Well, shoot, you found me... Shhhhh! Don't tell anyone that I'm here though! Seriously, Commander, I'm begging you!

605081.name: Protector of Love and Beauty
605081.desc: Heheh! You were not invited to this place, and as its guardian, I must punish you by... Oh, wait, wait, stop! This angle... This outline... It's simply perfect! Turning you into stone would be a waste, so just stay here and let me observe you every day!

608031.name: The God Craves Punishment
608031.desc: Oh, I wasn't expecting that you'd come here, Commander. As the God of Death, I will have to pass "judgment" on you♪

601111.name: Verses in Balance
601111.desc: Traveler from afar, allow me to pen a welcoming verse with this dance... Why'd I stop? Umm... S-silence is golden, as they say...

602031.name: The Empress' Romantic Ambush
602031.desc: Hrmm... Romance novel analysis shows that this pose is the most likely to succeed... Ah. C-Commander, there you are... Ahem. "What business do you have in my private chambers?"

107130.name: Franklin
107130.desc: Essex-class aircraft carrier – Franklin, Hull Number CV-13.

107131.name: Heart-Throbbing Records
107131.desc: Phew... Sorry I took so long, Commander. I'll be your examiner today. Ah, you're wondering how good I am as a nurse? Heehee. Let's just say you'll find out by... touch♡

102340.name: Santa Fe
102340.desc: Cleveland-class light cruiser – Santa Fe, Hull Number CL-60.

102341.name: The Rumor Mill Never Sleeps
102341.desc: Huh? You're already in bed, Commander? Come on, it's time for late-night gossip! Nyahaha! Let me slip into bed with you so we can chat the night away!

101530.name: Miller
101530.desc: Fletcher-class destroyer – Miller, Hull Number DD-535.

101531.name: Monster Experiment M-01
101531.desc: Don't move, Commander! ...Heheh, looks like it's time for the GOAT to take the stage. That was a sick entrance, right?! Hm? N-no, I'm not here to help you out! I'm here to, uhh... Yeah, to take revenge on the scientists who experimented on me!

705091.name: The Warm Morning Sunshine
705091.desc: Ah, you're up, Commander. Heehee. Good morning. It's so sunny today that even the kitchen is a bit hot. That's okay, though – I've made a refreshing breakfast for you. Go wash your face, then it's time to dig in.

1102010.name: De Zeven Provinciën
1102010.desc: De Zeven Provinciën-class light cruiser – De Zeven Provinciën.

1102011.name: Snuggling for Warmth
1102011.desc: Good morning, Commander. Did you sleep well? Oh, there are petals in your hair. I'll get them for you~

1101011.name: Basking by the Window
1101011.desc: Commander, relax wherever you like. ...Why so far? You won't get any sun there.

702081.name: Repose by the Fireplace
702081.desc: *yaaawn*... Nothing beats relaxing after a nice bath! Now that I've changed into my warm pajamas, what should we do next? Hm? Go to sleep? No, no, it's too early. I only yawned because I was getting comfortable!

201381.name: Sea Breeze, Moonlit Talks
201381.desc: The breeze is nice, isn't it? Do you want to have a drink with me? (This is exactly how my movies go, so this should work... Is my face too stiff?)

202351.name: Stars and Roses
202351.desc: Ah, Master, welcome. How do you like the set I put together? Has your heart been stolen? This book describes how the gods arrange their rooms when they look upon the stars... It's not quite a perfect replica, but isn't it pretty?

201391.name: Express-ive Delivery
201391.desc: Can you see me, Commander? I'm here to deliver your takeaway and a parcel! I've already made sure there's no danger out here – oh, and look, my ID! Just like the staff regulations stipulate! Come on, it's safe to open the door!

202361.name: Trapper in the Changing Room
202361.desc: Oh dear... You found me already? Here I thought I'd surprise you with my swimsuit... Oh well, what's done is done. Wanna go swimming? And don't worry, I'm as gentle as they get when I play the instructor♪

10100010.name: Neptune
10100010.desc: Heya! My name's Neptune! Nice to meet you!

10100020.name: Noire
10100020.desc: Are you the commander? Hmm... Very well. I'm Noire. The CPU of Lastation. You can put your mind at ease now that I'm here.

10100030.name: Blanc
10100030.desc: I'm Blanc. Nice to meet you. Maybe you could introduce some intriguing books from this world to me...

10100040.name: Vert
10100040.desc: My name is Vert, I am the CPU of Leanbox. I'm very good at first-person shooters, so please let me handle all combat-related matters!

10100050.name: Purple Heart
10100050.desc: I am Purple Heart, the CPU of Planeptune. And you must be the commander. I will follow your orders from now.

10100051.name: Goddesses' Promise
10100051.desc: Oh, Commander? Won't you join me in a short conversation? I'll tell you things about Planeptune. Oh, and I'm eagerly awaiting the day you come to Planeptune for a visit.

10100060.name: Black Heart
10100060.desc: I'm the CPU of Lastation, Black Heart. I've rushed here all the way from Gamindustri to lend you my aid. Be grateful.

10100061.name: Goddesses' Smile
10100061.desc: It's good to take it easy and celebrate once in a while, but especially in moments like these, you can't afford to let your guard down. Commander, why don't we spar for a bit? Don't even think about holding back - come at me!

10100070.name: White Heart
10100070.desc: I'm White Heart, the guardian CPU of Lowee. Pleased to meet you. I'm gonna give you a taste of a CPU's power!

10100071.name: Goddesses' Humility
10100071.desc: B-bastard! Where are you looking? I bet you're thinking I look like a kid! Eh....? They're just right? If Commander says something like that... I don't know how to react...

10100080.name: Green Heart
10100080.desc: I am the CPU of Leanbox, Green Heart. No matter who the enemy is, I will not hold back. Are you ready?

10100081.name: Goddesses' Moment
10100081.desc: Commander, are you having a good time? Ehehe, I certainly am. It's not often that we get to relax like this. Why don't we head out and enjoy the breeze?

10400010.name: Kizuna AI
10400010.desc: HAI DOMO! Kizuna AI here! Are you the commander I've heard rumors about? It's a pleasure to meet and work with you!

10400011.name: Festive Kizuna AI
10400011.desc: The clothes from the Sakura Empire are so stylish! Commander, since it's a rare occasion, let's go take a look around! Ah, of course, don't forget to run the reel~♪

10400020.name: Elegant Kizuna AI
10400020.desc: Well met. I'm Kizuna AI, the new addition to your base. I will do all in my power to be at least of some use. It is a pleasure meeting you, Commander.

10400030.name: Anniversary Kizuna AI
10400030.desc: Kizuna AI here, wearing a dress, coming at you! Be it concert or combat, I'll give it my all!

10400040.name: Super Gamer Kizuna AI
10400040.desc: HAI DOMO! Virtual Gamer Kizuna AI here! Don't worry, Commander, I've played AL a whole bunch before! ... Wait, I've become a ship now?!

10500010.name: Shirakami Fubuki
10500010.desc: We meet at last! I'm Hololive's virtual fox, Shirakami Fubuki! Commander, now that you've called me, we're gonna have a foxin' good time! Now then, let's get to work!

10500011.name: Beachside Fox
10500011.desc: Tada~! It's your favorite Shirakami Fubuki, Hololive Summer version! Commander, pleased to be your fox!

10500020.name: Tokino Sora
10500020.desc: Hey Commander, it's nice to meet you~! I'm Tokino Sora, a virtual idol affiliated with Hololive! I'll do my absolute best here like I always do! I'll be in your care, so cheer me on, Commander!

10500021.name: Under the Clear Sky
10500021.desc: "Hello, my friends! I hope you're well~! This is Sora, on site at a beach in a slightly different world!" Beach visits just feel so invigorating, don't they? On another note, I can't swim…

10500030.name: Minato Aqua
10500030.desc: G-Good Aquafternoon...! I'm Minato Aqua, the Gamer Maid from Hololive~ U-Ugh... I didn't know I would have to introduce myself in this outfit!

10500031.name: Marine Maid
10500031.desc: Commander, good Aquafternoon~! Nice to meet you, it's Aqua, the Gamer Maid from Hololive! I'll show ya what the strongest maid can do!

10500040.name: Natsuiro Matsuri
10500040.desc: I'm the lovely high school girl affiliated with Hololive, Natsuiro Matsuri!! I love singing and having all kinds of lively conversations with people, so make sure to keep your eyes on me!

10500041.name: Matsuri's Day Off
10500041.desc: I'm the lovely high school girl, now in her extra-pure pajamas, Natsuiro Matsuri! Hey hey, Commander, what do you think? Surprised? Don't gawk at me too much~

10500050.name: Nakiri Ayame
10500050.desc: Be cheery, for here's Nakiri! Ay am Nakiri Ayame, Hololive's virtual demon! Ay have come from the great beyond with my accompanying spirits!

10500051.name: Summertime Nakiri
10500051.desc: Be cheery, for here's Nakiri~! Ay am not used to this outfit and am a little embarrassed... But Ay am Nakiri Ayame, Hololive's virtual demon!

10500060.name: Murasaki Shion
10500060.desc: I am the mastermind magician, Murasaki Shion! Come and be bewitched by my mature, seductive outfit!

10500061.name: Virtual Magician
10500061.desc: Here comes Murasaki Shion, Hololive's famous virtual magician! This world will bear witness to my brilliance!

10500070.name: Ookami Mio
10500070.desc: Good Miovening! I'm Ookami Mio. Over here, I seem to be... some sort of aircraft carrier. Let's get along well.

10500071.name: Summer Vacation
10500071.desc: I changed into my swimsuit, but I wonder if it looks right on me? An outfit like this might make you feel breezier just by looking at it~

10600010.name: Marie Rose
10600010.desc: Hello! Oh... What am I supposed to call you? "Commander"? Got it! My name is Marie Rose. Just call me Marie, okay? I'm counting on your support, Commander!

10600011.name: Devilish Servant Against the Splashing Waves
10600011.desc: Hmm, this swimsuit is pretty cute, but isn't it a bit childish? ...In any case, if you like it, then it's all good!

10600012.name: Steamy Venus
10600012.desc: Phew... So warm and comfy~♪ Wanna join me, Commander? Oh... It's a little embarrassing, though, so... Don't look my way too much, okay?

10600020.name: Honoka
10600020.desc: Um... Are you the Commander? Oh, perfect! It's nice to meet you. My name is Honoka! I don't know how much I'll be able to help, but... let's be friends!

10600021.name: Summer Angel on the Shore
10600021.desc: Whoa, the sea is so pretty~! It's as beautiful as the Venus Islands! I'm so blown away, I don't even feel the heat anymore!

10600030.name: Kasumi
10600030.desc: Are you the Owner of the port? The "Commander"? Hello. My name is Kasumi, I'll be staying here for the foreseeable future. I hope we can both get along on friendly terms.

10600031.name: Springside Mist
10600031.desc: I was amazed to see the port had such a scenic place as this... Truly, you can't go without taking this view in. Right, Commander?

10600040.name: Misaki
10600040.desc: It's nice to meet you! From what I've heard, you're the "Commander," right? I'm Misaki. I have experience with various part-time jobs, so... I'm confident that I can be of help to you all. Let's do our best!

10600041.name: Golden Photoshoot
10600041.desc: A photoshoot? That'd be similar to what I did before coming here, but... um, this swimsuit is a bit much... Commander, is this what you're into? Geez... It's so embarrassing...

10600050.name: Nagisa
10600050.desc: Are you the person who led Misaki to this port? You go by the name... "Commander"? Hmm... I don't know how you sweet-talked her into it, but you're not fooling me. The moment you do anything strange... you better be on guard! My name? It's Nagisa. You... silly dog!

10600051.name: Blue Skies, Good Vibes
10600051.desc: Whew! The wind feels great! ...What are you staring at me like that for, you silly dog? You're the one who said you wanted to go to the beach, remember? To start with, how about... we take a stroll?

10600060.name: Nyotengu
10600060.desc: Oh? You don't seem to fear me... Who might you be? ...I see, so it is you who rules over this place. Then I shall call you "Commander." I am Nyotengu. You would do best to keep me entertained, hehe.

10600061.name: Scarlet-Tinged Hot Spring Vacation
10600061.desc: Oho! To think there was a place with this much class... Not bad! I shall hereby be enjoying my hot springs vacation right here, hehehe.

10600070.name: Monica
10600070.desc: Are you the one in charge here? The "Commander"? I'm Monica, the dealer! Well, dealer-in-training. I know it's sudden, but would you care to gamble with me? The stakes will, of course, be high!

10600071.name: The Ace of Hearts
10600071.desc: "Welcome to Monica's Fantabulous Casino! Where you can have your every whim satisfied!" ...Oh, that doesn't sound very casino-managery? Heheh!

10600080.name: Luna
10600080.desc: H-hmm... Wh-where am I? ...Me? I'm Luna, a scholar. Umm... You go by the Commander? Well, I'm hungry... Do you have anything to eat? I'd prefer roasted sweet potatoes...

10600081.name: Venus of the Beach
10600081.desc: Hmm... Commander, I'm tired from all this frolicking. How about we take a break, or have a snack? You know, nobody knows we're all alone right here... Heehee~♪

10600090.name: Tamaki
10600090.desc: Hmm? Where am I? Ohh, I get it now... I drank way too much yesterday... Ahahah. Oh well♪ There's tons of cuties here to keep me entertained❤ My name's Tamaki. It's a pleasure, Commander❤

10600091.name: Venus Shower Time
10600091.desc: Heehee~ I've been waiting, Commander♪ Come on, there's no need to be shy♥ I'm going to show you a lovely time, darling, so you'd better get ready♪

10700010.name: Haruka Amami
10700010.desc: Hello, Commander! I'm the idol, Haruka Amami! I'll do my best to share my dreams with everyone in port! Let's all have a great time together!

10700011.name: A Taste of Tranquility
10700011.desc: Good evening, Commander! Are you also taking a break? If so, let's go get some candied apples and have a little chat~♪

10700020.name: Chihaya Kisaragi
10700020.desc: Pleased to meet you. My name is Chihaya Kisaragi. Are you the one in charge of this port? I look forward to working with you.

10700021.name: Reflections of Heavenly Flowers
10700021.desc: Oh, the fireworks display is starting. I'm planning to meet up with the others after this, but... Why don't we spend some time enjoying the view here first?

10700030.name: Iori Minase
10700030.desc: Hello, hello~! My name is Iori Minase! It's such a pleasure to meet you! ...Huh? There's no need for me to force myself...? Hey, wait a second, what do you mean by that?!

10700031.name: A Little Evening Secret
10700031.desc: Blowing bubbles while sitting on a swing... It might seem a bit childish, but there's nothing wrong with enjoying activities like these every so often.

10700040.name: Azusa Miura
10700040.desc: Why hello, my name's Azusa Miura~ Um, this is a port, right? And these are... shipgirls? Um~ Where exactly am I?

10700041.name: Midsummer Relaxation
