10700041.desc: Listening to the wind flow through the chimes on the porch seems to carry the summer heat right away. Commander, would you also like to come unwind with me?

10700050.name: Ritsuko Akizuki
10700050.desc: Pleased to meet you. My name is Ritsuko Akizuki. I was wondering what was going to happen to me when I suddenly got blown away, but... In any case, I'm pleased to make your acquaintance!

10700051.name: Paddle Showdown - Summer Formation
10700051.desc: Sorry, what? A paddle showdown? Commander, please... You play that in a kimono, not a yutaka. But if you insist... If I win, you're buying me an ice cream!

10700060.name: Ami Futami
10700060.desc: Nihihi! I'm the idol, Ami Futami! This place seems awfully lively, just perfect for pranking~! See you around, Commander!

10700061.name: Summer Flowers and Sizzling Beats
10700061.desc: Summer's all about the festivals, and Ami Futami's the queen of festivals! Even the fireworks soaring through the sky can't hold a candle to how brilliant Ami is, so keep your eyes on me, Commander~♪

10700070.name: Mami Futami
10700070.desc: Nihihi~♪ I'm the idol, Mami Futami! You'll get to feast your eyes on how alluring Mami is, so look forward to it, Commander~!

10700071.name: Alluring Festival
10700071.desc: Woah~! They're starting to send up the huge fireworks! ...Hey, Commander, just where are you looking? Did Mami's alluring yukata make you go crazy with desire~?

10800010.name: Rikka Takarada
10800010.desc: Um, my name is Rikka Takarada. I'm still a bit confused about what's going on, but... I guess for the time being, I'm in good hands.

10800011.name: Blue Sky Station
10800011.desc: The train still isn't here yet? ...Oh, what a coincidence to see you here, Commander. Where were you headed?

10800012.name: Bedroom Attire
10800012.desc: Ack, Commander?! Geez, look, I at least want to be able to relax in my own room. Let it go just this once, okay?

10800020.name: Akane Shinjo
10800020.desc: Hey there, the name's Akane Shinjo. This rigging looks super cool, like it's right out of a mecha. Now if only there were some kaiju around, that'd be the best...

10800021.name: A Vacation Just for Two
10800021.desc: Welcome back, Commander. You sure brought a lot of goodies back for me, huh? Now then, don't just keep standing there, hurry and come to me~

10800022.name: Room of Secrets
10800022.desc: Hey, Commander, what's up~? You're not intoxicated by my good looks, are you? Pssh, lighten up, I'm kidding~

10800030.name: Hass
10800030.desc: Hello, I'm Hass. I was suddenly blown away to this strange place... But, I guess it seems interesting enough here. By the way, is it okay to shoot some videos here?

10800031.name: Seaside Scoop!
10800031.desc: Hass here. Tonight, we're going to take a walk around the port at night. Aaaand, we even have a special guest– the Commander! ...Psst, hey, look at the camera real quick!

10800040.name: Namiko
10800040.desc: Heyyo, it's Namiko! Uhh, wait, is this that whole getting-reincarnated-in-another-world thing that's been super popular? ...It's not, huh. Well, in any case, nice to meet you!

10800041.name: Miss Street-Wise
10800041.desc: Woo, you're here! So, how was it? This meeting spot was pretty easy to find, right? Welp, let's get going then!

10800050.name: Yume Minami
10800050.desc: Hello, my name is Yume Minami. I've ended up in this world for whatever reason. I'll do my best to contribute to the fleet as a heavy cruiser.

10800051.name: A Dream Upon an Open Windowsill
10800051.desc: How lovely. From here, you can see across the entire port, as well as the shimmering ocean... Oh, Commander, here to enjoy the view with me?

10800052.name: Morning Routine
10800052.desc: You're wondering why I'm so carefree? Uhh... Because I'm comfortable with you... Let's leave it at that.

10800060.name: Chise Asukagawa
10800060.desc: Woahhh, I somehow ended up in a totally unknown place... Oh, um, my name's Chise Asukagawa! Since I might be here for a while, thanks for looking after me!

10800061.name: Together, Swimming through the Sky
10800061.desc: Woaah, the sun's coming out! It feels so great outside after the rain... Oh, Commander! Let's take a stroll through the sky together!

10800062.name: Laundry Day
10800062.desc: Aww man, I hate to be seen in such a lazy-looking outfit. It's embarrassing, y'know~?

10800070.name: Mujina
10800070.desc: Kaiju Eugenicist, Mujina. I suppose I'm a battleship now. Just asking to be sure... There are no kaiju in your world, correct?

10800071.name: Golden Promenade
10800071.desc: You've come as well, Commander? In that case, let's accompany each other back while watching the gingko leaves fall.

10800080.name: The 2nd
10800080.desc: Oh, where am I now... Ah. Good to meet you. Call me The 2nd. I'm with the Gridknight Alliance... Not that it matters in this world, I'd assume.

10800081.name: Private Time
10800081.desc: Would you mind waiting a moment? I just have this one report. Oh, and can I interest you in coffee, Commander? Ah... Sorry, this is my only mug. We could... share it?

10800090.name: Princess Hime
10800090.desc: What? Where am I? Oh, umm, what may you need of me, young one? ...You don't need anything? Ahahah... Well met, person from this strange land. My name is... You know what, just call me "Princess Hime."

10800091.name: Nightcap Time
10800091.desc: Oh! Guess you found me... Look, it doesn't matter what I wear when I'm drinking at home... What's that? Does me being a bit flushed from the drinks really get you that fired up?

10900011.name: Late-Night Alchemist
10900011.desc: Hey there, Commander! Hehe, it's been a long while since I had a sleepover with someone. You know, I've really been looking forward to today. So, what would you like to do first?

10900021.name: Bedtime Memories
10900021.desc: Hehe, today was such a fun day... Oh, good evening, Commander. I was just writing my diary entry for the day. Since you're here, why don't you help me out?

10900031.name: Rest Betwixt Dreams and Reality
10900031.desc: Phew, that's everything taken care of for the day... Huh?! Commander, how long have you been there?! I-I apologize for letting you see my slovenly side... Please, just come over here for now.

10900041.name: Moonlit Encounter
10900041.desc: You shouldn't be up this late. What, you can't sleep? You want to stay up with me? ...Fine, I'll keep you company. I haven't been able to get a wink of sleep anyway.

10900051.name: Fairy Dreamer Beneath the Starry Sky
10900051.desc: An elegant verdure, a pellucid azure. I never knew there was such a lovely place at this port... Oh Commander, are you also out on a nighttime stroll?

11000010.name: Asuka
11000010.desc: Hello! I'm Asuka, second-year student at the Hanzō Academy! Wait... this isn't the new shinobi base at all! This place is your port, you say? Okay then... Well, no matter where I end up, I'll always train as best as I can!

11000011.name: Blue Oceans
11000011.desc: Blue skies, white sands, and oceans that stretch as far as the eye can see... I've seen this on TV before – this place is heaven on earth! Thanks so much for inviting me here, Commander! Now, it's time to have fun!

11000020.name: Ikaruga
11000020.desc: I am Ikaruga, a third-year student at the Hanzō National Academy, serving as the shinobi class representative. How should I conduct myself in this foreign place? I would be most grateful if you would provide me with your assistance.

11000021.name: A Moment of Peace
11000021.desc: Wow! The fish are so cute! The water's so clear that you can see everything under the waves! I've never seen an ocean like this before, and being able to relax while rocking back and forth on the water... is just like one of those "vacation paradises" I've read about in various books!

11000030.name: Homura
11000030.desc: My name's Homura. I'm the leader of Homura's Crimson Squad. I was once affiliated with a school, like many others, but... stuff happened. Anyway, don't let that bother you.

11000031.name: The Shinobi Angler
11000031.desc: Fish! Heheh, that's a biggun! We'll be eating good tonight... Wait, I guess I don't need to worry about food now. Old habits die hard, it seems... Commander! Hey! I know you're over there! I'm gonna let you have a taste, so stop staring all enviously like that!

11000040.name: Yumi
11000040.desc: I am Yumi, third-year student at the Gessen Girls' Academy. Though I know not why I was brought here, I am committed to justice, no matter where I go.

11000041.name: Afternoon Teatime
11000041.desc: Here, Commander – shaved ice. Say "aah"... Heehee. I've not fed someone like this many times before, so please don't get mad in the event that I spill some.

11000050.name: Fubuki
11000050.desc: I am named Fubuki. I try to keep out of the public eye, so how have I wound up in this strange place? Also, you may want to leave me to my own devices. If you wonder why, well...

11000051.name: Sunset Witch
11000051.desc: Ohh, it's so wonderful, being in the calm water with you, Commander... Eek! What's this?! A fish hook's caught on to me... Please stop reeling it in, or my swimsuit will untie itself!

11000060.name: Murasaki
11000060.desc: I'm Murasaki... from Hebijo Clandestine Girls' Academy. Umm... what is this place? I'd like to go home now... The outdoors are scary...

11000061.name: The Shut-In Princess's Lament
11000061.desc: When you're in a swimsuit, listening to the waves, eating ice cream, and playing a beach game... can't you say it counts as being on the beach, even if you're indoors?

11000070.name: Yūyaki
11000070.desc: My name is Yūyaki... and I'm the leader of the Tohno Tengu Shinobi Group... To be honest, I'm not great around water... Bad things always happen when I'm around it... And this place is a whole ocean, right? What should I do...?

11000071.name: Blue Sky Lagoon
11000071.desc: Phew... Nothing beats a cold shower. I'm still not great with water, but this cool and soothing sensation really makes me feel refreshed. Commander, do you want to join in?

11100010.name: Lala Satalin Deviluke
11100010.desc: I'm Lala, and I'm from Planet Deviluke. What's your name? ...Just call you Commander? Okay, Commander, it's great to meet you!

11100011.name: A Princess Imprisoned
11100011.desc: Go Go Vacuum-kun might be malfunctioning a little, hehe... But I'll fix it right away, so don't worry!

11100020.name: Nana Astar Deviluke
11100020.desc: Uh-huh, so you're the Commander? I'm Nana, Lala's little sister. This port you've got here is pretty lively... Well, it was nice meeting you.

11100021.name: High Roller
11100021.desc: There you are, Commander. I'm on a real hot streak today! Wanna come play with us and test your skills?

11100030.name: Momo Belia Deviluke
11100030.desc: Hi there. You're the Commander of this port, right? I'm Momo Belia Deviluke, but you can just call me Momo. I look forward to fighting with you, and I hope we'll be best friends♪

11100031.name: A Waking Dream
11100031.desc: Oh my, Commander. Did I wake you? You didn't look very restful... Were you having a nightmare? Don't worry. Everything's okay now~

11100040.name: Golden Darkness
11100040.desc: I'm Golden Darkness. Pleasured to make your acquaintance.

11100041.name: Pajama Status: On
11100041.desc: Commander, why have you entered without my express permission? Prepare to die.

11100050.name: Haruna Sairenji
11100050.desc: Nice to meet you, Commander. My name is Haruna Sairenji. I'm going to be in your care for a while, but if there's anything you need my help with, don't hesitate to ask!

11100051.name: On One Serene Night
11100051.desc: I made some black tea, Commander. We could drink it together, if you'd like...? These are my favorite tea leaves.

11100060.name: Yui Kotegawa
11100060.desc: Are you the Commander? I'm Yui Kotegawa, and I'm pleased to make your acquaintance. Some strange circumstances brought me here... But if I'm to intrude on your port, then I promise to uphold discipline in return!

11100061.name: The Disciplinarian's Day Off
11100061.desc: Come on over, I'm not scary~... Wha, Commander?! H-hey... don't go barging into people's rooms! Look, you're scaring my new friend!

11200010.name: BLACK★ROCK SHOOTER
11200010.desc: Are you... my enemy? No... I don't sense hostility, but instead, strong willpower. So this world is full of struggle, too. You are... the Commander? I am BLACK★ROCK SHOOTER, and I will protect you.

11200011.name: Goddess in Black
11200011.desc: The babbling of brooks and the crashing of waves were once such minor things to me. As people who do battle on the sea, you all must see something greater in them, too. But I wonder... if this swimsuit isn't very well-suited for combat.

11200020.name: DEAD MASTER
11200020.desc: Now where exactly am I? Hmm... Well, this is a mess, isn't it? I want you to tell me everything, but if I'm here, then she must be, too... Oh, don't worry about it. I'm DEAD MASTER, and I guess I'm sticking with you for a while. There's got to be a good reason I'm here, after all.

11200021.name: Warrior's Respite
11200021.desc: Oh? Commander, stop staring and come over here. Let's have a cup of tea and relax... Huh? You're concerned about my outfit? Aren't swimsuits common sights here, or am I special somehow?

299011.name: Princess of the Reindeers
299011.desc: Hehe~ I usually let the other girls have all the glory, but even I must sometimes give you something to remember me by. Merry Christmas, Commander~

299012.name: Nereid's Invitation
299012.desc: Welcome to our celebration, Commander. At this breathtaking venue, I, Neptune, shall be the one to show you around, rather than the Royal Maids. Heehee~♪

299021.name: White Warrick
299021.desc: Hmph. One's outfit is merely superficial. True nobility must come from within. Don't you agree, Commander?

299022.name: Black Gerard
299022.desc: So, an Eastern outfit this time... Hmph. My nobility is evident regardless of what I wear. However, since you prepared this outfit especially for me, it would be unbecoming of me to not express my gratitude. Thank you.

299023.name: Detective Arriving on the Scene
299023.desc: This common thief – calls herself "PhantoM" – is running circles around the Metropolitan Police. Now they've come to me for help... Bet they never thought this day would come when they demoted me to the sticks. On the bright side, we get to detect side by side again.

299024.name: Sovereign of the Beach
299024.desc: Whew... Surely now one can argue that I'm "enjoying the beach," yes? ...Still not enough? I am laying my exposed self bare before you – what more is there I need to do?

399011.name: Winter Sylph's Reverie
399011.desc: Milord, it's starting to snow... If it suits you, please take shelter under Ibuki's umbrella.

399012.name: Snow on the Wind
399012.desc: This is my first time wearing Western clothes... Um, Milord! Does this outfit... suit Ibuki well...?

399013.name: Arrival of Spring
399013.desc: The Dragon Empery's "Spring Festival" is... filled with fun, liveliness, and pure jubilation. I can feel my true feelings welling up... Maybe, an environment like this would suit me pretty well...

399014.name: Tranquil Sunya
399014.desc: I'm glad you've returned, Milord. I've changed my attire in order to better carry out your order–for us to "relax together." Now then... could you please instruct me on how to proceed?

399021.name: Izumo's Thousand Cherry Trees
399021.desc: You'd like to see my classical dance? Your tastes are quite refined, Commander... In that case, I'll show you the finest performance in the land!

499011.name: Dark Red Grin
499011.desc: Such a delightful party with our wonderful friends in this peaceful harbor... It's wonderful, really... But, it's all so boring...

499012.name: Viridescent Lullaby
499012.desc: It's so nice getting away from the bustling party hall and being alone with you, Commander. I'm eager to see what we'll do now as your idea of a... "break"~

899011.name: Holy Knight's Resplendence
899011.desc: With all due respect, Commander, this finery and this throne are not fit for one such as myself. Despite the hallowed name I have inherited, I am nothing more than a warrior. —However, if such an arrangement pleases you, then I shall hold my objections.

899012.name: Alluring Administrator
899012.desc: Commander, regarding your next appointment... Ah, hard work is one of the highest virtues of the Iris's holy knights. On weekdays or vacations, in knights' armor or the Dragon Empery's attire, there can be no pause to my prayer, my training, or my duties as the administrator of your will.

199011.name: Gorgeous Party
199011.desc: Hey! Great to have you here, Commander! I've gotta ask, whaddya think of my dress? Looking real gorgeous, right? ...Phew, awesome! I was worried my dress didn't look nice and might be dragging down the party mood, that's all!

199012.name: Christmas Party Prep!
199012.desc: Meeeerry Christmas~! Even though the party is about to start, as you can see, I'm still getting ready~ Just gimme a moment, all righty~?

199013.name: Sunfish Spell!
199013.desc: Supportive sorceress Seattle, comin' in hot! So, something got you down, my good pal? I'm up to talk about whatever's on your mind, but in return, you've gotta come to my party tonight!

199021.name: South Town Pearl
199021.desc: Oh? Commander, did you need to get some fresh air as well? Me? Ahaha... It's a bit too stiff inside that venue, so I came out for a change of pace. Why don't we take a little stroll together?

199022.name: Lanier Swan
199022.desc: Heh heh, the warm sun and the sea breeze really hit the spot, don't they? Alright, let's get out there and enjoy ourselves! That's what you've been waiting for, right, Commander?

199023.name: Exalted Vibrance
199023.desc: Happy New Year, Commander! I guess you dress up all flashy like this for the Sakura New Year. Would you escort me...? What are you gawking like that for...? Haha, am I so dazzling? Hahaha!

399031.name: Celebration Conquest!
399031.desc: All the preparations are now complete... Commander, let us sally forth and conquer these festival grounds! ...But before that, can we get something to eat first?

399033.name: Night of Doves and Magic
399033.desc: Mm, preparations complete. If I keep it up, the production will surely be a great success. The doves have been on their best behavior too. Commander, what do you think about Kitakaze's magic show?

399041.name: Soft Voice of Spring
399041.desc: Commander? Oh, I haven't quite finished changing. My hair still needs work... Sorry, would you mind waiting a bit longer?

399048.name: Lily-White Longing
399048.desc: I must be dreaming, to be able to don this white veil... Haha, though, what's more important is our life together afterwards! Commander, please look forward to the rich fruit of my bridal training~

499021.name: Dark Raiments of Gagaku
499021.desc: I see, so this is a "kimono" from the Sakura Empire. Exquisitely crafted, comfortable to the touch, and elegantly designed... How to wear it? ...My child, what are you talking about?

499022.name: One Summer Night's Intimacy
499022.desc: Welcome, my child. What do you desire tonight? That which ripples in my cup? This sweet, red fruit? Or to sate the desires sleeping deep, deep in your heart?

499028.name: Zeremonie of the Cradle
499028.desc: Ahh, the dreamlike beauty of this variation... let us write down this movement so that it may continue forever, my sweet child.

999011.name: Tropical Environs Acclimation Service Equipment
999011.desc: Gascogne uniform change complete. Directive assigned: have fun on the beach with Master. Requesting detailed instructions for how to "have fun on the beach."

299031.name: Summery Date!
299031.desc: Cheer up, Owner! Jeez, why are you so bummed out when we're at the beach... Because it's just a normal playdate instead of a romantic date? What's the difference anyway? C'mon, let's go head down to where the others are~!

299032.name: Cait Sith Crooner
299032.desc: I'll sing a song for you, Owner~ Ahem... Wait, I'm not sure I know any Dragon Empery songs, actually...

299033.name: The Cat and the White Steed
299033.desc: "Owner~ I've come to take you to the ball~" ...That's exactly what you were going to do? Eh, doesn't matter who does it~ All that matters is we'll be there together~♪

299034.name: The Cat in the Magic Hat
299034.desc: Owneeer! Lookie! You'll be spending the night with a magician – me! What's the matter? Are you already head over paws for my new look? Don't think I didn't notice how you can't take your eyes off me!

299038.name: White Seaside Melody
299038.desc: Owneeer! Look, look! I've got my wedding dress on! Isn't it frilly and floaty and just so cute? I'll bet you love me so much right now you can't think straight! Heehee♡

299041.name: The Golden Hind's Respite
299041.desc: Phew... Swimming like this doesn't feel all that refreshing... Hey, how about you stop staring and come join me?

499032.name: The Silkiest Brew
499032.desc: Ah! Changed already? Just wait a minute... No, you don't have to leave. I'm almost done.

499033.name: A Blend of Serenity
499033.desc: Commander, come join me in rest. ...Hm? I look unusually relaxed? This is a rare break, and I don't plan to waste it by being stuffy.

499041.name: Black Strokes upon Blank Snow
499041.desc: I thought I would never have time to pursue the fine arts, and yet here I am now. Your thoughts, Commander? Eastern as this calligraphy may be, does it not suit the connotations of my name?

899021.name: Lapis Lazuli's First Dream
899021.desc: It is not against the teachings to halt one's pursuit of destiny and to surrender to the warm draft of festivities. It is mankind's prerogative to seek out auspicious portents.

899028.name: Adulation Eternal
899028.desc: An ode of gratitude for the venerable Iris, echoing tones condensing to pure prayer. Seek blessings not in public worship, but in humanity's true triumph: our everlasting bonds.

199031.name: Dolphins and Swim Lessons
199031.desc: Mm... There... Teacher? Is Anchorage doing it right? Is Anchorage... swimming? Thank goodness... Falling into the water would be bad, right...?

199032.name: Moonlit Boat Ride
199032.desc: Teacher... How are Anchorage's new clothes? Do you like them...? Yeah, I do, too!

199038.name: Oath of Sunsets and Fireworks
199038.desc: Teacher... Anchorage loves you! Our oath... is special! We'll be together... forever!

399051.name: Slice, Dice, and Serve
399051.desc: All righty, one freshly-sliced plate of sashimi coming right up! ...Huh? I'm coming across too aggressive? Even after I went through all this trouble for you, you still have something to nitpick about? ...Well, whatever. Enjoy your meal!

399052.name: Flash of Silk and Strings
399052.desc: Katana... at the ready. Hmph, you again? Never expected you to know anything about music, the way you've been out there conquering the waves with us this whole time. Come then, let me test how good your tastes are with this song!

399053.name: Folded Over a Thousand Times
399053.desc: Hahahaha! Now THIS is a sword worthy of my hands! Perfect blade, perfect hilt, perfect cut – only a master of their craft could make such a beauty! Come on, let's see what this blade can do!

399054.name: Four Fine Layers
399054.desc: Y-you! How dare you make me wear... "I thought it would look good on you, and your current outfit is too breezy"?! What nonsense! I can wear whatever I want in my room! ...Achoo?!

499051.name: Iron Blood's Dragon Maid
499051.desc: Hmph. They think being a maid is so difficult, do they? I could do this with my eyes clo– What?! H-how long have YOU been here?!

499052.name: Golden Dragon Among Auspicious Clouds
499052.desc: New decorations, new outfits, and countless preparations to make... Lunar New Year is quite the busy time of year. Go on, see to your duties. I'm well aware how essential you are to this holiday's smooth operation. Just don't keep me waiting all day. Heehee.

499053.name: One-on-One Leisure Time
499053.desc: Well, I'm pleasantly surprised. A comfortable seat, high-quality beverages, and a nice private room... Hm? Are you going to stand there the whole day? Don't just stare at me like that...

499061.name: The Conquered Unhulde
499061.desc: My hair is a mess... There we go. No, I don't need a hand. I am here to serve you in this fleeting dream of yours. Enjoy it while it lasts. Hehehe.

499062.name: The Unhulde's Midday Respite
499062.desc: You've come, my familiar. I wondered when you'd awake from your... Hm? A little nicer than usual? Yes, because even I have my moments of placidness. Would you prefer that I was more harsh to you?

699011.name: The Queen of Hearts
699011.desc: Me? Serve as your maid? Oho! That's more like it, Commander! How magnificent and ambitious of you! ...Only temporarily? And you're content with that?

299051.name: Heart-Throbbing Refreshment
299051.desc: Rejoice, Commander. I have no doubt that this refreshing sensation will bring you the utmost satisfaction. Come, let us enjoy this experience together.

499071.name: The Gate Dragon's Advent
499071.desc: Woah, so this is the Dragon Empery's "Spring Festival" that I've heard so much about. But, why are they celebrating it in the middle of winter? And you, Commander – why are you helping with such a grandiose... Whuah?! What was that noise?!

499072.name: Midnight Pearl
499072.desc: You're late! I've been waiting ages for you! ...We never agreed to meet tonight? If I say we did, then we did! Anyway, you should feel bad! That's obvious!

599011.name: Union Between Sea and Sky
599011.desc: Pheeew! I just love blue skies and a fair ocean breeze. Since you're already here, Commander, set aside all the boring paperwork and business stuff, and come enjoy the waves!

599012.name: Set Sail for Summer Treasure
599012.desc: Hey, there you are. Remember what I said about the two of us being partners in crime? Well, actions speak louder than words, so I reserved this whole cruise for just the two of us. Whaddya say? Sound good, partner?

599018.name: Red Paeonia
599018.desc: Sorry to keep you waiting, Commander. So, how's my new look? It's got me a bit embarrassed... But, well, all that matters is that you like it.

799011.name: Seaside Sunset
799011.desc: Oh? What made you come over here instead of heading down to the beach? Surely you didn't ditch your friends on a hard-earned day off just to see me? But, I don't mind. It's called a day off because you get to decide how to spend your time.

899031.name: Marine Muse
899031.desc: "I devote this paean to thee, Champion of seas blue and free." There, the song is completed. But we've come all this way... Shall we continue our adventure through these undersea ruins, Champion?

899032.name: Moonlit Night's Spring Vista
899032.desc: O Champion, what manner of floral makeup would look best upon my brow? Or, could I perhaps... call upon you to apply it for me? ♪

199041.name: All-Night Charge
199041.desc: I am now the Hybrid Idealization given flesh and blood wearing a suit designed with my performance for you in mind. I am ready to receive orders at any time.

199042.name: Springtime Monitoring
199042.desc: This suit is a fusion of tradition and modernity. Your feedback would be appreciated... but first, a small issue must be dealt with. May I request your assistance in the matter, Commander?

399061.name: The Comfy Dragon God
399061.desc: You couldn't have picked a better time to come. Allow me to treat you to a cup of the Dragon God's benevolence– Uhh, I'll go boil some water right now, so sit tight. After you finish the tea, shall we kick back and relax awhile?

399062.name: The Relaxing Dragon God
399062.desc: Well, Commander, are you ready? I'm going to teach you the Dragon God's sacred training method. First, you scoop up some water, like... Achoo! Th-that one didn't count!

399063.name: The Relaxing Dragon God
399063.desc: Whew... So refreshing. Nothing beats lounging around indoors after a bath. Commander, there's plenty of time before dinner, so how about we... do something to kill the time?

499081.name: Sweet, Sleepy "Revenge"
499081.desc: My, my. I'm quite surprised you're still able to stay awake. As expected of the Commander– even a dose of Felix Schultz's special concoction isn't enough to put you under... but that ends here. It's your fault for peeping on me slacking off in the first place, so be nice and obedient and succumb to me already~♪

499091.name: Delirious Duel
499091.desc: It's just the two of us now, Contract Binder. Come – play a game with me and immerse yourself in the pleasures this place offers. The loser of this game, of course, must accept a punishment tonight♡

999021.name: If Love is a Sin, Thou Art Forgiven
999021.desc: *sniffle*... Oh, Commander, what have I done...? I was supposed to serve You, and now I've committed a grave sin of messing everything up... Where did I go wrong...?

199051.name: A Special Day with the Bunny Lord
199051.desc: "Welcome, dear guest♪ Right this way~ I'm happy to join you for a treat and chat♪" ...It was good? Well, obviously. I take my work very seriously!

399071.name: Bunny Priestess in Prayer
399071.desc: Oh, Commander! You're here earlier than I expected. Ah, I finally get to serve you in this specially made attire, stuffed full of such fantasy and dreams... I'm ever so honored.

699021.name: Dreamy Night
699021.desc: Commander... Apologies for appearing before you like this. I'll try to get up right at once... Agh... I'm still so dizzy...

799021.name: First Time in the Limelight
799021.desc: What are you doing on the set, Commander? Here to check on the progress? But won't this spoil your first impression of the final cut? Well, the video is made for you anyways, so consider this a preview.

799022.name: A Fresh, Green Day
799022.desc: Commander, come here and plant a saxaul... Oh, I look like I'm enjoying this a lot? Yeah. It's because I don't get to do much outdoor work, since I'm always stuck in my workshop, poring over data and equipment. Also, you're here with me.

899041.name: The Most Treacherous Trial
899041.desc: Welcome, Commander. ...You really don't know what I'm doing? So there are things even you don't know. This is a new means of training knights, you see. Expect ever greater exploits from me.

9707010.name: Hiryuu META
9707010.desc: I'm getting all fired up! The name's Hiryuu, Hiryuu from the 2nd CarDiv. As a member of this fleet, I'll obey your orders. I do hope that you are qualified to lead us.

9707020.name: Ark Royal META
9707020.desc: Aircraft carrier Ark Royal, at your service. I hereby vow to lend you my strength for as long as you harbour honourable ambitions!

9702010.name: Helena META
9702010.desc: Were you looking for me? I am willing to lend you my power – provided that you promise not to hide anything from me.

9707030.name: Souryuu META
9707030.desc: I am Souryuu of the Sakura Empire's 2nd CarDiv. Let's skip the formalities and get to work right away.

9705010.name: Fusou META
9705010.desc: I am battleship Fusou. I have come to bring peace to this world's tormented souls. Commander, do you seek blessings... or redemption?

9706010.name: Hiyou META
9706010.desc: Ahahahaha! The fact that you've chosen me means you clearly have a discerning eye. So, what now? Where's the enemy you need me to sink?

9704010.name: Gneisenau META
9704010.desc: You're... the Commander, right? In other words, the one with the authority to control me. Though I have no interest in you as an individual, I will still obey your orders... At least for the time being.

9706020.name: Junyou META
9706020.desc: I'm... Junyou. Please give me your orders... Commander.

9704020.name: Scharnhorst META
9704020.desc: I'm Iron Blood battlecruiser Scharnhorst. I am keen to join forces with a Commander as talented as you. Don't let my expectations of you be misplaced.

9705020.name: Yamashiro META
9705020.desc: Are you this fleet's Commander, Milord? I see. You have great potential, but your skills need some refinement. I wonder what's the best way to train you... You'll see soon enough – stay alert until then!

9702020.name: Memphis META
9702020.desc: I'm Memphis. You may not know me, but I know you and I know you well. Don't you worry, I'm not a threat – you can trust me. Today I assume the role of your right hand and bodyguard.

9704030.name: Repulse META
9704030.desc: I'm Repulse, Renown-class battlecruiser. I've been through a lot... but that's in the past. Now, I'm a part of this port. Whenever you're in a pinch, come see me.

9703010.name: Trento META
9703010.desc: I am heavy cruiser Trento, and I will be your assistant. The best thing I could ask for is that my support helps you achieve your goals.

9704040.name: Renown META
9704040.desc: Salutations to you, Commander. I am battlecruiser Renown. I hope that this battle-worn blade can become your power.

9701010.name: Hunter META
9701010.desc: Greetings, Commander. I'm Hunter. I hunt, as you might've surmised. Is this place... my new base?

9701020.name: Fortune META
9701020.desc: Well met, Commander. My name is Fortune. Please don't worry about these ch-chains... They're there to... keep my power in check.

9705030.name: Arizona META
9705030.desc: I am Arizona... This may be improper of me, but is it really alright for me to stay here? ...Very well, Commander. If that is what you've decided...

9702030.name: Sheffield META
9702030.desc: So you're the Commander... in other words, my Master. Alright, got it. The name's Sheffield, and the game's pointing my gun at vermin – Ah, please disregard that little gesture I made just now.

9705040.name: Queen Elizabeth META
9705040.desc: So you are the Commander? Very well. From this point forth, you will use your courage and intellect for our purposes! ...We don't have all day, now. You are our servant, so this won't go anywhere until you swear your fealty.

9702040.name: La Galissonnière META
9702040.desc: I'm La Galissonnière, the shipgirl from hell! I've come for your soul! ...Wow, didn't even flinch. Guess it's true that you don't fear death. Heheh, let's see if I can get a more interesting response out of you next time~♪

9708010.name: U-556 META
9708010.desc: U-556, the Parzival of the Seas, has arrived! Let's see if there's really anything I can help with here. Seeing as I'll be staying here – nice meeting you♪

9712010.name: Vestal META
9712010.desc: I... assume you're the Commander? Don't worry, I can see that you're in good health. I'm Vestal. Bring your sick to me, and I should be able to assist with treatment and repairs...

9703020.name: Algérie META
9703020.desc: You must be the Commander. I am the heavy cruiser Algérie. So, what pleasures can I experience here? I do hope you won't disappoint me. Heehee~

9701030.name: Hatakaze META
9701030.desc: You're helpless... So helpless it's worrying me. Oh, also, no need to concern yourself with who I am. Just think of me as the one who'll help you get your act together.

9702050.name: Jintsuu META
9702050.desc: I am the light cruiser named Jintsuu. I take it you summoned me because you need help? ...Very well. Then I shall humbly devise plans that will serve your fleet.

9706030.name: Princeton META
9706030.desc: Aircraft carrier Princeton, reporting for duty. I'm afraid I'm still a bit disoriented... would you mind briefing me on the situation?

9713010.name: Erebus META
9713010.desc: I have arrived, heeding your summon. Worry not, this isn't a nightmare, but rather a fateful mercy. Now, make a pact with me and become an acolyte of darkness.

9702060.name: Kirov META
9702060.desc: Tovarishch Ofitser, our meeting here will send trembles across the world! All my strength is yours to realize your ideals with. Let us fight, together!

9701040.name: Kimberly META
9701040.desc: I am Kimberly of the Fletcher class, ready to serve. That should do it for introductions. What's important is that I am your sword – all you need to do is tell me what to cut.

9702070.name: Pamiat' Merkuria META
9702070.desc: Yoohoo! Nice to meet you, Commander... When can I start? Heehee. You clearly don't understand the situation here. If you want the privilege of working with the noble Lady Pamiat' Merkuria, you'll have to earn it!

9705050.name: Rodney META
9705050.desc: On behalf of all Rodneys, greetings... You must understand, "I" am a physical representation of the concept of "Rodney." "I" am no more than that...

9701050.name: Vampire META
9701050.desc: The adorable Vampire, messenger of the dark night, graces thee with her presence. Hehe, thou smellest sweet♪ Thou art certainly the one I've dreamed of♡

9707040.name: Béarn META
9707040.desc: I am Béarn, a high mage and a humble seeker of knowledge and power. If I may ask, can I expect to find any supreme Sacraments in this place?

9703030.name: Foch META
9703030.desc: Hey and good day, Commander. I am Foch, the Warlord. Heehee, the Warlord of what, you ask? That should be obvious – the Warlord of Hell! Hahaha! It's good to be serving you.

9703040.name: Wichita META
9703040.desc: You the Commander? Alright, say no more. Take me into battle and I guarantee ya won't be let down!

9701060.name: Kasumi META
9701060.desc: You... have summoned Kasumi. Commander, what do you need of me?

9705060.name: Nagato META
9705060.desc: I am Nagato, Guardian Fox of the "Sakura Empire". Tell me, why have you summoned me? For power? Or for a wish you would like to have granted?

9704050.name: Hiei META
9704050.desc: Battlecruiser Hiei, at your service. What shall we do next, Commander? I am ready to patrol or head into battle, so let us sortie at your earliest convenience.

9706040.name: Houshou META
9706040.desc: Commander, I am Houshou. Henceforth, I will take veeery good care of you. Forget all your concerns and just let me handle everything. Heehee♥

9705070.name: Giulio Cesare META
9705070.desc: I am Giulio Cesare, conqueror of the empire. Spare me the needless chatter. I have no desire to squander time on such things.

9707050.name: Taihou META
9707050.desc: Finally... Finally, I've met you, my Commander! My thirst has been quenched and the hole in me has been filled! Heehee... Now if you don't mind, I'm going to melt you little by little with my immense love♥

9703050.name: Admiral Hipper META
9703050.desc: I'm Admiral Hipper, lead ship of my class and sister to Eugen and Blücher. Got it memorized?

9703060.name: Bolzano META
9703060.desc: I am Bolzano, a knight of the Sardegnia League. Commander, I await my next task.

9705080.name: Andrea Doria META
9705080.desc: I'm Andrea Doria, of the Sardegnia League. Is this your port, Commander? I see... It's a lovely place. I think I'll like it here.

9707060.name: Hornet META
9707060.desc: You're the Commander of the fleet? Nice meetin' you! I'm Hornet, the youngest among the Yorktown class. I may not be as amazing as my big sisters, but I'm still pretty capable... probably!

9705090.name: Nevada META
9705090.desc: Yo, young'un. I know you've got things under control here, but this port may not be peaceful forever. You should stay with me from now on! I'll keep you safe no matter what happens!

9701070.name: Grenville META
9701070.desc: I'm Royal Navy destroyer Grenville, returning to the battlefield in META form. Long ago, I... No, that's all in the past now. Just give me a chance, Commander. I swear to keep the fleet safe this time.

9707070.name: Glorious META
9707070.desc: Good day to you, Commander. I'm the Royal Navy aircraft carrier Glorious. It's an honour to be here, and I thank you for having me.

9701080.name: Kawakaze META
9701080.desc: So you're the Commander. I am Kawakaze, a roamer of the lands. We will be walking the same path for some time. Let's be cordial.
